<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1004> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: THE STUDY OF COMPLICATIONS IN CB USING DATA MINING IS INCIPIENT, BUT IT CAN SUPPORT SPECIALISTS IN CLINICAL DECISION MAKING. OBJECTIVE: TO IDENTIFY PREDICTORS OF IMMEDIATE POSTOPERATIVE COMPLICATIONS IN PATIENTS SUBMITTED TO CB USING DATA MINING. METHOD: AN ANALYTICAL DESCRIPTIVE STUDY, THROUGH THE ANALYSIS OF THE CB / UFPE CB PATIENT DATABASE, THROUGH THE APPLICATION OF THE FIRST THREE STAGES OF THE CRISP-DM METHODOLOGY. THE FIRST STAGE CONSISTED OF A SYSTEMATIC REVIEW AND CONSULT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "09FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
