<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1005> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PURPOSE: THE PURPOSE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO DETERMINE THE SAFETY OF MOXIFLOXACIN FOR FIVE WEEKS AFTER CATARACT SURGERY. METHODS: A PROSPECTIVE CONSECUTIVE SAMPLE OF 1.016 CATARACT SURGERIES WAS CONSIDERED. THE INCLUSION CRITERIA WERE PATIENTS WITH INDICATION FOR CATARACT SURGERY, AT LEAST 55 YEARS OF AGE, AND NO HISTORY OF ALLERGY TO QUINOLONES. PATIENTS WERE PREPARED FOR SURGERY USING A 5% DILUTED POVIDONE SOLUTION AS A TOPICAL ANTISEPTIC AGENT. THE OPERATIVE TECHNIQUE WAS PHACOEMULSIFICATION WIT"@pt ;
