<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10193> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SHORTAGE OF DRUGS APPROVED BY REGULATORY AGENCIES IN DOSES AND PHARMACEUTICAL FORMS SUITABLE FOR PEDIATRIC USE, REQUIRES HEALTH PROFESSIONALS TO PRESCRIBE AND ADMINISTER DRUGS DIFFERENTLY THE DIRECTIONS EXPRESSED IN THE PACKAGE LEAFLET, CHARACTERIZING OFF-LABEL USE. THE PREVALENCE OF OFF-LABEL DRUG USE INCREASES IN THE CONTEXT OF PEDIATRIC ICUS, AS THE SEVERITY OF INPATIENT PATHOLOGIES REQUIRES THE PRESCRIPTION OF A LARGE NUMBER OF DRUGS THAT OFTEN NEED TO BE CHANGED DURING PREPARATION AND P"@pt ;
