<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10205> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "POST VACCINATION ADVERSE EVENTS (EAPV) IS ANY UNWANTED OCCURRENCE FOLLOWING VACCINE OR IMMUNOBIOLOGICAL USE. SERIOUS ADVERSE EVENTS RESULTING IN DEATH, RISK OF DEATH, PERMANENT DISABILITY AS SEQUELAE, CONGENITAL ANOMALIES OR MINIMUM HOSPITALIZATION OF 24 HOURS ARE CONSIDERED SERIOUS, REQUIRING IMMEDIATE CLINICAL INTERVENTION TO PREVENT DEATH. THE OBJECTIVE IS TO DESCRIBE THE MAIN ADVERSE EVENTS FOLLOWING THE USE OF PERTUSSIS COMPONENT VACCINES REPORTED IN PERNAMBUCO AND TO VERIFY THE ASSOCIATION"@pt ;
