<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10206> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: ABOUT 55% OF BRAZILIAN PREGNANCIES ARE UNPLANNED AND REFLECT CONTRACEPTIVE NEEDS THAT WERE NOT COVERED. THE INSERTION OF THE COPPER INTRAUTERINE DEVICE IN THE IMMEDIATE POSTPARTUM PERIOD PROVIDE EFFECTIVE, SAFE AND CONVENIENT CONTRACEPTION. ALTHOUGH IT IS A PRACTICE STIMULATED BY SEVERAL MEDICAL SOCIETIES THERE ARE SOME POINTS TO BE UNDERSTOOD AS THE KNOWLEDGE OF THE ASSOCIATED FACTORS WITH THE VISIBILITY OF THE WIRES AND THE EXPULSION OF THE COPPER INTRAUTERINE DEVICE. OBJECTIVES:"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17JUN2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "FATORES ASSOCIADOS À VISIBILIDADE DOS FIOS E À EXPULSÃO DO DISPOSITIVO INTRAUTERINO DE COBRE INSERIDO IMEDIATAMENTE APÓS O PARTO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/AURELIANA_BARBOZA_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ENFERMAGEM_-_FESP-UPE_-_UEPB> .

