<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10210> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: THE INJURED BODY CAN HAVE A SOCIAL REPRESENTATION OF THE BODY SAID TO BE PERFECT BY SOCIETY. WHEN PEOPLE EXPERIENCE THE INJURED BODY, IT CAN AFFECT THE BIOPSYCHOSOCIAL ASPECTS REFERRING TO THE BODY IMAGE. OBJECTIVES: TO ANALYZE THE SELF-PERCEPTION OF THE INJURED BODY FROM THE SOCIAL REPRESENTATIONS OF THE BODY. METHODOLOGY: DESCRIPTIVE, EXPLORATORY STUDY WITH A QUALITATIVE APPROACH, GUIDED BY THE THEORY OF SOCIAL REPRESENTATIONS CARRIED OUT AT A UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL IN THE WOUND AMB"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30AUG2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PESSOAS ADULTAS COM FERIDAS CRÔNICAS: AUTOPERCEPÇÃO DO CORPO FERIDO A PARTIR DAS REPRESENTAÇÕES SOCIAIS DO CORPO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/KASSIA_MORGANNA_DE_VASCONCELOS_TORRES> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ENFERMAGEM_-_FESP-UPE_-_UEPB> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10211> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SEXUALITY IS SOMETHING THAT IS BUILT AND LEARNED, AN INTEGRAL PART OF THE DEVELOPMENT OF THE PERSONALITY, CAPABLE OF INTERFERING IN THE LEARNING PROCESS, IN THE MENTAL AND PHYSICAL HEALTH OF THE INDIVIDUAL. THE EXPERIENCE OF WOMEN'S SEXUALITY IS AN IMPORTANT COMPONENT OF QUALITY OF LIFE AND INDIVIDUAL AND RELATIONAL SATISFACTION. FEMALE SEXUAL DYSFUNCTION, ALTHOUGH PREVALENT, IS OFTEN UNDERREPORTED AND DIFFICULT TO ADDRESS BY BOTH THE PATIENT AND HEALTH PROFESSIONALS, DUE TO SHAME AND TABOOS SUR"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "26FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PREVALÊNCIA DE DISFUNÇÃO SEXUAL EM JOVENS UNIVERSITÁRIAS E FATORES ASSOCIADOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/WALQUIRIA_QUIRINO_DE_QUEIROZ> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ENFERMAGEM_-_FESP-UPE_-_UEPB> .

