<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1024> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PURPOSE OF THIS THESIS WAS TO ELABORATE AND VALIDATE A SCALE TO EVALUATE THE ATTITUDES OF DENTAL STUDENTS IN RELATION TO DENTAL COMPETENCES DURING THEIR TRAINING. THE THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK INVOLVED CONCEPTS OF SOCIAL PSYCHOLOGY AND EDUCATION, AMONG THEM THE DENTAL COMPETENCIES DESCRIBED IN THE NATIONAL CURRICULAR GUIDELINES: HEALTH CARE, COMMUNICATION, LIFELONG EDUCATION, DECISION MAKING, LEADERSHIP, AND MANAGEMENT. IT WAS A METHODOLOGICAL DEVELOPMENT STUDY THAT RESULTED IN THREE ARTICLES, C"@pt ;
