<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1031> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "OBJECTIVES: THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO EVALUATE THE PREVALENCE OF CYTOMEGALOVIRUS (CMV) AND PERIODONTITIS IN CHRONIC RENAL PATIENTS UNDERGOING HEMODIALYSIS. MATERIALS AND METHODS: THE PRESENT STUDY WAS EPIDEMIOLOGICAL AND OBSERVATIONAL, COMPOSED OF A CASE GROUP THAT INVOLVED PATIENTS ON HEMODIALYSIS FROM THE UFPE HOSPITAL DAS CLÍNICAS AND MARIA LUCINDA HOSPITAL, RECIFE, PE. THE CONTROL GROUP CONSISTED OF PATIENTS WHO FIRST CONSULTED FOR SCREENING AT THE STOMATOLOGY CLINIC OF UFPE, AND WERE HEA"@pt ;
