<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1033> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SILDENAFIL CITRATE IS A POTENT SELECTIVE PHOSPHODIESTERASE-5 INHIBITOR AND ITS DISCOVERY REPRESENTED A BREAKTHROUGH IN THE TREATMENT OF ERECTILE DYSFUNCTION. CURRENTLY, THIS DRUG HAS BEEN SHOWING POSITIVE EFFECTS WITH REGARD TO THE REDUCTION OF INFLAMMATORY PROCESS AND REDUCTION OF OXIDATIVE STRESS, WITH CONSEQUENT REDUCTION OF TISSUE DAMAGE, IN SEVERAL PATHOLOGIES. THE EFFECT OF SILDENAFIL CITRATE ON THE PREVENTION AND PROGRESSION OF EXPERIMENTAL PERIODONTITIS (PE) IN RATS WAS EVALUATED AS THE "@pt ;
