<http://example.com/capes#thesis/10633> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THYROID NODULES MAKE ABOUT 1-2% OF ALL TUMORS IN WORLDWIDE. THE EPIDEMIOLOGICAL DATA ARE STILL QUITE CONTROVERSIAL AND FEW STUDIES THE MORPHOLOGICAL CHARACTERISTICS OF THESE LESIONS WERE MADE. AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO ESTABLISH THE EPIDEMIOLOGICAL PROFILE AND THE MAIN ANATOMO-PATHOLOGICAL ASPECTS OF THYROID NODULES IN PATIENTS FROM PUBLIC HEALTH SERVICE IN BRAZIL, BETWEEN THE 2010 TO 2016 YEARS. THE STUDY HAD THE PARTICIPATION OF 130 VOLUNTEERS WITH BENIGN OR MALIGNANT LESIONS OF THYROID GLAND, "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "31JAN2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
