<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1101> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "OBJECTIVE: TO EVALUATE THE VASCULAR DENSITY OF THE SUPERFICIAL AND DEEP PLEXUS, THE FOVEAL AVASCULAR ZONE (FAZ), PERIPAPILLARY REGION, AND OPTIC DISC USING THE OPTICAL COHERENCE TOMOGRAPHY ANGIOGRAPHY (OCTA) IN INDIVIDUALS WITH SICKLE CELL DISEASE (SCD) RETINOPATHY COMPARED TO A CONTROL GROUP. METHODS: A CROSS-SECTIONAL AND OBSERVATIONAL STUDY INCLUDED INDIVIDUALS WITH SCD [SICKLE-CELL ANEMIA (HBSS), HEMOGLOBINOPATHY SC (HBSC), OR BETATHALASSEMIA (HBSB-THAL)], AND HEALTHY SUBJECTS, AGE MATCHED. "@pt ;
