<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1102> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "TYMPANOPLASTY IS A GOLD STANDARD TREATMENT FOR DRUM PERFORATIONS. MANY DIFFERENT GRAFTS WERE STUDIED BEING TEMPORALIS FASCIA AND CARTILAGE THE MORE ROUTINELY USED NOWADAYS. NASAL MUCOSA IS AN INTERESTING ALTERNATIVE GRAFT, BUT THERE ARE FEW PAPERS SHOWING ITS SAFETY AND EFFECTIVENESS. IN THIS CONTROLLED RANDOMIZED CLINICAL TRIAL, WE COMPARED SURGICAL AND AUDIOLOGICAL RESULTS OF NASAL MUCOSA GRAFT VERSUS TEMPORALIS FASCIA, IN 40 PATIENTS THAT UNDERWENT TYMPANOPLASTY, DIVIDED IN 2 GROUPS OF 20 PAT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "19FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "USO DO ENXERTO DE MUCOSA NASAL EM TIMPANOPLASTIA"@pt ;
