    capes:hasAbstract "ABSTRACT: BRAZIL UNDERSTANDS THAT THE PRODUCTION AND CONSUMPTION OF DRUGS IS A PUBLIC HEALTH AND SAFETY PROBLEM, ESTABLISHING IN ITS FEDERAL CONSTITUTION THAT IT IS UP TO THE FEDERAL POLICE TO CONFRONT THEM. WITH THIS FOUNDATION, THE PURPOSE OF THE RESEARCH WAS TO PROVE HOW THE OPERATION OF CONTROL OF ILLICIT MARIJUANA CROPS, CARRIED OUT BY THE FEDERAL POLICE, IN THE BACKLANDS OF PERNAMBUCO, CORRESPONDS TO AN ACTION AIMED AT HUMAN SECURITY. USING THE INDUCTIVE METHOD, THROUGH THE JOINT PROCEDURE"@pt ;
