<http://example.com/capes#thesis/11461> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: MEASLES IS AN ACUTE INFECTIOUS DISEASE, VACCINE PREVENTABLE, VIRAL IN NATURE, TRANSMISSIBLE AND EXTREMELY CONTAGIOUS. IN 2016 BRAZIL RECEIVED FROM THE WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION (WHO) THE CERTIFICATE FOR ELIMINATING THE CIRCULATION OF THE VIRUS IN THE COUNTRY, HOWEVER THERE WAS AN OUTBREAK IN 2018 AND AN ABRUPT INCREASE IN CASES IN THE FOLLOWING YEAR. WITH THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC, SEVERAL ADAPTATIONS AND INVESTMENTS IN HEALTH WERE NECESSARY, WHICH COULD LEAD TO SOME IMPACT ON OTHER DI"@pt ;
