    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/AVALIAÇÃO_EM_SAÚDE> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/11463> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SETTING: FROM MARCH 2020, BRAZIL HAS BEEN FACING A PANDEMIC CAUSED BY THE NEW CORONAVIRUS (SARS-COV-2), SIMULTANEOUSLY WITH ARBOVIRUSES - ZIKA, DENGUE AND CHIKUNGUNYA. THESE ARBOVIRUSES AND THE DISEASE CAUSED BY SARS-COV-2 (COVID-19) USE THE SAME MOLECULAR ASSAY FOR DIAGNOSIS, USING THE REAL-TIME RT-PCR (RT-QPCR) TECHNIQUE, THE GOLD STANDARD TEST. WITH THE INCURSION OF THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC, THE PUBLIC LABORATORY NETWORK OF PERNAMBUCO FOCUSED EFFORTS ON DETECTING SARS-COV-2 TO THE DETRIMENT OF Z"@pt ;
