<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1152> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH INTRODUCES THE READER TO THE IMPORTANCE AND IMPACT OF THE COMMERCIAL ENERGY LOSSES IN THE BRAZILIAN ELECTRICITY SECTOR. IT SHOWS THE RELATION BETWEEN THE MAIN SOCIOECONOMIC VARIABLES AND THE COMMERCIAL LOSSES OF ELECTRICITY OF THE LOCAL ELECTRICITY UTILITY IN A CASE STUDY IN RECIFE, CAPITAL OF PERNAMBUCO STATE, BRAZIL. THE RELATIONS WERE MADE USING THE C4.5 STATISTICAL ALGORITHM THAT SHOWS THE IMPACT OF EACH VARIABLE ON ENERGY LOSSES AND WHICH ARE THE MOST CRITICAL. WITH THIS, IT W"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30OCT2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
