<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1153> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE CO2 ADSORPTION PROCESS, WHICH IS ONE OF THE MAIN GASES THAT IMPACT GLOBAL WARMING, IS VERY IMPORTANT NOWADAYS AND IN THE NEXT FEW YEARS, IT WILL TAKE APPROXIMATELY A FEW YEARS. THE PRESENT DISSERTATION WAS WRITTEN TO THE MATHEMATICAL SYSTEM RULE TO SIMULATE THE CO2 ADSORPTION BEHAVIOR OF THE CO2 / N2 MIXTURE THROUGHOUT THE FLOW FILTRATION PROCESS THROUGH A BED CONTAINING ADSORBENTS KNOWN AS ZEOLITES. THE MATHEMATICAL MODEL WAS USED TO SIMULATE A TEMPERATURE VARIATION ALONG THE ADSORPTION PRO"@pt ;
