    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1154> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DUE TO THE OIL CRISIS OF 1970, THE DEMAND FOR RENEWABLE ENERGY SOURCES TO REPLACE FOSSIL FUELS AND THE VARIATION OF THE ELECTRIC GENERATION MATRIX ALLIED WITH LARGE-SCALE ELECTRICITY PRODUCTION WERE THE REASONS FOR THE UTILIZATION OF SOLAR ENERGY AROUND THE WORLD, LEADING TO THE IMPLEMENTATION OF CONCENTRATED SOLAR POWER (CSP) WITH THE PURPOSE TO HARNESS SOLAR ENERGY POTENTIAL WITH WELL-KNOWN CONVERSION TECHNOLOGY OF THERMAL ENERGY INTO ELECTRICAL. IN ORDER TO BRING BRAZILIAN ENERGY MATRIX ANOTH"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "04NOV2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
