<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1156> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE TEXTILE AND APPAREL INDUSTRY IS OF GREAT RELEVANCE TO THE BRAZILIAN ECONOMY, NOT ONLY BECAUSE OF THE ANNUAL TURNOVER OF ITS STRUCTURAL PRODUCTION CHAINS, NOR THE NUMBER OF COMPANIES IN BUSINESS, BUT MAINLY DUE TO THE GENERATION OF DIRECT AND INDIRECT JOBS THAT THIS SECTOR PROVIDES, THEN, ACCORDING TO THE BRAZILIAN ASSOCIATION OF TEXTILE AND CLOTHING INDUSTRY, RESPONSIBLE FOR 3.5% OF THE COUNTRY'S GROSS DOMESTIC PRODUCT (GDP). THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO HAS THE SECOND LARGEST POLO OF CONFECTIONS"@pt ;
