<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1176> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BRAZILIAN NORTHEAST HAS BECOME THE MAIN REGION OF THE COUNTRY ON DEVELOPING PROJECTS ABOUT SOLAR PHOTOVOLTAIC POWER PLANTS. IT OCCURS DUE THE FACT THAT THE VALUES OF SOLAR IRRADIATION ON THIS AREA HAS THE HIGHEST AVERAGE AND THE LOWER VARIABILITY ON THE COUNTY, BEING THE REGION LOCATED IN EXCELLENT POSITION TO THE IMPLEMENT OF SUCH POWER PLANTS. DESPITE THE WIDE DIMENSION OF AVAILABLE LANDS TO THIS KIND OF ENTERPRISE, IT IS NECESSARY TO TAKE INTO CONSIDERATION A GAMMA OF CRITERIA TO CHOOSE T"@pt ;
