    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1177> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE ARARIPE HINTERLAND IS KNOWN NATIONALLY FOR THE HIGH POVERTY RATES OF ITS POPULATION. IN CONTRAST TO THIS REALITY OF CONSTRAINTS, 95% OF THE NATIONAL GYPSUM IS PRODUCED IN THIS REGION, IN A CLUSTER OF COMPANIES CALLED POLO GESSEIRO DO ARARIPE (PGA). INVOLVED IN ITS PROBLEMS, THE LOW TECHNOLOGICAL LEVEL OF THE CALCINATION FURNACES IS THE RESULT OF THE LACK OF TECHNICAL STUDIES THAT ALLOW TO KNOW THE PHENOMENA OF HEAT AND MASS TRANSPORT RELATED TO THE TRANSFORMATION OF GYPSUM INTO GYPSUM THAT O"@pt ;
