<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1179> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ENERGY EFFICIENCY IS ONE OF THE MAJOR COMPANIES GOALS IN THE WORLD. KNOWING ENERGY CONSUMPTION AND FIND WAYS TO REDUCE THIS CONSUMPTION HAS BEEN ONE OF THE GREAT CHALLENGES FOR INDUSTRIES IN THE MANUFACTURE PROCESS OF THEIR PRODUCTS. ISO 50001 - ENERGY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM (SGEN) WAS ELABORATED WITH THE PURPOSE OF ESTABLISHING MINIMUM AND SPECIFIC REQUIREMENTS TO GUARANTEE THE CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT OF THE ENERGY PERFORMANCE IN THE ORGANIZATION THAT ADOPTS IT. THE STANDARD IS BASED ON THE PLAN-DO-C"@pt ;
