    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1180> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "A BRAZILIAN NAVAL INDUSTRY EXPERIENCED A MAJOR CRISIS IN THE LAST FORTY YEARS, BUT IN 2004 THE GOVERNMENT RETURNED TO INVEST IN THE SECTOR, RESURFACING THE BRAZILIAN SHIPBUILDING INDUSTRY. THE GENERATION OF ELECTRICAL ENERGY FROM A SUEZMAX TYPE OIL TANKER IS ONLY THROUGH DIESEL GENERATORS, WHOSE FINANCIAL COST IS HIGH, PROVIDES POLLUTION OF THE ENVIRONMENT, AGGRAVATING THE GREENHOUSE EFFECT OF THE PLANET. THE GOAL OF THIS DISSERTATION IS TO STUDY THE FEASIBILITY AND APPLICABILITY OF PHOTOVOLTAIC"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "16MAY2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "IMPLEMENTAÇÃO DO SISTEMA SOLAR FOTOVOLTAICO COMO FONTE ALTERNATIVA DE ENERGIA ELÉTRICA EM UM NAVIO PETROLEIRO"@pt ;
