<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1181> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AMONG THE MAIN IMPROVEMENTS WITH THE EVOLUTION OF THE STRUCTURE OF THE BRAZILIAN ELECTRICITY SECTOR, THE END OF THE MONOPOLY IN THE PURCHASE OF ENERGY FOR SOME CONSUMERS HAS BECOME VERY STRONG TOOL IN THE SCOPE OF THE ECONOMY AND RESOURCE REDIRECTION. IN THIS WORK, WE ANALYZED THE CASE OF SEASONAL COMPANIES, ESPECIALLY THE SHIPYARDS, BELONGING TO THIS GROUP OF FREE NEGOTIATION, AIMING THE MIGRATION TO THE ACL AS A RESOURCE TO REDUCE ENERGY COSTS AND RESALE THE BALLAST IN MARKET. AFTER SOME BASIC"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "MIGRAÇÃO PARA O AMBIENTE DE CONTRATAÇÃO LIVRE DE ENERGIA COMO UMA ALTERNATIVA ECONÔMICA PARA ESTALEIROS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
