<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1183> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THE PRESENT WORK, A BASIC STUDY OF COMPUTATIONAL FLUID DYNAMICS (CFD), IN A CENTRIFUGAL FIRE-FIGHTING PUMP, USING THE ANSYS-CFX COMPUTATIONAL PACKAGE IN THE STUDENT VERSION, WERE CARRIED OUT SIMULATIONS OF THE WORK FLUID FLOW (LIQUID WATER), WITH INPUT PARAMETERS OF 25ºC OF TEMPERATURE AND ATMOSPHERIC PRESSURE. THE DEFINITION AND PRESENTATION OF A CFD DESIGN METHODOLOGY AND ITS VALIDATION, IN A WAY THAT CAN BE APPLIED IN SIMILAR EQUIPMENT PROJECTS IS THE MAIN OBJECTIVE OF THE WORK. WE, THEN, "@pt ;
