<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1186> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN BRAZIL THERE IS A COMPLEX SYSTEM IN THE TRANSPORTATION AND STORAGE LOGISTICS OF LIQUEFIED PETROLEUM GAS (LPG), IMPORTANT FOR THE POPULATION AND LOCAL INDUSTRIES. THIS LOGISTICS INCLUDES SEVERAL STEPS, THIS STORAGE BEING ONE OF THE MOST IMPORTANT. IN STORAGE, THE GAS IS KEPT IN LIQUIDVAPOR EQUILIBRIUM (LVE) BY COMPRESSION AND, IF FOR SOME REASON THE INTERNAL PRESSURE OF THE GAS VARIES ABOVE THE SUPPORTED MATERIAL OF THE STORAGE VESSEL, CRASHES MAY OCCUR WHICH CAUSE ACCIDENTS. IN THIS SENSE, IN"@pt ;
