    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1188> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN ORDER TO INCREASE THE PHOTOVOLTAIC'S COMPETITIVENESS AGAINST OTHER SOURCES AND TO ADAPT TO LOWER AND LOWER PRICES, IT IS NECESSARY FOR THE INVESTOR TO USE APPROPRIATE TOOLS TO POSITION THEMSELVES IN AUCTIONS, AVOIDING UNWANTED RISKS AND INCREASING THEIR CHANCES OF GUARANTEEING A MINIMUM RETURN. THIS WORK AIMS TO DEVELOP A COMPUTATIONAL APPLICATION THAT HELPS A PHOTOVOLTAIC INVESTOR TO FIND A COMBINATION OF SALES PRICE AND AMOUNT OF ENERGY THAT CAN GUARANTEE WITH A CERTAIN DEGREE OF CONFIDENCE"@pt ;
