<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1190> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE GROWTH IN CONSUMPTION AND THE INCORRECT DISPOSAL OF PLASTIC MATERIALS MAKE THIS WASTE A WORLDWIDE PROBLEM. IN BRAZIL, THE PERCENTAGE OF RECYCLING OF PROCESSED PLASTICS IS ONLY 26% (M/M) OF THE DEMAND CONSUMED, ANOTHER PART CONTINUES TO BE DEPOSITED IN LANDFILLS AND LANDFILLS, NOT TAKING ADVANTAGE OF ITS ENERGY POTENTIAL, DEGRADING IT IN A SLOW AND UNDESIRABLE WAY. THIS DISSERTATION USES THE PYROLYSIS PROCESS AS AN ALTERNATIVE TO REAPPROVE THE ENERGY CONSUMPTION OF THESE RESIDUES, GENERATING "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "05DEC2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
