    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1191> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BRAZIL PRODUCES ENERGY FROM FOSSIL AND RENEWABLE SOURCES AT ALMOST THE SAME PERCENTAGES, A FACT THAT DOES NOT OCCUR IN THE REST OF THE WORLD WHERE GENERATION BY NON-RENEWABLE SOURCES IS PRIORITIZED (78%). HYDROELECTRIC PLANTS DOMINATE THE NATIONAL GENERATION WITH 61.6%, BUT THE LACK OF USEFUL VOLUME IN THE RESERVOIRS OF THE PLANTS AND THE GROWING DEMAND FOR ENERGY CAUSE A SEARCH FOR ALTERNATIVE SOURCES THAT CAN COMPOSE THE ENERGY MATRIX EFFICIENTLY AND DO NOT PRODUCE TOXIC GASES. TO THE ENVIRONM"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "12DEC2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
