<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1192> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS PAPER SHOWS ONE PROPOSAL FOR A LITTLE CAPACITY TANK (100 L) WITH THE GOAL OF THE COOL DOWN AND STORAGE BOVINE MILK FROM LITTLE PRODUCERS FARMS FROM BRAZIL. THE LAW SET THAT THE MILK, AFTER MILKING PROCESS, BE CHILLED IN TEMPERATURES BELOW 4 °C, IN UNTIL 3 H. EVEN WITH THIS NORMATIVE OBLIGATION, MOST NATIONAL PRODUCERS HAVE NOT COOLING TANK. THE FACILITY SALE OF THE PRODUCT ON IRREGULAR MARKET AND THE OPERATIONAL COST WITH THE TRADITIONAL EQUIPMENT, CONTRIBUTE WITH THE REFUSE OF THE PRODUCER"@pt ;
