    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ARTES_VISUAIS_(UFPB_J.P._-_UFPE)> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12183> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WITH VISUALITY AS ITS AXIS, I PRESENT AN ARTISTIC PROJECT EQUIVALENT TO THE DISSERTATION, FROM THE LINE OF RESEARCH ON CREATIVE PROCESSES OF VISUAL ARTS. IN ORDER TO HIGHLIGHT THE CYCLICAL CHARACTER OF LIFE,I SOUGHT INSPIRATION FROM THE BOOK AVALOVARA AND THE FILM BEFORE THE RAIN TO GUIDE THE VISUAL NARRATIVES PRESENTED HERE. DURING THE RESEARCH, WHILE I TRIED TO DEVELOP MY OWN ARTISTIC, CREATIVE AND AESTHETIC THINKING, I ALSO DEVELOPED A REFLECTION, USING THE ANALOGICAL METHODOLOGY, ON THE CREA"@pt ;
