<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12795> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECTIVE IS TO REPORT AND DESCRIBE THE METASTATIC LESIONS OBSERVED IN IDENTIFIED SKELETONS BELONGING TO THE COLLECTION OF THE CENTER FOR STUDIES IN FORENSIC ANTHROPOLOGY, FACULTY OF DENTISTRY, UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO (CEAF/FOP/UPE), WHOSE DEATHS WERE CAUSED BY COMPLICATIONS RESULTING FROM BREAST CANCER, TO PROVIDE INFORMATION AND EVIDENCE THAT CAN BE USED TO ESTABLISH DIFFERENTIAL DIAGNOSES IN CASES OF HUMAN IDENTIFICATION. IN SEARCH OF THE LABORATORY'S DATABASE, THE ANALYSIS OF THE BONES "@pt ;
