<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12801> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO ANALYZE MORPHOSCOPIC DATA TO ESTIMATE POPULATION AFFINITY IN BRAZILIAN HUMAN DRY CRANIA. THIS OBSERVATIONAL RESEARCH WAS CARRIED OUT AT THE CENTER FOR FORENSIC ANTHROPOLOGY STUDIES AT THE FACULTY OF DENTISTRY OF THE UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO (CEAF/FOP/UPE), AT THE LABORATORY OF FORENSIC ANTHROPOLOGY AND OSTEOLOGY AT THE FEDERAL UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO (LAOF/UFPE) AND THE IDENTIFICATION LABORATORY AND FORENSIC OSTEOLOGY (LIHOF) AT UFPE. CONSIDERING THE THREE OSTEOLOGICA"@pt ;
