<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12803> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE APPLICATION \"FOOT HEIGHT\" WAS DEVELOPED TO ASSIST THE WORK OF THE CRIMINAL INVESTIGATION. THINKING OF CONTRIBUTING EVEN MORE TO SOCIETY, IT WAS OBSERVED THAT IT WAS IMPORTANT TO ADD A MORE PRACTICAL FUNCTION THAT WOULD FACILITATE THE ACQUISITION AND CALCULATION OF PLANTAR MEASUREMENTS. THEREFORE, THE MAIN OBJECTIVE OF THIS RESEARCH WAS TO IMPLEMENT THE SCANNING FUNCTION IN THE APP. THE METHODOLOGY EMPLOYED FOR THIS PURPOSE INVOLVED SELECTING PRODUCTS TO ASSEMBLE, COLLECTING DATA, STRUCTURING"@pt ;
