<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12804> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH AIMED TO EVALUATE THE OCCURRENCE OF OSTEOARTHRITIS (OA) IN IDENTIFIED HUMAN SKELETONS FROM AN OSTEOLOGICAL COLLECTION IN NORTHEAST BRAZIL, CHECKING THE MOST AFFECTED AGE AND SEX GROUPS AND THE BONE SEGMENTS MOST AFFECTED BY THE PATHOLOGY. THE RESEARCH WAS CARRIED OUT AT THE CENTER FOR STUDIES IN FORENSIC ANTHROPOLOGY, FACULTY OF ODONTOLOGY, UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO (CEAF/FOP/UPE). MACROSCOPIC EXAMINATIONS WERE PERFORMED ON ALL SKELETONS OF BOTH SEXES AND WITH A MINIMUM AGE OF 60 YE"@pt ;
