<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12827> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN OUR LEGISLATION, CHILDREN AND ADOLESCENTS UNDER THE AGE OF EIGHTEEN HAVE SPECIAL CRIMINAL PROTECTION, PURSUANT TO ART. 228 OF THE FEDERAL CONSTITUTION. THIS SPECIAL RESPONSIBILITY WAS INSERTED IN THE NATIONAL LEGISLATION THROUGH A NEW BRANCH OF BRAZILIAN LAW, WHICH PRESENTS ITSELF AS THE LAW OF CHILDREN AND ADOLESCENTS, CREATED BY LAW 8.069/90, WHICH HAS AS ITS FORMAL SOURCES THE DOCTRINE OF INTEGRAL PROTECTION, EMBODIED IN INTERNATIONAL LAW.  UNITED NATIONS CONVENTION. WITH THIS ADVENT, IT "@pt ;
