<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12829> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECTIVE OF THE PRESENT WORK IS TO ANALYZE THE PRESENT WORK RELATIONSHIPS ARISING FROM THE MODEL CALLED UBERIZATION, HIGHLIGHTING FACTUAL ASPECTS THAT FORESAW THIS TYPE OF SITUATION CURRENTLY EXPERIENCED, IN A PRISM OF CONSTITUTIONAL TEMPORAL EVOLUTION INITIALLY. INITIALLY, THE BASES OF EVOLUTION FROM THE LIBERAL TO THE SOCIAL STATE AND THE ENTIRE HISTORICAL AND LEGAL DEVELOPMENT. AFTER THE NEOLIBERAL CONCEPTION AND ITS DEVELOPMENT IN LABOR RELATIONS. THE QUALITATIVE METHOD WAS USED, IN WHI"@pt ;
