<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12832> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "USING THE INDUCTIVE METHOD OF REASONING, THE RESEARCH ANALYSES RANSOMWARE ATTACKS IN THE FACE OF BRAZILIAN CRIMINAL LAW, WITH THE SCOPE OF GUIDING LEGISLATIVE MEASURES TO CRIMINALIZE CYBERCRIMES. BY MEANS OF NATIONAL AND FOREIGN BIBLIOGRAPHICAL REVIEW OVER THIS MATTER, THE STUDY BEGINS WITH DEFINITION, CLASSIFICATION AND CRIMINALIZATION OF CYBERCRIME. THEN, ANALYSES THE CONCEPT AND HISTORICAL EVOLUTION OF RANSOMWARE. LASTLY, EXAMINES IF AND WHICH CRIMINAL OFFENSES ARE COMMITTED AS A RESULT OF TH"@pt ;
