<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12833> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS DISSERTATION BRINGS AN ANALYSIS OF THE POSSIBILITY OF APPLYING THE INSTITUTE OF CRIMINAL DETRACTION WHEN COMPLYING WITH THE PRECAUTIONARY MEASURES OTHER THAN IMPRISONMENT PROVIDED FOR IN THE CODE OF CRIMINAL PROCEDURE. PENAL DETRACTION IS PROVIDED FOR IN ARTICLE 42 OF THE PENAL CODE, WHICH ESTABLISHES THAT THERE WILL BE A DISCOUNT ON THE SENTENCE OF PROVISIONAL PRISON TIME, IN BRAZIL AND ABROAD, ADMINISTRATIVE ARREST OR HOSPITALIZATION. IT SO HAPPENS THAT, WITH THE ENACTMENT OF LAW N.O 12.4"@pt ;
