<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12838> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY AIMS TO ADDRESS THE PURPOSE OF THE PENALTY IN CRIMINAL ENFORCEMENT, WITHIN THE BRAZILIAN REALITY. CURRENTLY, MOST OF THE NATIONAL DOCTRINE, AS WELL AS THE CASE LAW OF THE STF, HAS DEFENDED THAT THE PENALTY HAS A POLY-FUNCTIONAL CHARACTER, I.E., THAT IT HAS THREE CHARACTERS: RETRIBUTIVE, PREVENTIVE AND RE- SOCIALIZING. AN ANALYSIS OF THE DOCTRINE SHOWS THAT THERE IS NO CONSENSUS AS TO WHAT THE RESOCIALIZATION OF THE OFFENDER MEANS. FOR THE ADVOCATES OF THE MAXIMUM RESOCIALIZING PROGRAM"@pt ;
