<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12845> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE RESEARCH SEEKS TO INVESTIGATE WHETHER THERE WOULD BE, IN BRAZILIAN BIOLAW, A CONSTITUTIONALLY GUARANTEED FUNDAMENTAL RIGHT TO ASSISTED HUMAN REPRODUCTION AND WHAT ELEMENTS ARE NECESSARY FOR THE CONSTRUCTION OF A SPECIFIC LEGISLATION ON THE ISSUE. THE METHODOLOGY USED WAS DEDUCTIVE-QUALITATIVE, THROUGH THE TECHNIQUE OF BIBLIOGRAPHIC RESEARCH IN BOOKS, THESES, DISSERTATIONS, SCIENTIFIC ARTICLES, RESOLUTIONS, CONSTITUTIONAL AND INFRA-CONSTITUTIONAL LEGISLATION AND RESEARCH ON BILLS. IT STARTS F"@pt ;
