<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12851> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK SEEKS TO ANALYZE, FROM A THEORETICAL-LEGAL PERSPECTIVE, THE NATIONAL TAX SYSTEM, CONSIDERING, MAINLY, THE PANDEMIC PERIOD AND THE FUNDAMENTAL RIGHTS GUARANTEED BY THE FEDERAL CONSTITUTION, IN ORDER TO IDENTIFY THE MEASURES THAT WERE TAKEN IN THE LAST TWO YEARS, WITH THE ADVENT OF THE PANDEMIC. OF THE VIRUS KNOWN AS COVID-19, AND THE POSSIBLE WAYS TO ACHIEVE FISCAL JUSTICE. THE MATTER IS GAINING MORE AND MORE IMPORTANCE, GIVEN THAT PUBLIC SPENDING HAS GROWN TOO MUCH WITH THE NEED"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "04FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "OS DIREITOS FUNDAMENTAIS COMO UMA LIMITAÇÃO AO PODER DE TRIBUTAR: UMA ANÁLISE DO SISTEMA TRIBUTÁRIO NACIONAL EM PERÍODO PANDÊMICO A LUZ DO PRINCÍPIO DA CAPACIDADE CONTRIBUTIVA"@pt ;
