    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/DIREITO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/12856> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE FINANCIALIZATION OF HOUSING REFERS TO THE GROWING ROLE OF FINANCIAL MARKETS AND CORPORATIONS IN THE REAL ESTATE SEGMENT. GENERALLY SPEAKING, THE INCREASING PARTICIPATION OF FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS IN THE REAL ESTATE MARKET HAS A SIGNIFICANT IMPACT ON PEOPLE ´S LIVES, BE IT THROUGH A DISCRIMINATORY EFFECT ON LOW-INCOME FAMILIES DUE TO INACCESSIBILITY TO HOUSING, OR WHEN THEIR RIGHTS TO ADEQUATE HOUSING ARE IMPAIRED. THE FINANCIALIZATION OF HOUSING IS NOT ALWAYS CAST UNDER A POSITIVE LIGHT WHEN"@pt ;
