<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13006> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DURING THE DEVELOPMENT OF BRAZILIAN GEOGRAPHIC THOUGHT, IN ITS MODERN PARADIGM, HE PARTICIPATED IN REPRESENTATIONS ABOUT THE TERRITORY, THE POPULATION AND THE PEOPLES THAT COMPOSE THEM - AS IN THE TERRITORIAL CONFLICTS OF QUILOMBOLA COMMUNITIES. ALTHOUGH MANY RESEARCHES AND PUBLICATIONS ARE BEING CARRIED OUT ON THE TERRITORIAL TENSIONS BETWEEN QUILOMBOLA COMMUNITIES IN BRAZIL, THE DISCUSSION AND RESULTS THAT THESE RESEARCHES HAVE BROUGHT HAVE BEEN LITTLE EXPLORED, THAT IS, ON THE EPISTEMOLOGICAL"@pt ;
