<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13007> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC BROUGHT VISIBILITY TO HOW RELEVANT THE WORK CARRIED OUT BY COURIERS IS, DESPITE BEING PRECARIOUS IN SEVERAL INSTANCES, INCLUDING THE RISK OF ACCIDENTS AND EVEN DEATH, IN SEARCH OF OBTAINING LITTLE REMUNERATION. WE ARE INVESTIGATING THIS ISSUE IN THE LIGHT OF THE CONCEPTS OF DIFFUSION OF INNOVATIONS, ADDING THAT IN THE TERRITORIAL SYSTEM WE FIND OURSELVES IN, THIS PRECARIOUSNESS IS STRUCTURAL AND WOULD CONDITION THE MOST VULNERABLE USERS TO SUBMIT TO THIS PRECARIOUS RELATION"@pt ;
