    capes:hasAbstract "THE ADVANCEMENT OF TECHNOLOGY HAS BEEN ENTERING THE SOCIETY SCENARIO OVER THE YEARS TO PROVIDE FACILITIES, ESPECIALLY IN THE SOCIAL ECONOMIC SPHERE. IN 2020, WITH THE UNEXPECTED ARRIVAL OF THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC, THE DIGITAL AGE HAS ACCELERATED CONSIDERABLY, IN VIEW OF THE MEASURES THAT HAVE BEEN ADOPTED WORLDWIDE, SUCH AS SOCIAL DISTANCING AND THE NEW FORMS OF COEXISTENCE AND ADAPTATIONS IMPOSED BY THE AUTHORITIES. GOVERNMENT AGENCIES, FOR EXAMPLE, THE INTENSIFICATION OF HOME OFFICE WORK. THE CH"@pt ;
