<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13036> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS DISSERTATION AIMS TO ANALYZE THE INFLUENCE OF THE DEGREE OF PERSONAL ENVIRONMENTAL AWARENESS OF THE SERVERS, IN THE ADOPTION OF EFFECTIVE MEASURES OF THE SELECTIVE COLLECTION OF THE FORUM DESEMBARGADOR HENRIQUE CAPITULINO, OF JABOATÃO DOS GUARARAPES PERNAMUCO. THE ANALYSIS WAS CARRIED OUT USING A QUESTIONNAIRE PREPARED FROM STUDIES OF I) ENVIRONMENTAL AWARENESS (CA) (ROBERTS; BACON, 1997; VERGRAGT ET AL., 2016; SEVERO ET AL., 2018; 2019;) II) SUSTAINABLE BEHAVIOR (CS) (SEVERO; GUIMARÃES; DE"@pt ;
