    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/GESTÃO_EMPRESARIAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13037> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECT OF STUDY OF THIS WORK IS THE PROPOSITION OF A TRAINING MODEL APPLIED TO PUBLIC SERVANTS IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO, BASED ON THE OBSERVATION AND QUESTIONING OF THE TRAINING MODELS THAT APPLIED TO WORKERS, ESPECIALLY THOSE ALLOCATED IN A MUNICIPALITY IN THE INTERIOR OF THE STATE. THE INTEREST WAS TO IDENTIFY THE POTENTIAL OF EMOTIONAL INTELLIGENCE AS AN ESSENTIAL CHARACTERISTIC OF GOOD LEADERSHIP. OUR MAIN OBJECTIVE, THEREFORE, WAS TO PROPOSE TRAINING TO LEVERAGE THE EMOTIONAL INTELLIG"@pt ;
