<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13041> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CUSTOMER SATISFACTION IN ANY SEGMENT IMPACTS SALES, MARKET GAIN AND, CONSEQUENTLY, BUSINESS PROFITABILITY. IN THE ELECTRICITY DISTRIBUTION SECTOR (DEE) THERE ARE FORMAL TOOLS THAT ASSESS CUSTOMER SATISFACTION, SUCH AS THE IASC SATISFACTION SURVEY. WITHIN A MARKET THAT IS STILL MOSTLY MONOPOLISTIC, OTHER PROCESSES THAT BRING GREATER PROFITABILITY PREVAIL IN THE FACE OF CUSTOMER FOCUS, SUCH AS THOSE TO COMBAT LOSSES AND DEFAULT, SINCE WITH THESE INDICES WORSE THAN THE REGULATORY TARGETS, THE COMPA"@pt ;
