<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13388> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE STUDY OF CLIMATIC CONDITIONS AND THE CHANGES ASSOCIATED WITH THEM ARE OF GREAT IMPORTANCE FOR A SOCIETY. MAINLY BECAUSE THEY PRESENT GREAT IMPLICATIONS IN EVERYDAY LIFE, AS IN THE CASE OF PLUVIOMETRIC VARIATIONS THAT CAN INTERFERE, FROM ECONOMIC, ENVIRONMENTAL, AND SOCIAL ISSUES. THUS, THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY IS TO PREDICT RAINFALL IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF VITÓRIA DE SANTO ANTÃO - PE, FOR THE NEXT FOUR YEARS. THE ANALYZED DATA ARE PLUVIOMETRIC RECORDS OF FOUR MONITORING STATIONS (65, 541, "@pt ;
