<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13389> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AEOLIAN ENERGY IS A RENEWABLE SOURCE OF GREAT STRATEGIC POTENTIAL FOR THE COUNTRY. ITS EXPLOITATION FOSTERS LOCAL DEVELOPMENT THROUGH TECHNICAL MOVEMENTS, TRANSPORTATION, EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITIES AND ENERGY GENERATION. HOWEVER, THERE ARE VAST BRAZILIAN AREAS TO BE EXPLORED AND THEIR WIND REGIMES UNNAMED. IN THIS SCENARIO, THE CITY OF PETROLINA / PE WAS CHOSEN TO ANALYZE THE WIND POTENTIAL AND THE REGIME OF THE WIND SPEED DYNAMICS ON MULTIPLE SCENARIOS: TIME, MONTH AND STATION BETWEEN THE YEARS 2"@pt ;
