<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13468> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PEREIRA, V. M. A. O. THE INFLUENCE OF SPIRITUALITY IN CONVIVING PEOPLE WITH HIV/AIDS. 2017. 78P. . DISSERTAÇÃO (MESTRADO) - FACULDADE DE ENFERMAGEM NOSSA SENHORA AS GRAÇAS, UNIVERSIDADE DE PERNAMBUCO / UNIVERSIDADE ESTADUAL DA PARAÍBA, RECIFE, 2017. THIS STUDY AIMED TO UNDERSTAND THE INFLUENCE OF SPIRITUALITY ON LIVING WITH PEOPLE LIVING WITH HIV / AIDS. THE MOTIVATION TO CARRY IT OUT IS DUE TO MY CONCERNS ABOUT THE ACADEMIC AND PERSONAL EXPERIENCES THAT I HAVE EXPERIENCED AFTER JOINING THE MAST"@pt ;
