    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ENFERMAGEM_-_FESP-UPE_-_UEPB> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13471> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BASTOS, W. D. G. ANALISYS OF SAFETY IN PREPARATION AND MEDICATION ADMINISTRATION ON SENTINEL NETWORK HOSPITALS. 2017. 111 F. DISSERTATION (MASTER DEGREE) FACULDADE DE ENFERMAGEM NOSSA SENHORA AS GRAÇAS, UNIVERSIDADE DE PERNAMBUCO, RECIFE, 2017. INTRODUCTION: THE DRUG THERAPY IS A RESOURCES OF THE MOST USED IN HEALTH CARE WHEN AN ERROR IN THAT PROCESS BECOMES THE USER AN EASY TARGET FOR A SENTINEL EVENT. STUDIES INDICATE THAT MOST MEDICATION ERRORS CAN BE INTERCEPTED IN THE SELECTION, PREPARATION"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "09MAR2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DA SEGURANÇA NO PREPARO E NA ADMINISTRAÇÃO DE MEDICAMENTOS EM HOSPITAIS DA REDE SENTINELA"@pt ;
