<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13621> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT DISSERTATION IS THE RESULT OF A RESEARCH THAT HAS AS ITS MAIN OBJECTIVE: TO UNDERSTAND THE ROLE OF THE INSTITUTIONAL TEACHING INITIATION SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM - PIBID IN THE INITIAL FORMATION OF GEOGRAPHY TEACHERS FOR BASIC EDUCATION IN CONTEMPORARY TIMES. THE RESEARCH STARTS FROM THE FOLLOWING PROBLEM: HOW THE PIBID-SUBPROJECT/INTERDISCIPLINARY, MATA NORTE CAMPUS, UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO - UPE CONTRIBUTED TO THE IMPROVEMENT OF THE INITIATION TO TEACHING OF GRADUATES OF THE GEOGRAPHY "@pt ;
