<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13749> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CANCER IS ONE OF THE LEADING CAUSES OF DEATH WORLDWIDE. IN RECENT YEARS, IMPROVEMENTS IN TREATMENT HAVE BEEN MADE, LEADING TO A DROP OF MORE THAN 20% IN THE MORTALITY RATE OF THIS DISEASE, HOWEVER, CANCER IS STILL A SERIOUS PROBLEM. THUS, RESEARCH ON THIS AXIS IS ESSENTIAL TO REDUCE DEATH DUE TO CANCER. A TOTAL OF 15 HYBRID COMPOUNDS CONTAINING PORTIONS OF PYRIDYL,1,3-THIAZOLE AND THIOSEMICARBAZONES WERE TESTED FOR THEIR ANTICANCER POTENTIAL, AND A PHARMACOLOGICAL STUDY OF THEIR ANTITUMOR PROPER"@pt ;
