<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13753> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DOMESTIC ANIMALS ARE INCREASINGLY CLOSER TO HUMANS, SHARING ENVIRONMENT, WATER AND FOOD. WITH A PHYSIOLOGY, YOU CAN POSSIBLY DEVELOP THE SAME DISEASES, INCLUDING SUFFERING FROM THE SAME EXPOSURE TO CHEMICAL ELEMENTS AND THEIR HARMFUL EFFECTS. THEREFORE, WE PRESENT THE WORK AS AN OBJECTIVE TO CARRY OUT A BIOMONITORING OF CHEMICAL ELEMENTS USING A NON-INVASIVE MATRIX (HAIR), VERIFYING THE POSSIBLE RELATIONSHIP WITH THE WEAKENED IMMUNE SYSTEM IN MADE ANIMALS. TO CARRY OUT THE COLLECTIONS, THEY WERE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "14SEP2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "BIOMONITORAÇÃO DE ELEMENTOS QUÍMICOS DE MATRIZ NÃO INVASIVA (PELOS) APLICADA À SAÚDE DE ANIMAIS DOMÉSTICOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
