<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13762> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BRAZILIAN SEMIARID REGION IS FACING SERIOUS PROBLEMS OF SOIL DEGRADATION. THE REPLACEMENTOF NATIVE VEGETATION OF THE CAATINGA BY PASTURES IN AN INAPPROPRIATE WAY, CAUSES A DECREASE IN CARBON SEQUESTRATION AND STORAGE, INCREASES SOIL COMPACTION, DECREASES THE CAPACITY OF THE SOIL TO STOREAND CONDUCT WATER TO ITS INTERIOR, DECREASES BIODIVERSITY AND ALTERS THE SOIL MICROBIAL COMMUNITY. AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS HAVE BEEN SEEN AS A CONSERVATION TECHNIQUE CAPABLE OF MITIGATING SOIL DEGRADATION BECAUS"@pt ;
