<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13763> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS PROJECT WAS CARRIED OUT AT THE BELO JARDIM CAMPUS OF THE FEDERAL INSTITUTE OF PERNAMBUCO TO EVALUATE THE BIOLOGICAL NITROGEN FIXATION (BNF) OF SORGHUM AND CONSORTIATED LEGUME SPECIES AND THE TRANSFER OF N FROM THE LEGUMES TO THE SORGHUM, DURING TWO SORGHUM CULTIVATION CYCLES. THE EFFECTS OF MOLYBDENUM APPLICATION WERE ALSO STUDIED. THE EXPERIMENT CONSISTED OF A FACTORIAL OF TWO MOLYBDENUM DOSES (0 AND 1.6 KG HA-1) AND FIVE CROPPING SYSTEMS: 1) SINGLE CROP OF SORGHUM; 2, 3 AND 4) INTERCROPPI"@pt ;
