<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13766> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ACCORDING TO THE INTERNATIONAL RECOMMENDATION, THE MINIMUM FILTRATION OF IPE FOR HOSPITAL AEROSOL GENERATOR ENVIRONMENTS MUST ACHIEVE 95% FOR SOLID PARTICLES AND WATER DERIVATIVES. NEVERTHELESS, WITH THE PANDEMIC, THE SCARCITY OF THESE DEVICES HAS RESULTED IN THE LIBERATION FOR REUTILIZING, PROVIDED THAT THE IPES SUSTAIN THEIR FILTRATION CAPABILITY. IN THIS WORK, THE INTEGRITY AND FUNCTIONALITY OF PFF2 RESPIRATORY PROTECTORS AFTER REUTILIZING IN HOSPITAL ENVIRONMENT BY MEANS OF MICROSCOPIC EVALU"@pt ;
