<http://example.com/capes#thesis/13779> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AUTOLOGOUS BONE GRAFT IS CONSIDERED THE BEST OPTION AMONG THE OTHER TYPES, AS IT USES THE PATIENT'S OWN BONE, BEING CONSIDERED THE GOLD STANDARD FOR REGENERATION, SAFETY AND EFFICACY. HOWEVER, IT HAS LIMITATIONS RELATED TO THE AMOUNT OF MATERIAL AVAILABLE FOR GRAFTING. HYDROXYAPATITE HAS BEEN INCREASINGLY USED IN MEDICINE AND DENTISTRY AS AN OPTION FOR BEING A BIOMATERIAL THAT INDUCES OSTEOGENESIS, A RELEVANT CHARACTERISTIC FOR THE REPLACEMENT OF AUTOLOGOUS BONES. THIS WORK INTENDS TO OBTAIN"@pt ;
