<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14058> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "GIVEN THE CURRENT SCENARIO OF EMERGENCY AND RE-EMERGENCE OF VIRAL INFECTIOUS DISEASES, SUCH AS THE EMERGENCE OF COVID-19 AND THE POSSIBILITY OF NEW OUTBREAKS OF ZIKA VIRUS (ZIKV), THE SEARCH FOR STRATEGIES CAPABLE OF CONTAINING THE SPREAD OF THESE INFECTIONS BECOMES A GLOBAL PRIORITY. OF PUBLIC HEALTH. THE YEAST SURFACE DISPLAY OF RECOMBINANT PROTEINS USING SACCHAROMYCES CEREVISIAE HAS BEEN POINTED OUT AS A ALTERNATIVE TOOL FOR FACING EMERGING EPIDEMICS THROUGH THE DEVELOPMENT OF IMMUNOREAGENTS "@pt ;
