<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14473> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "UNTREATED DENTAL CARIES IN CHILDREN REMAINS A PUBLIC HEALTH CONCERN IN DISADVANTAGED COMMUNITIES. TO REDUCE THE PREVALENCE OF DENTAL CARIES, PREVENTION AND ORAL HEALTH PROMOTION STRATEGIES HAVE BEEN WIDELY STUDIED. TO IMPROVE THE ACCESS TO ORAL HEALTH CARE AND THE QUALITY OF LIFE OF THESE POPULATIONS, THE USE OF SIMPLE AND LOW-COST TECHNOLOGIES ARE REQUIRED. THE AIM OF THIS DOUBLE-BLIND RANDOMIZED CONTROLLED TRIAL WAS TO EVALUATE THE EFFECTIVENESS OF A NEW ANTICARIES AGENT, NANO SILVER FLUORIDE "@pt ;
