<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14488> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DENTAL CARIES IS STILL A PROBLEM IN SOME INDIVIDUALS EVEN IN LOW CARIES PREVALENCE POPULATION. AS THE PREVALENCE IS SIGNIFICANTLY HIGHER FOR CHILDREN WHO COME FROM LOWER SOCIAL-ECONOMIC CLASSES OR LOWER INCOME FAMILIES, CONVENTIONAL DENTAL CARE IS OFTEN EITHER UNAVAILABLE OR UNAFFORDABLE FOR THEM. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS SYSTEMATIC REVIEW WAS TO INVESTIGATE THE PREVENTED FRACTION OF BOTH SILVER DIAMINE FLUORIDE AND FLUORIDE SEALANTS AND SUMMARIZE THE AVAILABLE CLINICAL EVIDENCE REGARDING THE EFFIC"@pt ;
