<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14490> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ABSTRACT THIS STUDY EVALUATED THE INFLUENCE OF THE VARIATION OF TIME AND DISTANCE IN THE CURING CYCLE AND YOUR EFFECT ON LINEAR CONTRACTION SUREFIL SDR RESINS FREE BULK FILL (DENTSPLY) AND BULK FILL RESTORATIVE AURA (SDI). FOR THE EVALUATION OF LINEAR POLYMERIZATION CONTRACTION FREE, WAS MADE A CIRCULAR METAL MOLD WITH INNER DIAMETER OF 6 MM AND HEIGHT OF 4 MM. THE RESINS WERE PHOTOPOLYMERIZED ACCORDING TO THE DIVISION OF GROUPS (WITH DISTANCES OF 0 CM AND 1 CM) WITH CALIBRATED POWER 1,200 MW/CM"@pt ;
