<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14829> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ABSTRACT VITAMIN LEVELS OF LIPID PROFILE IN PATIENTS UNDERGOING BARIATRIC SURGERY INTRODUCTION: BRAZIL IS ALREADY THE GLOBAL LEADER IN THE NUMBER OF BARIATRIC SURGERIES IN THE WORLD, BEING CONSIDERED THE MOST EFFECTIVE THERAPY FOR WEIGHT LOSS IN OBESE PATIENTS, BUT IT IS ASSOCIATED WITH A SERIES OF VITAMIN, MINERAL AND METABOLIC DEFICIENCIES. OBJECTIVE: TO EVALUATE THE ASSOCIATION OF VITAMIN D LEVELS WITH LIPID PROFILE AND HEPATIC STEATOSIS IN OBESE PATIENTS UNDERGOING BARIATRIC SURGERY. METHODO"@pt ;
