<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14914> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HAVE POPULIST ATTACKS ON JOURNALISTS REPRESENTED A FORM OF PRESS CENSORSHIP IN BRAZIL SINCE 2019? THE PRESENT DISSERTATION SEEKS TO ANSWER THIS RESEARCH QUESTION, THROUGH THE INVESTIGATION OF THE ATTACKS ON THE PRESS, PROMOTED BY THE GOVERNMENT OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE REPUBLIC JAIR BOLSONARO SINCE ITS INAUGURATION IN 2019, VERIFYING IF THIS POSTURE HAS RESULTED IN THE WEAKENING OF THE FREEDOM OF THE PRESS AND REPRESENTED A WAY TO CREATE BARRIERS AND CENSOR OPPONENTS OF THE GOVERNMENT. THE CENTRA"@pt ;
