<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14919> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE ADVANCE OF INFORMATION AND COMMUNICATION (S) TECHNOLOGY (ICT) HAS RESULTED IN RISING UNEASINESS AMONG THE POPULATION REGARDING EFFECTIVE PROTECTION OF THEIR PERSONAL DATA, SINCE VIOLATIONS OF THIS NATURE COULD PUT CIVIL LIBERTIES AT RISK ALONG WITH DEMOCRACY ITSELF. A NEW GLOBAL ARCHITECTURE WAS SCULPTURED, AND SOCIETY IS FACING A CAPITALIZATION OF DATA THAT HAS CONTINUOUSLY APPROPRIATED SUCCESSIVE LAYERS OF HUMAN LIFE. CONSIDERING THIS SCENARIO, LEGAL SCIENCE IS INVITED TO STEP UP AND TRY T"@pt ;
