<http://example.com/capes#thesis/14947> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HAVING REACHED THE 21ST CENTURY, LATIN AMERICAN INDIGENOUS PEOPLES CONTINUE TO BE THREATENED, HARASSED, AND LOOTED. ASSIMILATIONISM, GENOCIDES, AND ETHNOCIDES AIMED TO TURN INDIGENOUS PEOPLES INTO SLAVES. WHETHER FROM A CULTURE FOREIGN TO THEIR ANCESTRY, OR FURTHER AHEAD, FROM THE SHACKLES OF CAPITAL. AS THE GREATEST OF THE TASKMASTERS, IT IS CONSIDERED THE FIGURE OF THE MODERN STATE, EUROCENTRIC, STANDARDIZING, UNIVOCAL, AND UNISON. AVERSE TO DIFFERENCE, AN INSTITUTIONAL, INDIVIDUALISTIC, MATER"@pt ;
