<http://example.com/capes#thesis/16256> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AYAHUASCA IS A PSYCHOACTIVE BEVERAGE THAT HAS BEEN USED FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS TO ALTER THE I OR SELF TOWARD MYSTICAL STATES. SELF-AWARENESS IS THE COGNITIVE PROCESS IN WHICH THE I BECOMES THE OBJECT OF ATTENTION, AND SELF-CONSCIOUSNESS IS A STABLE TRAIT REGARDING THIS PROCESS. MYSTICAL EXPERIENCES ARE INTENSE, MEANINGFUL, AND TRANSIENT MODIFICATIONS OF THE SELF. THEY ARE COMMONLY REPORTED BY AYAHUASCA USERS AND ARE ESSENTIAL TO UNDERSTANDING THE BREW'S LASTING COGNITIVE EFFECTS. THIS THESIS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "19DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
