<http://example.com/capes#thesis/16259> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO INVESTIGATE HOW AN ELDERLY PERSON'S IMAGINATIVE PROCESSES DEVELOP ABOUT LIFE AFTER EXPERIENCING THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC. THE ELDERLY MAKE UP ONE OF THE MAIN RISK GROUPS FOR WORSENING AND DEATH DUE TO THE RESPIRATORY INFECTION CAUSED BY THE CORONAVIRUS, IN VIEW OF THIS, THERE WAS AN IMPERATIVE FOR RESEARCH AND STRATEGIES FOR THE CARE AND PREVENTION OF THE PHYSICAL AND MENTAL HEALTH OF THIS POPULATION. THE ELDERLY MAKE UP ONE OF THE MAIN RISK GROUPS FOR WORSENING AND DEA"@pt ;
