<http://example.com/capes#thesis/16975> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS SEEKS TO UNDERSTAND THE EFFECT OF OPERATION CAR WASH ON THE 2018 PARLIAMENTARY ELECTION. THIS WORK AIMS TO HIGHLIGHT WHETHER CANDIDATES INVOLVED IN THE OPERATION CAR WASH INVESTIGATION AND ITS DEVELOPMENTS WERE AFFECTED ELECTORALLY BY THE MEASURES ADOPTED BY THE FEDERAL POLICE OPERATION, AND TO WHAT EXTENT. THE HYPOTHESIS CONSIDERED HERE IS THAT, IN THE 2018 ELECTORAL PROCESS, LAVA JATO NEGATIVELY AFFECTED THE PERFORMANCE OF FEDERAL DEPUTIES INVESTIGATED BY THE OPERATION. THIS HYPOTH"@pt ;
