<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17127> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "LEISHMANIASIS IS AN IMPORTANT PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM IN AT LEAST 88 COUNTRIES, REPRESENTING AN IMPORTANT CAUSE OF MORBIDITY AND MORTALITY IN BRAZIL TO HUMANS AND DOGS. THE IMMUNOSENSORS ARE BIOANALYTICAL DEVICES THAT CONVERT ELECTRICAL SIGNAL IN RESPONSE TO THE ANTIGEN-ANTIBODY INTERACTION. COMPARED TO CONVENTIONAL SEROLOGICAL TECHNIQUES, THE DEVICES HAVE THE ADVANTAGE OF CONVENIENCE, THE POSSIBLE PORTABILITY, LOWER COST AND ANALYSIS TIME. IN THIS PROJECT, WE USE THE CYCLIC VOLTAMMETRY AND SQUARE"@pt ;
