<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17197> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CONTAMINATION BY PETROLEUM AND ITS BY-PRODUCTS CAUSES SERIOUS DAMAGE, WHICH HAS AWAKENED GREAT ATTENTION TO THE DEVELOPMENT AND APPLICATION OF INNOVATIVE TECHNOLOGIES FOR THE REMOVAL OF THESE CONTAMINANTS. IN THIS SENSE, THIS WORK AIMED TO PRODUCE A BIOSURFACTANT OF CANDIDA TROPICALIS UCP0996 FROM INDUSTRIAL RESIDUES AS SUBSTRATES FOR APPLICATION AS A REMEDIATION AGENT. BIOSURFACTANT PRODUCTION OPTIMIZATION WAS EVALUATED FOR THE INFLUENCE OF THE VARIABLES CONCENTRATIONS OF MOLASSES, CORN STEEP L"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PRODUÇÃO, CARACTERIZAÇÃO E APLICAÇÃO DE BIOSSURFACTANTE COMO AGENTE DE REMEDIAÇÃO EM AMBIENTE MARINHO"@pt ;
