<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17198> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CAATINGA IS A BIOME NOT YET EXPLORED AS REGARDS THE MICROBIAL BIODIVERSITY OF THE SOIL. DUE TO ITS PECULIARITY OF CLIMATE, RELIEF AND ECOSYSTEM REPRESENTS A GREAT FIELD FOR PROSPECTING CONSIDERING THAT ADAPTED MICROORGANISMS CAN PRESENT CHARACTERISTICS OF INDUSTRIAL APPLICATION. MOREOVER, IT IS OF BIOTECHNOLOGICAL INTEREST THE IMPLEMENTATION OF ECOLOGICALLY CORRECT PROCESSES THAT USE LOW COST SUBSTRATES IN OBTAIN PRODUCTS WITH HIGH ADDED VALUE. DEVELOPMENT OF NEW PRODUCTS MAY BE ASSOCIATED WITH "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "20FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PRODUÇÃO DE AROMAS NATURAIS POR LEVEDURAS NATIVAS DO SOLO DA CAATINGA UTILIZANDO RESÍDUOS AGROINDUSTRIAIS"@pt ;
