<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17202> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HYMENAEA COURBARIL VAR. COURBARIL IS A BRAZILIAN TREE BELONGING TO THE FAMILY FABACEAE AND SUBFAMILY CAESALPINIACEAE, POPULARLY KNOWN AS JATOBÁ. RECENTLY, XYLOGLUCAN (X), THE POLYSACCHARIDE PRESENT IN ITS SEEDS, HAS BECOME A FOCUS OF INTEREST FOR APPLICATION IN THE AREA OF FOOD BIOTECHNOLOGY DUE TO ITS WATER SOLUBILITY, NON-TOXICITY AND ABILITY TO FORM VISCOUS SOLUTIONS. IN THIS WAY, IT CAN BE USED IN THE FOOD INDUSTRY TO FORM MICROSTRUCTURED MATERIALS FOR THE DEVELOPMENT OF RELEASE SYSTEMS. IN "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "18DEC2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PRODUÇÃO DE MICROESTRUTURADOS DE XILOGLUCANA DAS SEMENTES DE JATOBÁ (HYMENAEA COURBARIL VAR. COURBARIL) E SUA APLICAÇÃO NA ÁREA ALIMENTAR"@pt ;
