<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17330> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THIS WORK, WE APPROACH THE PREPARATION AND CHARACTERIZATION OF NANOSTRUCTURED MATERIALS AND THEIR APPLICATION IN DIFFERENT AREAS, SUCH AS CONTAMINANT REMOVAL, DNA EXTRACTION AND PURIFICATION, SUPERCAPACITOR, AND SENSING OF THE LEISHMANIA PATHOGEN. INITIALLY, WE SYNTHESIZED THE MAGNETIC NANOCOMPOSITE (MNC) OF IRON OXIDE/CHITOSAN/POLYANILINE (G-FE2O3/CHI/PANI), WHICH WAS PROPERLY CHARACTERIZED BY FOURIER TRANSFORM INFRARED SPECTROSCOPY (FTIR), THERMOGRAVIMETRIC ANALYSIS (TGA), MAGNETIZATION CUR"@pt ;
