<http://example.com/capes#thesis/17339> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HEREIN, IN THIS WORK, IT IS SHOWN THE SYNTHESIS AND STRUCTURAL CHARACTERIZATION OF HYDROXYFUNCTIONAL SPIROPYRAN-TYPE MOLECULES, FOR THEIR COMPLEXATION WITH CATIONS FROM S-BLOCK (CA) AND D-BLOCK (FE, NI) OF THE PERIODIC TABLE. THROUGH THIS COMPLEXATION, THE STABILITY OF THE MEROCYANINE ISOMER HAS BEEN STUDIED, AND THEN THESE MOLECULES HAVE USED IN THE DEVELOPMENT OF A PHOTOCHROMIC MATERIAL SUPPORTED ON MESOPOROUS SILICA OF THE MCM-48 TYPE. IN THIS RESEARCH, THE SPIROPYRAN MOLECULES HAVE BEEN SYNT"@pt ;
