<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18466> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CANCER, DESPITE ADVANCES IN DIAGNOSTIC AND TREATMENT ISSUES, IS STILL ONE OF THE LEADING CAUSES OF DEATH WORLDWIDE. IN ADDITION, ONE OF THE BIGGEST CURRENT PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEMS IS THE INCREASE IN THE RESISTANCE OF MICROORGANISMS TO ANTIMICROBIALS, ESPECIALLY IN HOSPITAL ENVIRONMENTS. THEREFORE, IT IS NECESSARY TO SYNTHESIZE AND OBTAIN NEW DRUGS THAT ARE EFFECTIVE IN THESE TREATMENTS. IN THE PRESENT WORK, TWO SEMICARBAZONIC DERIVATIVES WERE USED: LS12 AND LS21, IN ADDITION TO FIVE THIOSEMICARBA"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA CITOTOXICIDADE, POTENCIAL ANTIC NCER E ATIVIDADE ANTIMICROBIANA DE DERIVADOS ARIL-SEMICARBAZÔNICOS E ARIL TIOSSEMICARBAZÔNICOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/GEORGE_TORRES_DE_LIMA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18467> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DUE TO AN UNBALANCED DIET AND OTHER LIFESTYLE COMPONENTS, THERE HAS BEEN AN INCREASE IN THE PREVALENCE OF CHRONIC DISEASES, ESPECIALLY THOSE ASSOCIATED WITH METABOLIC DISORDERS SUCH AS THOSE PRESENT IN METABOLIC SYNDROME. METABOLIC SYNDROME IS CHARACTERIZED BY A GROUP OF METABOLIC ABNORMALITIES AND CLINICAL FACTORS SUCH AS INSULIN RESISTANCE, DYSLIPIDEMIA, HYPERTENSION, OBESITY, INCREASED ABDOMINAL CIRCUMFERENCE, WHICH CAN BE INDUCED BY AN UNHEALTHY DIET. GOAT MILK PLAYS AN IMPORTANT ROLE IN HUM"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA SEGURANÇA E DA EFICÁCIA DE UM ALIMENTO FUNCIONAL À BASE DE LEITE CAPRINO FERMENTADO EM UM MODELO EXPERIMENTAL DE SÍNDROME METABÓLICA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/AUREA_MARCELA_DE_SOUZA_PEREIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18468> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "STEMODIA MARITIMA L. IS A SHRUB FOUND THROUGHOUT SOUTH AMERICA AND ON CARIBBEAN ISLANDS, WHERE IT IS POPULARLY USED TO TREAT SEXUALLY TRANSMITTED DISEASES AND EDEMA. IN THE NORTHEAST OF BRAZIL IT IS KNOWN AS MASTRUZ-BRAVO OR MELOSA. STUDIES REVEAL THE PRESENCE OF FLAVONOIDS, STEROIDS AND DITERPENES IN ITS LEAVES AND ROOTS. THESE SECONDARY COMPOUNDS PLAY AN IMPORTANT ROLE IN SEVERAL BIOLOGICAL ACTIVITIES, THEREFORE, THIS WORK IS AIMED AT EVALUATING THE ANTIOXIDANT, ANTIBACTERIAL, AND CYTOTOXI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "26MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DAS ATIVIDADES ANTIOXIDANTE, ANTIBACTERIANA E GASTROPOTETORA DAS FOLHAS DE STEMODIA MARITIMA L."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/RAYANE_SIQUEIRA_DE_SOUSA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18469> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SEARCH FOR NATURAL PRODUCTS WITH ANTIMICROBIAL, ANTI-INFLAMMATORY, AND ANTITUMOR ACTIVITIES IS A RECURRING THEME THAT HAS MADE GREAT ADVANCES TODAY. LAGUNCULARIA RACEMOSA (L.) C.F. GAERTN IS A SPECIES BELONGING TO THE COMBRETACEAE FAMILY THAT PLAYS A RELEVANT ECOLOGICAL ROLE IN THE MANGROVE ECOSYSTEM AND SOME STUDIES REPORT ITS ACTIVITY IN THE INTERACTION AND BIOLOGICAL MONITORING OF SOME MICROORGANISMS. HOWEVER, THIS SPECIES WAS LITTLE STUDIED IN THE PHARMACOLOGICAL, TOXICOLOGICAL, AND PHYT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "18NOV2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DAS ATIVIDADES ANTIOXIDNTE, ANTI-INFLAMATÓRIA E ANTIMICROBIANA DO EXTRATO HIDROALCOÓLICO DAS FOLHAS DE LAGUNCULARIA RACEMOSA (L) C. F. GAERT"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JHONATTA_ALEXANDRE_BRITO_DIAS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18470> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CROTON BLANCHTIANUS (EUPHORBIACEAE) COMMONLY KNOWN AS QUINCE OR QUINCE-BLACK, IS A PLANT SPECIES USED IN FOLK MEDICINE TO MANAGE VARIOUS DISORDERS, SUCH AS DIARRHEA, HEADACHE, GASTROINTESTINAL DISORDERS, RHEUMATISM, FEVER AND INFLAMMATORY PROCESSES. THUS, THIS STUDY AIMED TO EVALUATE THE EXTRACTIVE PROCESSES OF CROTON LEAVES, AS WELL AS TO EVALUATE THE TOXICITY AND ANTIDIABETIC EFFECT IN MICE. A PHYTOCHEMICAL SCREENING AND A 22 FACTORIAL DESIGN WERE CARRIED OUT IN ORDER TO INITIALLY OBTAIN T"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DO EFEITO ANTIDIABÉTICO DO EXTRATO HIDROALCOÓLICO DE FOLHAS DE CROTON BLANCHETIANUS EM CAMUNDONGOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JOSE_ISRAEL_GUERRA_JUNIOR> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18471> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BELONGING TO THE ASTERACEAE FAMILY, TRIDAX PROCUMBENS L. POPULARLY KNOWN AS BULLGRASS HAS PRESENTS LEAVES AND FLOWERS WITH THERAPEUTIC ACTIVITIES. ITS LEAVES ARE USED IN FOLK MEDICINE IN TEAS FOR THE TREATMENT OF HYPERTENSION, INFLAMMATION, ANEMIA, COLDS, HEPATOPATHIES, DIARRHEA, AMONG OTHERS. HOWEVER, IT IS NOTEWORTHY THAT THE SPECIES PRESENTS EXTERNAL MORPHOLOGICAL CHARACTERISTICS SIMILAR TO OTHERS OF THE ASTERACEAE FAMILY GENERATING MISUNDERSTANDINGS IN ITS IDENTIFICATION. BECAUSE OF THIS, ST"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "18NOV2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CARACTERIZAÇÃO ANATÔMICA E HISTOQUÍMICA DOS ÓRGÃOS VEGETATIVOS DE TRIDAX PROCUMBENS L. (ASTERACEAE)"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MIRIAM_TEIXEIRA_ALVES_DAMASCENO_RAMOS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18472> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "EFFLUX PUMPS PRESENT IN STAPHYLOCOCCUS AUREUS IS ONE OF THE MAIN MECHANISMS CAUSING ANTIBIOTIC RESISTANCE. THIS MICROORGANISM IS RESPONSIBLE FOR MANY NOSOCOMIAL INFECTIONS AND DUE TO ITS ABILITY TO CAUSE DISEASE AND EVEN DEATH OF THE HOST, IT IS CONSIDERED A PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM WORLDWIDE. THEREFORE, IT IS NECESSARY TO DEVELOP A DRUG THAT IS EFFECTIVE AGAINST MULTIDRUG-RESISTANT BACTERIA AND HAS FEW SIDE EFFECTS. IN THE PRESENT STUDY, SIX COMPOUNDS DERIVED FROM SEMICARBAZONIC AND THIOSEMICARBAZ"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "14DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DERIVADOS SEMICARBAZÔNICOS E TIOSSEMICARBAZÔNICOS ASSOCIADOS A ANTIBIÓTICOS INIBEM ¿-LACTAMASE E BOMBAS DE EFLUXO EM CEPAS DE STAPHYLOCOCCUS AUREUS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/DEBORA_FEITOSA_MUNIZ> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18473> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE TREATMENT OF INFECTIONS THAT AFFECT THE SKIN IS USUALLY CARRIED OUT WITH ANTIMICROBIAL DRUGS. INAPPROPRIATE PRESCRIBING AND IRRATIONAL USE OF THESE DRUGS CAN RESULT IN BACTERIAL RESISTANCE. STUDIES REPORT THE DEPENDENCE OF IRON UPTAKE (FE3+) FOR THE SURVIVAL OF BACTERIA, AND THUS, AS GALLIUM (GA3+) SHOWS CHEMICAL SIMILARITY TO IRON (III), IT HAS THE ABILITY TO DISRUPT THE BIOLOGICAL PROCESSES OF BACTERIA, REDUCING THE CHANCE OF DEVELOPING RESISTANCE, AS WELL AS HAVING ANTI INFLAMMATORY ACTIV"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "14MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE FORMA FARMACÊUTICA SEMISSÓLIDA BASEADA EM NOVOS COMPOSTOS DE GÁLIO COMO ALTERNATIVA DE UM NOVO CICATRIZANTE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/TAYSA_RENATA_RIBEIRO_TIMOTEO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18474> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "EUGENIA UNIFLORA L. AND CINNAMOMUM VERUM J. PRESL., ARE TWO SPECIES RICH IN FLAVONOIDS, WIDELY USED IN TRADITIONAL MEDICINE. SO THAT THE USE OF THESE AND OTHER MEDICINAL PLANTS CAN BE DONE SAFELY AND EFFECTIVELY, THE QUALITY AND STABILITY OF THESE PLANTS AND THEIR PRODUCTS MUST BE ATTESTED. IN THIS SENSE, AN IMPORTANT TOOL IN THE EVALUATION OF THE STABILITY OF PHARMACEUTICAL PRODUCTS IS THE USE OF STABILITY-INDICATING METHODS. THUS, THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO DEVELOP AND VALIDATE STABILITY-IND"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE MÉTODO INDICATIVO DE ESTABILIDADE DE FLAVONOIDES EM MATRIZES VEGETAIS: EUGENIA UNIFLORA L. E CINNAMOMUM VERUM J. PRESL."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/EWELYN_CINTYA_FELIPE_DOS_SANTOS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18475> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "TERBINAFINE HYDROCHLORIDE (TBF) IS ASSOCIATED WITH A HIGH INCIDENCE OF ADVERSE EVENTS THAT CAN LEAD TO TREATMENT INTERRUPTIONS FOR ONYCHOMYCOSIS. LAPONITE (LAP) IS A LOW-COST SYNTHETIC CLAY MINERAL THAT HAS STOOD OUT AS A VEHICLE FOR THE DEVELOPMENT OF DRUG DELIVERY SYSTEMS. THE OBJECTIVE OF THE PRESENT WORK WAS TO DEVELOP A HYBRID SYSTEM FORMED FROM LAP ASSOCIATED WITH TBF FOR THE CONTROLLED RELEASE OF THIS DRUG. EXPERIMENTAL CONDITIONS FOR THE ADSORPTION OF TBF ON LAP WERE EVALUATED, CONSIDERI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "15MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE UM SISTEMA HÍBRIDO A PARTIR DO ARGILOMINERAL LAPONITA PARA LIBERAÇÃO CONTROLADA DO CLORIDRATO DE TERBINAFINA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/FRANCISCO_DE_ASSIS_SILVEIRA_DE_OLIVEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18476> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ONYCHOMYCOSIS IS A CHRONIC FUNGAL NAIL INFECTION, WITH AN ESTIMATED GLOBAL PREVALENCE OF 5.5% IN THE YEAR OF 2017. THE EFFECTS OF THE INFECTION, WHEN UNTREATED, CAN INCLUDE PAIN, SECONDARY BACTERIAL INFECTIONS, LOW SELF-ESTEEM, AND EMOTIONAL EMBARRASSMENT DUE TO DISFIGUREMENT OF THE AFFECTED NAILS. THE NAIL IS THE MOST RESISTANT BARRIER OF THE NAIL STRUCTURE FOR THE PENETRATION OF DRUGS, DUE TO ITS COMPOSITION AND THE PRESENCE OF MANY DISULFIDE BONDS THAT INTERCONNECT THE KERATIN FIBERS. THIS IS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17JUN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO E AVALIAÇÃO DE DESEMPENHO DE FORMULAÇÕES UNGUEAIS À BASE DE TERBINAFINA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CAMILA_DE_ALMEIDA_PEREZ_PIMENTA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18477> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ONYCHOMYCOSIS IS A CHRONIC FUNGAL NAIL INFECTION, WITH AN ESTIMATED GLOBAL PREVALENCE OF 5.5% IN THE YEAR 2017. THE EFFECTS OF THIS INFECTION, WHEN UNTREATED, CAN INCLUDE PAIN, SECONDARY BACTERIAL INFECTIONS, INABILITY TO WEAR SHOES, LOW SELF-ESTEEM AND EMOTIONAL EMBARRASSMENT DUE TO DISFIGUREMENT OF THE AFFECTED NAILS. THE NAIL IS THE MOST RESISTANT BARRIER OF THE NAIL STRUCTURE FOR THE PENETRATION OF DRUGS, DUE TO ITS COMPOSITION AND THE PRESENCE OF MANY DISULFIDE BRIDGES THAT CONNECT THE KERA"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "06MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO E AVALIAÇÃO DO DESEMPENHO DE FORMULAÇÕES UNGUEAIS À BASE DE CICLOPIROX OLAMINA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JULIANA_KISHISHITA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18478> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BIOSAFETY OF A DRUG IS CONTROLLED IN THE INDUSTRIAL ROUTINE, MOSTLY THROUGH THE DISSOLUTION TEST. THE BRAZILIAN PHARMACOPOEIA DESCRIBES THAT THE DISSOLUTION TEST MAKES IT POSSIBLE TO DETERMINE THE AMOUNT OF ACTIVE SUBSTANCE DISSOLVED IN THE DISSOLUTION MEDIUM WHEN THE PRODUCT IS SUBJECTED TO THE ACTION OF SPECIFIC EQUIPMENT, UNDER EXPERIMENTAL CONDITIONS. THE ASSET MUST BE QUANTIFIED BY SPECIFIC ANALYTICAL TECHNIQUES THAT ALLOW IDENTIFYING THE PERCENTAGE DECLARED ON THE LABEL. SPECTROSCOPY I"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "24FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO E VALIDAÇÃO DE MÉTODO ANALÍTICO PARA QUANTIFICAÇÃO DO TEOR DISSOLVIDO DE OLANZAPINA COMPRIMIDO REVESTIDO POR ESPECTROFOTOMETRIA DE ABSORÇÃO ULTRAVIOLETA/VISÍVEL (UV/VIS)"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MIGUEL_WILSON_REGUEIRA_RIBEIRO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18479> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO EXPLORE THE POTENTIAL OF LOW-SUBSTITUTED HYDROXYPROPYLCELLULOSE (L-HPC), A WATER-INSOLUBLE HYDROGEL POLYMER, AS A CARRIER OF AMORPHOUS SOLID DISPERSIONS (ASDS) LOADED WITH INDOMETHACIN (IND) OR POSACONAZOLE (PCZ) AS MODEL DRUGS. TWO GRADES OF L-HPC (LH-31 AND LH-32) WERE SELECTED BASED ON DIFFERENT DEGREES OF SUBSTITUTIONS AND SWELLING EXTENSIONS IN WATER. ASDS WITH ~10% DRUG LOADING WERE OBTAINED THROUGH THE SWELLING/SORPTION PROCESS AND WERE CHARACTERIZED BY DIFFER"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "08APR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DISPERSÕES SÓLIDAS AMORFAS DO HIDROGEL INSOLÚVEL DE HIDROXIPROPILCELULOSE PARA INCREMENTO DA SOLUBILIDADE CINÉTICA DE FÁRMACOS POUCO SOLÚVEIS EM ÁGUA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LUCAS_JOSE_DE_ALENCAR_DANDA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18480> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PLINIA PERUVIANA IS KNOWN IN ETHNOMEDICINE AS JABOTICABA AND IS USED IN THE TREATMENT OF DIARRHEA AND RESPIRATORY PROBLEMS. THIS STUDY EVALUATED THE GASTROPROTECTIVE ACTIVITY OF JUICE (SPP) AND HYDROALCOHOLIC EXTRACT OF PLINIA PERUVIANA (EHPP). THE SPP AFTER OBTAINED WAS SOLIDIFIED AND LYOPHILIZED. THE EHPP WAS PREPARED FROM THE PEELS USING THE PERCOLATION AND LYOPHILIZATION TECHNIQUE. CHEMICAL ANALYSIS WAS PERFORMED BY HPLC. THE ACUTE TOXICITY OF SPP AND EHPP WAS ESTIMATED, AND SUBSEQUENTLY T"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "04FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO DA ATIVIDADE GASTROPROTETORA DO SUMO E EXTRATO HIDROETANÓLICO DAS CASCAS DO FRUTO DE PLINIA PERUVIANA (POIR.) GOVAERTS (MYRTACEAE)"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ISABEL_SOUSA_ALCANTARA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18481> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "TAMOXIFEN (TMX) IS A HORMONE THERAPY USED FOR BREAST CANCER BELONGING TO THE GROUP OF SELECTIVE ESTROGEN RECEPTOR MODULATORS (SERMS). IT COMPOSES CLASS II OF THE BIOPHARMACEUTICAL CLASSIFICATION, PRESENTING LOW WATER SOLUBILITY, LOW SELECTIVITY AND BIOAVAILABILITY, WHICH CAN CAUSE DISTINCT AND SERIOUS ADVERSE EFFECTS TO PATIENTS UNDERGOING TREATMENT. ON THE OTHER HAND, THE PRODUCTION OF MEDICINES REQUIRES THE PERFORMANCE OF STUDIES THAT ENSURE THE SAFE AND EFFECTIVE USE, AMONG THESE, STUDIES OF "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO DE ESTABILIDADE: DESENVOLVIMENTO DE MÉTODO INDICATIVO POR CLAE-DAD E CARACTERIZAÇÃO DOS PRODUTOS DE DEGRADAÇÃO EM HIDROLISE ÁCIDA DO CITRATO DE TAMOXIFENO (IFA) POR LC-MS-TOF"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LORENA_MARIA_BARBOSA_DE_LIMA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18482> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "RUTIN (RUT) IS A FLAVONOID PRESENT IN MANY PLANT SPECIES. IT HAS EXTENSIVE THERAPEUTIC APPLICATION IN CONTRAST TO THE RESTRICTED SAFE USE RESULTING FROM THE LIMITED KNOWLEDGE OF ITS STABILITY. THIS WORK PROPOSES TO DEVELOP ANALYTICAL TOOLS, APPLYING EXPERIMENTAL PLANNING TECHNIQUES BY QUALITY BY DESIGN (QBD), FOR THE DEVELOPMENT AND OPTIMIZATION OF A STABILITY INDICATOR METHOD (SIM) BY HIGH PERFORMANCE LIQUID CHROMATOGRAPHY WITH DIODE ARRAY DETECTOR (HPLC-DAD), CAPABLE OF ASSISTING IN THE CONSTR"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "21DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO DE ESTABILIDADE DO FITOFÁRMACO RUTINA: DESENVOLVIMENTO DE FERRAMENTAS ANALÍTICAS, DETERMINAÇÃO DA CINÉTICA DE DEGRADAÇÃO HIDROLÍTICA E AVALIAÇÃO DE SISTEMAS POLIMÉRICOS PROTETORES"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JOSE_IZAK_RIBEIRO_DE_ARAUJO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18483> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "METALLIC NANOPARTICLES EXHIBIT SEVERAL PROPERTIES THAT HAVE BEEN STUDIED IN RECENT YEARS IN DIFFERENT AREAS OF KNOWLEDGE, ESPECIALLY THOSE OF SILVER AND GOLD. A CHARACTERISTIC EFFECT IS SURFACE PLASMON RESONANCE (SPR), THAT CONFERS THE ABILITY TO INCREASE OPTICAL PROPERTIES OF OTHER MOLECULES UNDER SPECIFIC CONDITIONS. IN THE HEALTH AREA, ONE POSSIBILITY OF USING THESE SYSTEMS IS IN ASSOCIATION WITH THE SO-CALLED PHOTOSENSITIZERS (PS), WHICH ARE USED FOR THE PRODUCTION OF REACTIVE OXYGEN SPECIES"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "24FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "INATIVAÇÃO FOTODINAMICA DE MICRORGANISMOS RESISTENTES MEDIADA POR AZUL DE METILENO E NANOPRISMAS DE PRATA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CLAUDIO_HENRIQUE_RODRIGUES_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18484> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HYPOVITAMINOSIS D IS A STATE OF NUTRITIONAL DEFICIENCY OF VITAMIN D THAT HAS AN ESTIMATED PREVALENCE OF APPROXIMATELY ONE BILLION PEOPLE WORLDWIDE. AT THE SAME TIME, CASE REPORTS INVOLVING THIS VITAMIN INTOXICATION HAVE BEEN INCREASINGLY PUBLISHED IN THE LITERATURE. IN THIS ANTAGONISTIC CLINICAL SCENARIO, WHICH IMPOSES NEW CHALLENGES ON HEALTH PROFESSIONALS, THE USE AND DISPENSING OF THIS DRUG, IN THE LIGHT OF EVIDENCE-BASED HEALTH, IS OF FUNDAMENTAL IMPORTANCE, ESPECIALLY IN THE FACE OF THE PAN"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "MEDICAMENTOS CONTENDO COLECALCIFEROL: AVALIAÇÃO DOS USOS E LIMITES NA TERAPÊUTICA  UMA ABORDAGEM SOB A PERSPECTIVA DO USO RACIONAL DE MEDICAMENTOS (URM)"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/STEPHANYE_CAROLYNE_CHRISTINO_CHAGAS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18485> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THERAPEUTIC DRUG MONITORING (TDM) IS AN AREA OF ¿¿CLINICAL PHARMACOKINETICS AIMED AT INDIVIDUALIZING DOSAGE. TDM TECHNIQUES ARE APPLIED TO GUARANTEE THE SAFETY AND EFFICACY OF A PHARMACOLOGICAL TREATMENT. PATIENTS UNDERGOING CHEMOTHERAPY TREATMENT MAY BENEFIT FROM TDM. AMONG THE DRUGS USED IN ADJUVANT THERAPY IN ONCOLOGY, ONDANSETRON STANDS OUT, WHICH IS AN ANTIEMETIC, SELECTIVE ANTAGONIST OF THE 5-HT3 RECEPTOR. THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO PERFORM AN INTEGRATIVE LITERATURE REVIEW THAT IDENTIFIE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "06DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "MONITORIZAÇÃO TERAPÊUTICA DA ONDANSENTRONA EM PACIENTES ONCOLÓGICOS HOSPITALIZADOS: UMA REVISÃO INTEGRATIVA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JORDAN_CARLOS_SILVA_DE_MEDEIROS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18486> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "EUTERPE OLERACEA IS AN OIL SEED PREDOMINANTLY FOUND IN THE AMAZON, HAVING ITS SEED TREATED AS PULP RESIDUE, AND ITS DISPOSAL CONSIDERED AS A WASTE DISPOSAL PROBLEM. THE OIL FROM THIS SEED IS A PROMISING RAW MATERIAL NOT ONLY FOR THE PHARMACEUTICAL INDUSTRY, BUT ALSO AS PESTICIDES, AS INSECTICIDES OF PLANT ORIGIN HAVE BEEN AN ALTERNATIVE BECAUSE THEY ARE SELECTIVE, BIODEGRADABLE AND REDUCE THE IMPACT ON BIODIVERSITY. DISEASES SUCH AS ZIKA, CHIKUNGUNYA AND DENGUE HAVE BEEN REPORTED AS PUBLIC HEALT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "14SEP2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "NANOEMULSÃO A BASE DO ÓLEO DA SEMENTE DE EUTERPE OLERACEA (MART.) COM ATIVIDADE FRENTE AEDES AEGYPTI"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/STEFANI_FERREIRA_DE_OLIVEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18487> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "N-ACYLHYDRAZONIC DERIVATIVES ARE STRUCTURES WIDELY USED IN MEDICINAL CHEMISTRY DUE TO THEIR EASE OF SYNTHESIS AND BECAUSE THEY EXHIBIT A WIDE RANGE OF PHARMACOLOGICAL ACTIVITIES DESCRIBED IN THE LITERATURE. THE OBJECTIVE OF THE RESEARCH WAS TO EVALUATE THE POSSIBLE DUAL EFFECT OF N-ACYLHYDRAZONIC DERIVATIVES JR-13, JR-15, JR 17 AND JR-18 AS ANTI-INFLAMMATORY AND ANTIMICROBIAL. THE ANTIMICROBIAL ACTIVITY WAS TESTED AGAINST GRAM-POSITIVE AND GRAM-NEGATIVE MICROORGANISMS, YEASTS AND CLINICAL ISOLAT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "10OCT2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "NOVOS DERIVADOS N-ACILHIDRAZÔNICOS COMO POTENCIAIS FÁRMACOS DUAIS COM ATIVIDADES ANTI-INFLAMATÓRIA E ANTIMICROBIANA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/KATHARINA_RODRIGUES_DE_LIMA_PORTO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18488> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "LEISHMANIASIS AND CHAGAS DISEASE ARE PART OF A GROUP OF ILLNESSES KNOWN AS NEGLECTED TROPICAL DISEASES, AND THEY CAN CAUSE DISFIGUREMENT AND DISABILITY, LEADING TO STIGMATIZATION AND SOCIAL DISCRIMINATION. FOR THE WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION, IT IS URGENT TO FIND LESS TOXIC AND MORE EFFECTIVE THERAPEUTIC ALTERNATIVES THAN THOSE CURRENTLY AVAILABLE. IN THIS WORK, A PROFILED IN SILICO STUDY OF THE 4-AMINO-5-CARBONITRILE-PYRIMIDINE PROTOTYPE WAS PROMOTED TO OPTIMIZE ANTICHAGASIC ACTIVITY. THE EVALUAT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "29JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PLANEJAMENTO IN SILICO, SÍNTESE, CARACTERIZAÇÃO E AVALIAÇÃO IN VITRO DE NOVOS ANÁLOGOS DA 4-AMINO-5-CIANO-PIRIMIDINAS DE INTERESSE FARMACOLÓGICO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/GLEYBSON_CORREIA_DE_ALMEIDA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18489> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ACCORDING TO THE WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION, IN 2020, THERE WERE 1.3 MILLION PREGNANT WOMEN LIVING WITH HIV, OF WHOM APPROXIMATELY 85% RECEIVED ANTIRETROVIRAL DRUGS TO PREVENT MOTHER-TO-CHILD TRANSMISSION. THE SPECIFIC PHYSIOLOGICAL BACKGROUND INDUCED BY PREGNANCY LEADS TO SIGNIFICANT CHANGES IN MATERNAL PHARMACOKINETICS, SUGGESTING POTENTIAL VARIABILITY IN PLASMA CONCENTRATIONS OF ANTIRETROVIRALS DURING GESTATION. THEREFORE, PREGNANT WOMEN MAY BE EXPOSED TO SUBTHERAPEUTIC CONCENTRATIONS OF ANTIR"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "QUANTIFICAÇÃO SIMULTÂNEA DE ANTIRRETROVIRAIS EM DRIED BLOOD SPOT E PLASMA UTILIZANDO LC-MS/MS: FARMACOCINÉTICA E MONITORIZAÇÃO TERAPÊUTICA DE EFAVIRENZ EM GESTANTES"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MAIRA_LUDNA_DUARTE> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18490> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DIABETES MELLITUS IS A CHARACTERISTIC METABOLIC SYNDROME FOR TRIGGERING HIGH GLYCEMIC LEVELS, CAUSED BY THE ABSENCE OR REDUCED PRODUCTION AND RELEASE OF THE HORMONE INSULIN. SUBCUTANEOUS ADMINISTRATION OF THE SYNTHETIC PROTEIN IS NECESSARY FOR GLUCOSE UPTAKE AND USE BY CELLS. DUE TO THE DISCOMFORT CAUSED BY THE CONVENTIONAL FORM OF TREATMENT, A STRATEGY IS GIVEN BY THE ADMINISTRATION OF THE DRUG ORALLY, BUT IT IS NECESSARY TO PROTECT THE MOLECULE FROM EXPOSURE TO VARIATIONS IN GASTROINTESTINAL P"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "20DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SÍNTESE DE NANOPARTICULAS A PARTIR DE BIOPOLÍMEROS PARA ADMINISTRAÇAO DE INSULINA POR VIA ORAL"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JANIRA_MARIA_NASCIMENTO_ALVES_BEZERRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18491> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PLASMA PROTEINS, SUCH AS ALBUMIN (BSA), ARE ALSO USED IN THESE STUDIES TO VERIFY THE PHARMACOKINETIC PROPERTIES OF DRUGS. IN THESE STUDIES, MOLECULES CONTAINING PHENYL AND THIOSEMICARBAZONES ARE CONSIDERED PROMISING BECAUSE THEY HAVE BIOLOGICAL ACTIVITY. THIS IS PARTICULARLY RELEVANT FOR TREATMENTS OF VARIOUS DISEASES, SINCE THIS PROTEIN ACCUMULATES IN THE MICROENVIRONMENT, INCREASING THE DISTRIBUTION OF DRUGS, IN ADDITION TO SUPPLYING THE ENERGY DEMANDS OF CELLS. DIFFERENT TECHNIQUES OF SPECTRO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17NOV2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SÍNTESE DE TIOSSEMICARBAZONAS, ELUCIDAÇÃO ESTRUTURAL, CITOTOXICIDADE, ATIVIDADE ANTIOXIDANTE, ADMET E ESTUDOS DE INTERAÇÃO COM ALBUMINA SÉRICA BOVINA (BSA)"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MARIA_JOSE_CRISTIANE_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18492> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ISOXAZOLES AND DERIVATIVES ARE HETEROCYCLICS OF GREAT RELEVANCE IN MEDICINAL CHEMISTRY, AS THEY HAVE ACTIVITIES SUCH AS ANTI-INFLAMMATORY, ANTICANCER AND ANTIPARASITIC, AND IN COMMERCIAL DRUGS. ANOTHER HETEROCYCLE OF GREAT INTEREST IS THIAZOLE, WHICH HAS SHOWN IMPORTANT ANTICANCER AND LEISHMANICIDAL ACTIVITIES, AND THESE ACTIVITIES ARE POTENTIATED BY HYDRAZONES AND HYDRAZIDES, GENERATED IN THE FORMATION OF THIAZOLE NUCLEUS. IN OUR RESEARCH GROUP (LASOF), THE 2-ISOXAZOLINE AZA-BICYCLIC NUCLEUS WA"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27JUN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SÍNTESE E AVALIAÇÃO DAS ATIVIDADES CITOTÓXICA E ANTIPARASITÁRIAS DE NOVOS DERIVADOS HÍBRIDOS ISOXAZOLINA AZA-BICÍCLICA/TIAZOL E DERIVADOS DI-ARIL ISOXAZÓIS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/FELIPE_NEVES_COUTINHO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18493> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE DEGREE OF SEVERITY OF MICROBIAL INFECTIONS CAN BE INFLUENCED BY THE PRESENCE OF VIRULENCE FACTORS, AS WELL AS THE DEVELOPMENT OF INTRINSIC AND EXTRINSIC RESISTANCE TO ANTIMICROBIALS. SUCH CHARACTERISTICS HAVE BEEN ONE OF THE MAIN REASONS FOR THE FAILURE OF ANTIBIOTICS IN THE TREATMENT OF INFECTIONS. THEREFORE, THE PRESENT WORK AIMED TO DEVELOP NEW ANTIMICROBIAL AGENTS AGAINST CLINICAL ISOLATES OF FUNGI. THE SYNTHESIZED COMPOUNDS WERE CHARACTERIZED AND IDENTIFIED BY MEANS OF INFRARED SPECTROS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "31AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SÍNTESE E ELUCIDAÇÃO ESTRUTURAL DE NOVOS DERIVADOS 2,4- DIHIDROXI-BENZILIDENO-TIOSSEMICARBAZONAS POTENCIAIS ANTIMICROBIANOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MARIA_FERNANDA_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_FARMACÊUTICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1872> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN MANY AREAS OF SCIENCE. DATA SETS AND STATISTICAL PROCEDURES ARE OFTEN AFFECTED BY MISSING VALUES. IN CLUSTERING ANALYSIS, LACK OF DATA MAY IMPAIR THE FORMATION OF GROUPS. MANY CLUSTERING METHODS FOR INCOMPLETE DATA PRESENT IN THE LITERATURE DO NOT TAKE INTO ACCOUNT THE WEIGHTS OR THE RELEVANCE OF THE VARIABLES IN THE CONSTRUCTION OF THE CLUSTERS. THIS WORK AIMS TO PROPOSE AND EVALUATE THE METHOD OF FUZZY C-MEANS KERNEL CLUSTERING WITH METRIC KERNELIZATION VIA LOCAL ADAPTIVE DISTANCES (VKFCM-K"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30JUL2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AGRUPAMENTO FUZZY KERNELIZADO ADAPTADO PARA DADOS FALTANTES"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ANNY_KEROLLAYNY_GOMES_RODRIGUES> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ESTATÍSTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1873> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "RESEARCHES INVOLVING SURVIVAL AND RELIABILITY DATA ARE OF SIGNIFICANT IMPORTANCE IN SEVERAL RESEARCH FIELDS, SUCH AS ENGINEERING, BIOMEDICINE, SOCIAL SCIENCES, AMONG OTHERS. WITH THE ADVANCEMENT IN DATA ANALYSIS, IT IS NECESSARY THE USE OF PROBABILITY DISTRIBUTIONS THAT BEST FIT THESE DATA SETS. THE PROPOSAL OF NEW DISTRIBUTIONS OF PROBABILITY IS A RESEARCH TOPIC CONSIDERED BY SEVERAL AUTHORS, WHO ARE MOTIVATED TO PROPOSE DISTRIBUTIONS THAT ARE MORE FLEXIBLE IN TERMS OF THE FAILURE RATE FUNCTION"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22JUL2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ALGUNS MODELOS NA FAMÍLIA NADARAJAH-HAGHIGHI G COM APLICAÇÕES A DADOS CLÍNICOS E DE FADIGA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JOSE_JAIRO_DE_SANTANA_E_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ESTATÍSTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1874> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS WORK PROPOSES THE USE OF A VALUE-AT-RISK MEASURE BASED ON THE LINEAR AUTOREGRESSIVE CONDITIONAL HETEROSKEDASTICITY MODEL ESTIMATED BY QUANTILE REGRESSION METHODS IN EXCHANGE TRADED FUNDS RETURNS DURING THE UNITED STATES SUBPRIME MORTGAGE CRISIS. THIS TASK WAS PERFORMED WITH THE HELP OF A SUBGRADIENT TEST FOR STRUCTURAL CHANGE (QU), WHICH ALLOWS US TO EVALUATE WHETHER THE PARAMETER VALUES REMAIN STABLE THROUGHOUT THE SERIES AND IN A GENERALIZED MOMENTS METHOD BASED DURATION TEST (GMM) FOR CO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AN EMPIRICAL EVALUATION OF STRUCTURAL CHANGES IN QUANTILE AUTOREGRESSIVE MODELS RECIFE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/YURI_MARTI_SANTANA_SANTOS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ESTATÍSTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1875> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PRINCIPAL COMPONENT ANALYSIS (PCA) IS OFTEN USED FOR DATA DE-CORRELATION AND DIMENSIONALITY REDUCTION. BECAUSE OF ITS ENERGY COMPRESSION CHARACTERISTICS IN A FEW MAIN COMPONENTS, THERE ARE IMPORTANT PCA APPLICATIONS IN THE CONTEXT OF IMAGE COMPRESSION. IN THE AREA OF SIGNAL PROCESSING, PCA IS KNOWN AS THE KARHUNEN-LOÈVE TRANSFORM (KLT). DUE TO THE FACT THAT ITS COMPUTATION DEPENDS ON THE VARIANCE AND COVARIANCE MATRICES OF THE INPUT SIGNAL, THE USE OF THE KLT IN REAL APPLICATIONS IS SEVERELY CON"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "21FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "APROXIMAÇÕES DE BAIXA COMPLEXIDADE PARA A TRANSFORMADA DISCRETA DE KARHUNEN-LOÈVE: PROJETO, ALGORITMOS RÁPIDOS E COMPRESSÃO DE IMAGENS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ANABETH_PETRY_RADUNZ> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ESTATÍSTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1876> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THIS THESIS WE PRESENTED THE RESULTS OF TWO DISTINCT LINES OF RESEARCH, NAMELY CIRCULAR DATA ANALYSIS AND SCALE MIXTURE MODELS. IN THE FIRST ONE, IN THE CIRCULAR DATA ANALYSIS, A NEW CIRCULAR DISTRIBUTION CALLED WRAPPED BIRNBAUM-SAUNDERS WAS PROPOSED. FOR THIS DISTRIBUTION WE HAVE FOUND EXPRESSIONS FOR THEIR PROBABILITY DENSITY FUNCTION, DISTRIBUTION FUNCTION AND TRIGONOMETRIC MOMENTS, IN ADDITION, WE CONDUCTED A MONTE CARLO SIMULATION STUDY TO EVALUATE THE PERFORMANCE OF THE OF THE MAXIMUM L"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "26FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CLASSE DE DISTRIBUIÇÕES MISTURA DE ESCALA T-STUDENT E ENSAIOS EM ANÁLISE DE DADOS CIRCULARES: DISTRIBUIÇÃO WRAPPED BIRNBAUM-SAUNDERS."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MARLEY_APOLINARIO_SARAIVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ESTATÍSTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/18769> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BRAZILIAN DEMOGRAPHIC PROFILE HAS CHANGED SINCE THE 70S, WHEN THERE WAS AN INCREASE IN URBAN SOCIETY, ASSOCIATED WITH A NEW FAMILY STRUCTURE COMPOSED OF A REDUCED NUMBER OF CHILDREN. DESPITE HUMAN SEXUALITY BEING PART OF ONE OF THE PILLARS OF QUALITY OF LIFE, IT IS RARELY ADDRESSED IN HEALTH SERVICES. THERE ARE STILL SOME PREJUDICES AND TABOOS LINKED TO THE EXERCISE OF SEXUALITY. IN THIS SENSE, THE STUDY AIMS TO CHARACTERIZE THE SELF-PERCEPTION OF SEXUALITY IN THE ELDERLY POPULATION WITH PAR"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PESSOA IDOSA COM DOENÇA DE PARKINSON: UM ESTUDO DA AUTOPERCEPÇÃO SOBRE A SEXUALIDADE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/BIANCA_VERISSIMO_DE_OLIVEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/GERONTOLOGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/1877> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AIM OF THIS WORK IS TO USE CLASSIC CARDIAC CHARACTERISTICS AND NEW PARAMETERS INTRODUCED BY CAMPELLO SOUZA (2010) [SUPPORT OF MEDICAL DIAGNOSIS: WHAT CAN BE DONE WITH A TENSIOMETER?. 2. ED. RECIFE] IN THE PROCESS OF CLASSIFICATION OF INDIVIDUALS WITH HEART DISEASE. CONSIDERING DIFFERENT SCENARIOS, AND BASED ON FOUR DIFFERENT DATABASES, THE PARAMETERS OF CAMPELLO SOUZA WERE INCLUDED IN THE SELECTION PROCESS OF THE MOST INFORMATIVE ATTRIBUTES AND ADDED IN THE BINARY CLASSIFICATION PROCESS OF T"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30JUL2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CLASSIFICAÇÃO BINÁRIA PARA CARDIOPATIAS USANDO CARACTERÍSTICAS CARDÍACAS CLÁSSICAS E NOVOS PARÂMETROS"@pt ;
