    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_GEODÉSICAS_E_TECNOLOGIAS_DA_GEOINFORMAÇÃO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19260> a capes:Thesis ;
