<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19314> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "KNOWLEDGE ABOUT SEA LEVEL VARIATIONS PLAYS AN IMPORTANT ROLE IN IDENTIFYING CLIMATE CHANGE, WHETHER GLOBAL OR REGIONAL, AS SEA LEVEL RISE IS LARGELY ASSOCIATED WITH THESE CHANGES AND DIRECTLY AFFECTS COASTAL ZONES. THE GLOBAL GEODETIC OBSERVING SYSTEM (GGOS), INTERNATIONAL ASSOCIATION OF GEODESY (IAG), IDENTIFIED SEA LEVEL CHANGE AS ONE OF ITS MAIN THEMES AND ESTABLISHED IT AS ONE OF ITS RESEARCH FOCUSES. GGOS THEME 3, UNDERSTANDING AND PREDICTION OF UNDERSTANDING AND FORECASTING SEA LEVEL RISE "@pt ;
