<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19344> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "JUDICIAL DEPOSITS IN THE COURTS OF JUSTICE AT THE END OF 2020 TOTALED 224 BILLION REAIS, THESE RESOURCES ARE MANAGED BY OFFICIAL FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS THAT REMUNERATE THEIR DEPOSITORS AT RATES SIMILAR TO THOSE OF SAVINGS. CURRENTLY, THE COURTS DELEGATE THE FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS TO THE MANAGEMENT OF THESE JUDICIAL DEPOSITS THROUGH CONTRACTS, HOWEVER, SEVERAL NEGATIVE POINTS ARE PERCEIVED IN THIS CONTRACT, SUCH AS: LOW YIELDS; GREAT DEPENDENCE ON FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS; LACK OF TRANSPARENCY, LAC"@pt ;
