<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19365> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN RECENT YEARS, THE INCREASING MARKET PRESSURE AND CONSTANT EMERGENCE OF NEW TECHNOLOGIES HAVE DRIVEN FIRMS TO UNDERTAKE DIGITAL TRANSFORMATIONS TO CREATE VALUE AND DELIVER BETTER PRODUCTS OR SERVICES FOR CUSTOMERS. CORPORATIONS FACE SEVERAL CHALLENGES WHEN IT COMES TO INCORPORATING NEW TECHNOLOGIES OR ACCELERATING AND DIGITIZING THEIR WELL-ESTABLISHED PROCESSES. BY CONTRAST, STARTUPS ARE RECOGNIZED FOR THEIR INNOVATION CAPACITY, WILLINGNESS TO TAKE RISKS, SCALABLE SOLUTIONS, AND AGILE PROCESSE"@pt ;
