<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19397> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN COMPUTING HIGHER EDUCATION, THERE IS A GROWING MOVEMENT TO CHANGE AN EDUCATIONAL PARADIGM THAT GOES BEYOND KNOWLEDGE-BASED EDUCATION. THEREFORE, ACTIVE LEARNING METHODOLOGIES BASED ON PRACTICAL EXPERIENCES, SUCH AS PROBLEM-BASED LEARNING (PBL), HAVE BECOME INCREASINGLY POPULAR TO DEVELOP NOT ONLY TECHNICAL KNOWLEDGE, BUT STUDENT SKILLS AND ATTITUDES. ENABLING TO PERFORM BETTER PROFESSIONALLY. ALL THESE ELEMENTS INVOLVE ITERATIONS THAT NEED TO BE MAPPED AND CONTINUOUSLY MONITORED THROUGH A COM"@pt ;
