<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19412> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE USE OF MACHINE LEARNING (ML) HAS BEEN INCREASINGLY COMMON IN SEVERAL AREAS OF KNOWLEDGE. SOFTWARE ENGINEERING, AS WELL AS EDUCATIONAL PERFORMANCE STUDIES, ARE EXAMPLES OF AREAS THAT HAVE ADHERED TO ML TECHNIQUES. THE METHODS USED RANGE FROM THE INDIVIDUAL ONES, WHICH GENERATE OUTPUTS FROM A MODEL, TO THE MULTIPLE MODEL SYSTEM. THE STRATEGIES USED IN THESE COMBINATIONS HAVE BEEN AN IMPORTANT RESEARCH TOPIC IN AM, SINCE THE USE OF MULTIPLE MODELS HAS REDUCED THE ERROR AND VARIANCE OF PREDICTIO"@pt ;
