<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19416> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THE AGE OF BIG DATA, A LARGE VOLUME OF STRUCTURED, SEMI-STRUCTURED, AND MOSTLY UNSTRUCTURED DATA IS GENERATED MUCH FASTER BY DIGITAL TECHNOLOGIES AND INFORMATION SYSTEMS. IN THIS CONTEXT, DATA LAKES EMERGED AS AN ALTERNATIVE TO TRADITIONAL DATA WAREHOUSES, BECOMING ONE OF THE MOST USED BIG DATA SOLUTIONS FOR DISTRIBUTED ANALYSIS AND MANAGEMENT OF LARGE VOLUMES OF DATA. THE MAIN IDEA OF DATA LAKE IS TO INGEST RAW DATA AND PROCESS IT DURING ITS USE, CHARACTERIZING THE SCHEMA ON-READ APPROACH. D"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "10MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
