<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19441> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HPV VACCINE IS A PRIMARY FORM OF PREVENTION FOR CERVICAL CANCER. UTERUS AND OTHER ANOGENITAL CANCERS. IN BRAZIL, IT IS AVAILABLE FOR GIRLS FROM NINE TO 14 YEARS AND BOYS FROM 12 TO 14 YEARS. SINCE ITS IMPLEMENTATION IN THE UNIFIED HEALTH, VACCINATION RATES HAVE BEEN DECREASING, WHICH MAY BE LOW LEVELS OF KNOWLEDGE ABOUT IMMUNOBIOLOGICALS. THE REALIZATION OF HEALTH EDUCATION ACTIONS MAY PROVIDE IMPROVEMENT OF THIS KNOWLEDGE, REFLECTING POSITIVE ATTITUDES AND VACCINATION PRACTICE. AN INTEGRATIVE R"@pt ;
