<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19447> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HEALTH EDUCATION INTERVENTION ACTIVITIES WERE CARRIED OUT BY NURSES WITH THE AIM OF INSTRUCTING PEOPLE ON HOW TO AVOID, CONTRACT OR SPREAD COVID-19, WHICH WAS CONSIDERED A PANDEMIC BY THE WORLD HEALTH ORGANIZATION IN MARCH 2020. HOWEVER, THE INSUFFICIENCY OF HEALTH LITERACY IN SOME INDIVIDUALS MAY HAVE IMPAIRED UNDERSTANDING OF THE CONTENT. THUS, THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS RESEARCH WAS TO ANALYZE THE HEALTH LITERACY OF PEOPLE RECOVERED FROM COVID - 19. THIS WAS AN ANALYTICAL, CROSS-SECTIONAL STUDY WI"@pt ;
