<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19449> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DESPITE THE RECOMMENDATIONS OF HEALTH ORGANIZATIONS ON GOOD PRACTICES, GAPS IN THE CARE OF WOMEN IN THE STREETS IN THE PREGNANCY-PUERPERAL CYCLE ARE PERCEIVED. THIS STUDY AIMS TO ANALYZE THE EXPERIENCES OF STREET WOMEN IN PREGNANCY/PRENATAL CARE, CHILDBIRTH/BIRTH, PUERPERIUM AND BREASTFEEDING AND THEIR INTERFACES WITH GOOD CARE PRACTICES. THIS IS A DESCRIPTIVE, EXPLORATORY, QUALITATIVE STUDY, ANCHORED IN THE THEORY OF SOCIAL NETWORK AND GUIDED BY THE HERMENEUTIC-DIALECTIC CIRCLE, CARRIED OUT IN "@pt ;
