    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIAS_ENERGÉTICAS_E_NUCLEARES> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19540> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN A LITERATE SOCIETY, WRITING IS PRESENT AND NECESSARY IN THE MOST VARIED SOCIAL CONTEXTS, BECOMING A SOCIAL ASSET, ACCORDING TO MARCUSCHI (2010), INDISPENSABLE TO FACE DAILY LIFE. HOWEVER, ACCESS TO THIS GOOD DOES NOT HAPPEN EQUALLY TO EVERYONE. BECAUSE OF THIS REALITY, A CONSIDERABLE NUMBER OF STUDENTS REACH THE INITIAL GRADE OF THE THIRD CYCLE OF ELEMENTARY EDUCATION - 6TH GRADE - WITH A LEVEL OF READING AND WRITING FAR BELOW EXPECTATIONS. AWARE OF THIS SITUATION, AN INTERVENTION PROPOSAL WA"@pt,
