<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19548> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "COMPUTED TOMOGRAPHY (CT) IS AN IMPORTANT MEDICAL DIAGNOSTIC TOOL FOR ACQUISITION OF HIGH PRECISION AND HIGH-RESOLUTION RADIOGRAPHIC IMAGES. HOWEVER, DESPITE CONTINUOUS TECHNOLOGICAL ADVANCES, CT SCANS MAY RESULT IN HIGH DOSES ABSORBED BY PATIENTS, AS HAS BEEN OBSERVED IN SEVERAL STUDIES CONDUCTED IN DIFFERENT COUNTRIES. IN THE CASE OF BRAZIL, THERE ARE FEW STUDIES THAT PROVIDE AN OVERVIEW OF THE CT INSTALLED BASE IN THE COUNTRY AND HOW THIS EQUIPMENT HAS BEEN USED, AS WELL AS THE RADIATION DOSES"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30AUG2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
