<http://example.com/capes#thesis/19554> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY INTENDS TO MODEL AND ANALYZE A PHOTOVOLTAIC WATER SUPPLY SYSTEM (PVWPS) IN DIFFERENT CLIMATIC CONDITIONS. THE PVWPS CONSISTS IN A SET OF PHOTOVOLTAIC PANELS, A FREQUENCY INVERTOR, A PUMP AND A STORAGE SYSTEM. THIS SYSTEM HAS BEEN OVERLY TESTED EXPERIMENTALLY IN A TEST BENCH IN REAL CONDITIONS (OUTDOOR). THE METEOROLOGICAL AND GEOMETRICAL PARAMETERS OF SYSTEM AND THEIR DUE FLOW RATE HAS BEEN DEVELOPED USING AN ARTIFICIAL NEURAL NETWORK (ANN) MODELING A FUNCTION OF METEOROLOGICAL DATA A"@pt ;
