<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20049> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "RECIFE, A CITY IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO, IS HOME TO THREE LARGE HYDROGRAPHIC BASINS OF THE CAPIBARIBE, BEBERIBE AND TEJIPIÓ RIVERS AND THEIR TRIBUTARIES. THIS SYSTEM OF WATER BODIES IS RESPONSIBLE FOR THE CITYS GEOLOGICAL FORMATION, WHICH TOGETHER WITH HUMAN ACTION, THROUGH SUCCESSIVE LANDFILLS, SHAPED THE NATURAL ENVIRONMENT. THEREFORE, THE WAY THE CITY WAS OCCUPIED, BUILT AND LIVED, IS DIRECTLY RELATED TO THE WATERS. THE PRESENT RESEARCH FOCUSES ON THE CAPIBARIBE RIVER AND WAS DEVELOPED WIT"@pt ;
