<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20443> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WITH THE INCREASE IN TECHNOLOGICAL ADVANCES AND INNUMERABLE DIGITAL TOOLS, THIS HAS LED THE BRAZILIAN JUSTICE TO RETHINK ITS MODELS OF PROCEDURAL DATA STORAGE, WORK ROUTINE AND TIME IMPROVEMENT, AS WELL AS COULD IMPACT THE SUSTAINABILITY, ECONOMY AND SPEED OF JUDICIAL PROVISION. IN THIS WAY, THE PERNAMBUCO COURT OF JUSTICE (TJPE) IMPLEMENTED AN ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE SYSTEM. THE PRESENT WORK SEEKS TO ANALYZE SUSTAINABILITY WITH THE IMPLEMENTATION OF ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE SYSTEMS ASSOCIATED WI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "11MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DA SUSTENTABILIDADE DA IMPLANTAÇÃO DO SISTEMA DE INTELIGÊNCIA ARTIFICIAL NO TRIBUNAL DE JUSTIÇA DE PERNAMBUCO"@pt ;
