    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ELISABETE_CAVALCANTI_GIL_RODRIGUES> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20444> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE CONSERVATION OF THE ENVIRONMENT IS THE TASK OF NATIONS, ENSURING THE AVAILABILITY AND SUSTAINABLE MANAGEMENT OF WATER IS AMONG THE GOALS OF THE UN 2030 AGENDA. THE SOCIOECONOMIC CONTEXT CAUSED BY THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC, AND MORE RECENTLY WITH THE WAR IN UKRAINE, WERE RESPONSIBLE FOR A MAJOR CRISIS IN THE WORLD ECONOMY. FACED WITH THIS SITUATION OF INFLATION AND THE RISE OF THE DOLLAR, ACCESS TO BASIC ITEMS SUCH AS WATER AND COOKING GAS HAS BECOME AN OBSTACLE FOR THE NEEDY POPULATION. ON THE O"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DA UTILIZAÇÃO DA ÁGUA DE CHUVA EM ATIVIDADES DE LAVAGEM DE PISO E IRRIGAÇÃO DE JARDIM:ESTUDO DE CASO NO PRÉDIO DO JUIZADO ESPECIAL CÍVEL E DAS RELAÇÕES DE CONSUMO DE CAMARAGIBE-PE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/AURICELIA_GALDINO_DOS_SANTOS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20445> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "URBAN GROWTH, POPULATION GROWTH AND THE CONSTRUCTION INDUSTRY GROWTH CAUSE AN INCREASED ENVIRONMENTAL WASTE GENERATION. ONE OF THE GROWING PROBLEMS IN THE WORLD TODAY IS CAUSED BY ERRONEOUS WASTE DISPOSAL IN INAPPROPRIATE PLACES, IN AN UNCONTROLLED WAY, CAUSING GREAT ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACTS. CIVIL CONSTRUCTION WASTE (CCW) GENERATED NOWADAYS IN BRAZIL REPRESENTS A MAJOR SOCIO-ENVIRONMENTAL PROBLEM THAT REQUIRES PLANNING FOR ITS REDUCTION, RECYCLING AND FINAL DISPOSAL. PLANS, STANDARDS, RESEARCH AND"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "11JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DO GERENCIAMENTO DE RESÍDUOS DA CONSTRUÇÃO CIVIL EM OBRAS NA CIDADE DE OLINDA COM AVALIAÇÃO DE INDICADORES AMBIENTAIS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/GILKA_DINIZ_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20446> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WATER IS A FINITE RESOURCE, AND ITS SCARCITY HAS WORSENED DUE TO POPULATION GROWTH, LACK OF MANAGEMENT AND SUSTAINABLE USE OF NATURAL RESOURCES. THE UNITED NATIONS RECOGNIZES THAT WATER REUSE IS A SAFE SOLUTION FOR MEETING THE WORLD'S WATER NEEDS, ESTABLISHING THIS PRACTICE THROUGH THE 2030 AGENDA AS A FUNDAMENTAL TOOL FOR ACHIEVING ONE OF THE SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT GOALS. WASTEWATER REUSE TECHNOLOGY, THROUGH SEWAGE TREATMENT PLANTS (ETE), IS A SUSTAINABLE SOLUTION TO HELP RATIONALIZE WATER USE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "02JUN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DO IMPACTO DA IMPLEMENTAÇÃO DA TECNOLOGIA NO REUSO DE ÁGUAS RESIDUÁRIAS: ESTAÇÃO DE TRATAMENTO DE ESGOTO, UM ESTUDO DE CASO NO FÓRUM DES. RODOLFO AURELIANO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JOAO_BOSCO_DOS_REIS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20447> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE ADVENT OF THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC IMPOSED A PROFOUND TRANSFORMATION IN THE DAILY LIFE OF SOCIETY AROUND THE WORLD, DUE TO THE EASE OF CONTAMINATION OF THE DISEASE AND THE LETHAL POTENTIAL PRESENTED BY THE VIRUS. GOVERNMENTS IN SEVERAL COUNTRIES HAVE ADOPTED STRICT SOCIAL DISTANCING PROTOCOLS. IN BRAZIL, THE ARRIVAL OF THE DISEASE LED THE NATIONAL COUNCIL OF JUSTICE TO ADOPT ATTITUDES CONSISTENT WITH THE TEMPORARY RULES OF SUSPENSION OF FACE-TO-FACE ACTIVITIES, GUARANTEEING THE PHYSICAL FUNCTIO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ANÁLISE DOS INDICADORES DE SUSTENTABILIDADE E EFICIÊNCIA DO TRABALHO REMOTO DOS SERVIDORES DA JUSTIÇA NA PANDEMIA DA COVID-19"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MARIA_DAS_GRACAS_DE_OLIVEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20448> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE ANALYSIS OF AIR QUALITY IS DIRECTLY RELATED TO THE PRESERVATION OF THE HEALTH OF INDIVIDUALS WHO ATTEND CLOSED ENVIRONMENTS, WHETHER CLIMATE-CONTROLLED OR NOT, AND THIS FACTOR MAY BE LINKED TO THE (UN)HEALTHY LOCATION OF THE PLACE. CERTAIN POLLUTING FACTORS ARE POTENTIATED BY THE LACK OF NATURAL VENTILATION; IN OTHER CASES, DEPENDING ON THE REGION, THE NATURAL WIND CIRCULATION IS WHAT BRINGS POLLUTION TO THE AREA. CONSIDERING THAT ALL ENVIRONMENTS CAN BE AFFECTED BY A DECREASE IN SANITARY CO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "13APR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA QUALIDADE DO AR EM UMA EDIFICAÇÃO PÚBLICA DO PODER JUDICIÁRIO NO MUNICÍPIO DE OLINDA/PE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ALAIDE_MARIA_PEIXOTO_PEREIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/20449> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WATER IS A VERY IMPORTANT RESOURCE FOR EVERY SOCIETY, BUT FOR MANY YEARS IT WAS TREATED AS AN INEXHAUSTIBLE SOURCE. HOWEVER, THE GROWTH OF THE WORLD POPULATION AND THE INDUSTRIAL REVOLUTION CAUSED AN UNCONTROLLED CONSUMPTION OF NATURAL RESOURCES, AMONG THEM, THE SCARCITY OF DRINKING WATER FOR A CONSIDERABLE PART OF THE POPULATION. THUS, THIS WORK HAS AS MAIN OBJECTIVE TO EVALUATE THE PERCEPTION OF SOCIETY ABOUT THE POTENTIAL BENEFITS FOR CAPTURING, STORING AND APPLICABILITY OF RAINWATER IN A SHO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "13APR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CAPTAÇÃO, ARMAZENAMENTO E APLICABILIDADE DE ÁGUA PLUVIAL EM UM CENTRO DE COMPRAS: UMA ANÁLISE DA PERCEPÇÃO DA SOCIEDADE"@pt ;
