    capes:hasAbstract "PROPELLED BY THEORETICAL AND METHODOLOGICAL REFLECTIONS OF THE NETWORK OF MEANINGS (REDE DE SIGNIFICAÇÕES) AND GENDER THEORIES, THIS WORK AIMED TO SCRUTINIZE THE ONTOGENY OF THE DRAG QUEEN. THE METHOD WAS BASED ON INDIVIDUAL SEMI-STRUCTURED INTERVIEWS THAT HAPPENED IN 3 DIFFERENT MOMENTS: BEFORE, DURING AND AFTER GETTING INTO DRAG. THE FIRST MEETING TOOK PLACE WITH EACH PARTICIPANT OUT OF DRAG, AND FOCUSED ON THE ORIGIN AND HISTORY OF THE DRAG QUEEN. THE SECOND MEETING HAPPENED DURING AND AFTER "@pt ;
