<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21202> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE STUDY AIMED TO UNDERSTAND THE EXPERIENCES OF ELDERLY HOMOSEXUALS THROUGHOUT THEIR LIVES, AND HOW THESE HAVE HAD CONSEQUENCES ON THEIR PERCEPTION AND/OR EXPERIENCE OF AGING. THUS, USING THE PRINCIPLES OF A QUALITATIVE RESEARCH WITH A NARRATIVE CHARACTER, I CONDUCTED IN- DEPTH INTERVIEWS WITH A BIOGRAPHICAL FOCUS WITH THREE HOMOSEXUAL MEN BETWEEN FIFTY-SIX AND SIXTY-SIX YEARS OLD. FROM THE DOUBLE-HERMENEUTICS, I SOUGHT TO REVEAL THE MEANINGS THAT THE PARTICIPANTS BUILT FROM THEIR OWN ACTIONS A"@pt ;
