<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21672> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE RESEARCH ANALYZES THE TAX EXEMPTION OF PROFITS AND DIVIDENDS AND INTEREST ON EQUITY (JCP) TAXATION, CURRENTLY STRUCTURED IN LAW 9.249/1995, EXAMINING THE AUTHORITATIVE BASIS THAT INSTITUTED IT: THE PRINCIPLE OF ECONOMIC EFFICIENCY. BASED ON A NORMATIVE AND INTERDISCIPLINARY ANALYSIS, THE REASONS WHY THE CURRENT MODEL IS ECONOMICALLY INEFFICIENT ARE POINTED OUT. THIS WORK DEMONSTRATES HOW THE CURRENT LEGISLATION CONTRADICTS THE PREMISE OF \"ATTRACTING INVESTMENTS\" ESTABLISHED IN THE EXPLANAT"@pt ;
