<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21676> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH ANALYZES THE LEGAL EFFECTIVENESS OF THE DECISION HANDED DOWN BY THE PLENARY IN THE INCIDENT OF UNCONSTITUTIONALITY CLAIM, A DECISION THAT LENDS TO MAINTENANCE OF THE LEGAL SYSTEM HEALTH, ALTHOUGH PRODUCED IN AN AUTONOMOUS INCIDENT LINKED BY HARMFULNESS TO A SUBJECTIVE PROCESS. IT CONTEXTUALIZES THAT, ALTHOUGH THE CONSTITUTIONALITY REVIEW WAS CREATED IN THE 19TH CENTURY FROM THE NORTH AMERICAN JUDICIAL REVIEW, THE 20TH CENTURY BROUGHT SUBSTANTIAL INNOVATIONS TO THE INSTITUTE, EVEN F"@pt ;
