<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21678> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PURPOSE OF THIS STUDY IS TO INVESTIGATE HOW THE PROTECTION OF DIVERSITY IN THE HUMAN GENETIC HERITAGE, BY CONSIDERING THE DISABILITY GENE AS PART OF THE GENETIC INHERITANCE OF HUMANITY, CAN WORK AS A LIMITER OF AUTONOMY IN FAMILY PLANNING IN ASSISTED PARENTING PROJECTS. IN THIS WAY, IT DISCURSIVELY STARTS FROM THE INTERPRETATION THAT IS CONCERNED WITH DISTINGUISHING WHAT WOULD BE DISABILITY AND ILLNESS/DISEASE, SINCE THE ARGUMENT THAT RESTS FOR GENETIC MANIPULATION IS THAT THE LABORATORY-GEN"@pt ;
