<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21681> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CONTEMPORARY SOCIETY, MOST SIGNIFICANTLY CHARACTERIZED BY THE OUTCOMES OF THE FOURTH INDUSTRIAL REVOLUTION, HAS INCREASINGLY MADE USE OF THE TOOLS PROVIDED BY THE NEW INFORMATION AND COMMUNICATIONS TECHNOLOGIES TO ESTABLISH RELATIONS WITHIN IT. THE EMERGENCE OF A NEW DIFFUSION MEDIUM HAS NOT HAD A NEUTRAL EFFECT; RATHER, IT HAS SHAPED OUR HABITS, SOCIAL INTERACTIONS, WAYS OF THINKING, COMMUNICATION AND EVEN LAW ITSELF. THEREFORE, DISPUTE RESOLUTION PROCESSES  WHICH REFLECT AND, SIMULTANEOUSLY, "@pt ;
