<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21691> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY AIMS TO INVESTIGATE THE CATEGORY OF TECHNOLOGICAL FETISHISM IN PLATFORM CAPITALISM AND ITS IMPACTS ON LABOR LAW. INSPIRED BY THE MARXIAN CONCEPT OF \"COMMODITY FETISHISM\", THE AIM IS TO EXTRAPOLATE THIS CONCEPT TO TODAY'S WORLD IN ORDER TO UNDERSTAND SOME OF THE \"VEIL\" THAT CAPITALISM PRINTS OVER SOCIAL RELATIONS IN AN ATTEMPT TO ALWAYS HIDE THE FACT THAT, SINCE ITS ORIGINS, BEHIND COMMODITIES AND EXCHANGE RELATIONS BETWEEN THINGS, THERE IS HUMAN LABOR AS A VITAL AND CRUCIAL SOURCE OF "@pt ;
