    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/DIREITO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21697> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WITH ITS OWN METHODOLOGICAL CHAPTER, EXPLORING THE RELEVANCE OF STUDIES IN COMPARATIVE CONSTITUTIONAL LAW FOR THE ENRICHMENT OF NATIONAL ACADEMIC KNOWLEDGE, THIS RESEARCH OFFERS A COMPARATIVE INVESTIGATION BETWEEN THE CONSTITUTIONAL JUSTICE SYSTEMS IN FRANCE AND BRAZIL. STARTING FROM THE ANALYSIS OF THE SYSTEM ADOPTED IN FRANCE, GOING THROUGH ITS INSTITUTES AND HISTORICAL ORIGINS, AS WELL AS THE LEGAL REVOLUTION CAUSED BY THE ADOPTION OF THE PRIORITY QUESTION OF CONSTITUTIONALITY (QPC) IN THE CO"@pt ;
