<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21702> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DURING THE COLD WAR THERE WAS A TECHNOLOGICAL EXPANSION IN THE SPACE AREA, IN AN EMINENTLY PUBLIC WAY, GENERATING THE NEED TO REGULATE THE FIRST TREATIES ON THE MATTER. SUBSEQUENTLY, PRIVATE AGENTS WERE CONSOLIDATING IN THE SECTOR, MAINLY IN PARTNERSHIP WITH THE STATES. HOWEVER, THE EXISTING SPACE TREATIES DO NOT SATISFACTORILY COVER BUSINESS PARTICIPATION IN THE EXPLOITATION OF SPACE RESOURCES, WHICH CAUSES LEGAL UNCERTAINTY. WITH THE AIM OF CREATING COOPERATION NETWORKS BETWEEN SPACE AGENCIES,"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "OS ACORDOS DE ÁRTEMIS E A EXPLORAÇÃO DOS RECURSOS ESPACIAIS: UM ESTUDO SOBRE A COMPATIBILIDADE COM O DIREITO INTERNACIONAL ESPACIAL"@pt ;
