<http://example.com/capes#thesis/21715> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE INFORMATION SOCIETY HAS AS A CLEAR CHARACTERISTIC THE MODIFICATION OF THE ECONOMIC, POLITICAL, SOCIAL AND CULTURAL STRUCTURES OF THE COUNTRIES AND THE CREATION OF THE NEED TO ESTABLISH NEW POLICIES. THIS INFORMATIONAL MAGNITUDE GAVE RISE TO BIG DATA, WHICH IS A PHENOMENON BY WHICH DATA IS PRODUCED IN DIFFERENT FORMATS AND STORED IN A LARGE NUMBER OF DEVICES AND EQUIPMENT. THIS CONTEXT TRIGGERS NEW SCIENCES, AS IS THE CASE OF DATA SCIENCE, WHICH FOCUSES ON THE OBSERVATION AND STUDY OF THE LIF"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27JUN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "A RELAÇÃO DO USO DO BIGDATA E DA DATASCIENCE NO PROCESSO DECISÓRIO PARA A PRODUÇÃO DE CONHECIMENTO, TECNOLOGIA E INOVAÇÃO: UMA ANÁLISE EM INSTITUTOS DE CIÊNCIA E TECNOLOGIA DE PERNAMBUCO"@pt ;
