<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22321> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE MANGALARGA BREED ORIGINATED FROM THE CROSS BETWEEN LOCALLY ADAPTED MARES AND PORTUGUESE HORSES FROM THE ALTER STUD FARM. DUE TO THE SPORTIVE ABILITY AND DIAGONAL AND COMFORTABLE GAIT OF THESE ANIMALS, THE BREED SOON BECAME POPULAR. THE EXPANSION OF THE MANGALARGA HERD AND THE EMERGENCE OF NEW BREEDERS INTENSIFIED THE SELECTION, MAKING THE PROCESS MORE PROFESSIONAL AND LEADING TO THE CREATION OF THE BRAZILIAN ASSOCIATION OF MANGALARGA BREED HORSE BREEDERS (ABCCRM). SINCE THE FOUNDATION OF ABC"@pt ;
