<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22689> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS WORK EVALUATED SIX NATIVE WOOD SPECIES OF THE CAATINGA FROM THE ANATOMICAL, PHYSICAL AND MECHANICAL POINTS OF VIEW. FOR THIS, SEVEN TREES PER SPECIES WERE COLLECTED, BEING THESE: ANGICO (ANADENANTHERA COLUBRINA VAR. CEBIL), AROEIRA (MYRACRODRUON URUNDEUVA), CUMARU (AMBURANA CEARENSIS), IMBURANA (COMMIPHORA LEPTOPHOLEOS), MORORÓ (BAUHINIA CHEILANTHA) AND PEREIRO (ASPIDOSPERMA PYRIFOLIUM). REGARDING THE ANATOMICAL MEASUREMENTS, THE FOLLOWING WERE DETERMINED: THE DIMENSIONS OF CELLULAR ELEMENT"@pt ;
