    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_DOS_MATERIAIS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22690> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN BRAZIL, ARBOVIRUSES ARE A SERIOUS PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM. CURRENTLY, THE FIGHT AGAINST THE AEDES AEGYPTI (AE. AEGYPTI) VECTOR IS CARRIED OUT THROUGH THE APPLICATION OF INSECTICIDES, WHICH CAUSE RESISTANCE IN MOSQUITOES, REQUIRING THEIR REPLACEMENT. AMONG THE POSSIBILITIES OF NATURAL PRODUCTS, THE ESSENTIAL OIL EXTRACTED FROM THE LEAVES OF COMMIPHORA LEPTOPHLOEOS (MART.) J. B. GILLETT. (OECL), NATIVE TO BRAZIL AND FOUND IN THE CAATINGA, POPULARLY KNOWN AS IMBURANA-DE-CAMBÃO. HOWEVER, TO PROTECT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "14FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE COMPRIMIDO BIOLARVICIDA À BASE DE NANOCOMPÓSITO ARGILOSO/ÓLEO ESSENCIAL DA COMMIPHORA LEPTOPHLOEOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/MADALENA_MACHADO_ROCHA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_DOS_MATERIAIS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22691> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN BRAZIL THERE ARE AREAS WHERE DRINKING WATER IS SCARCE, MAINLY IN THE SEMIARID REGION, WHERE THE AVERAGE ANNUAL PRECIPITATION IS LOW (<500 MM/YEAR). AN ALTERNATIVE TO OBTAIN DRINKING WATER IS THROUGH GROUNDWATER. HOWEVER, CONTAMINATION OR HIGH SALT CONTENT IN THE SEMIARID REGION PREVENT ITS USE FOR HUMAN CONSUMPTION AND AGRICULTURAL ACTIVITIES. THE MAIN INORGANIC SALTS PRESENT IN BRACKISH WATER ARE NACL AND CACL2. THE MOST WIDELY USED METHOD FOR THE REMOVAL OF SALINE RESIDUES IS THROUGH REVERS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "31JAN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE HIDROGEL DE CARBOXIMETILCELULOSEETILENODIAMINA PARA REMOÇÃO SALINA EM MEIO AQUOSO"@pt ;
