    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_DOS_MATERIAIS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22694> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THIS WORK, CRYSTALLINE CERAMIC POWDERS OF YTTRIUM OXIDE DOPED WITH EU3+ WERE PRODUCED THROUGH COMBUSTION AND HYDROTHERMAL SYNTHESIS METHODS USING THREE DIFFERENT FUELS, AIMING TO RELATE, COMPARE AND EVALUATE THE INFLUENCE OF METHODS AND FUELS ON MORPHOLOGICAL, STRUCTURAL AND LUMINESCENT PROPERTIES OF THE SYNTHESIZED CRYSTALLITES. THE CHARACTERIZATION BY SCANNING ELECTRON MICROSCOPY ASSOCIATED WITH ENERGY DISPERSION X-RAY SPECTROSCOPY ALLOWED THE VISUALIZATION OF THE MORPHOLOGY OF THE SURFACES"@pt ;
