<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22703> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE CULTIVATION OF GRAPEVINES IN THE AGRESTE MERIDIONAL PERNAMBUCO HAS SHOWN GOOD RESULTS REGARDING PRODUCTIVITY AND FINAL QUALITY CHARACTERISTICS OF THE GRAPES AND WINE. IN THE MANAGEMENT OF A TERROIR, THE NUTRITION OF THE PLANTS IS OF UTMOST IMPORTANCE, BECAUSE IT HAS A GREAT INFLUENCE ON THE PLANTS, AND THE LEAVES ARE THE GREATEST INDICATORS OF DEFICIENCIES. THE XRAY FLUORESCENCE TECHNIQUE IS A METHOD THAT ANALYZES SAMPLES NON-DESTRUCTIVELY AND REQUIRES ONLY A SMALL AMOUNT OF SAMPLES. AIMING "@pt ;
