<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22705> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BEAN IS PART OF THE DIET OF MOST BRAZILIANS, ITS USE GOES BEYOND HUMAN FOOD AND CAN BE USED IN ANIMAL FEED AND AS GREEN MANURE. IN BRAZIL THE METHOD OF CONVENTIONAL PLANTING THROUGH THE USE OF CHEMICALS PREDOMINATES, THUS THE NEED ARISES FOR NEW ALTERNATIVES THAT ARE MORE ECONOMICAL, COMBINED WITH AN INCREASINGLY HIGH PRODUCTION. THUS, THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS WORK WAS TO EVALUATE THE EFFECT OF THE APPLICATION OF DIFFERENT DOSES OF LIQUID EFFLUENT FROM DAIRY PRODUCTS, ASSOCIATED WITH INOCULANT "@pt ;
