<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22706> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SOUTHERN AGRESTE REGION OF PERNAMBUCO IS AN IMPORTANT AGRICULTURAL HUB IN PERNAMBUCO. HOWEVER, THIS REGION SUFFERS FROM THE ENVIRONMENTAL LIMITATIONS RESULTING FROM THE SEMI-ARID CLIMATE. AGRICULTURE IS MAINLY CARRIED OUT DURING THE RAINY SEASON UNDER THE RAINFED REGIME, WITH SCARCITY AS A MAJOR CHALLENGE. IN ADDITION TO CLIMATIC ADVERSITIES, AGRICULTURE ALSO SUFFERS FROM SOILS IN POOR CONDITIONS, MOST OF WHICH ARE DEGRADED. BIOCHAR IS A POTENTIAL ORGANIC COMPOUND FOR THE MAINTENANCE OF AGRO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "29JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
