<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22707> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE BIOCHAR ITS A BYPRODUCT RICH IN CARBON AND THAT PROVIDES ALTERATIONS IN THE SOIL CHARACTERS AND CROP PRODUCTIVITY. THE BIOCHAR IS OBTAINED BY THE PROCESS OF PYROLYSIS OF MANY TYPES OF BIOMASSES, BEING THAT THE PRODUCTION OF BIOCHAR FROM POULTRY WASTE HAS BECOME A AN ENVIRONMENTALLY INTERESTING STRATEGY FOR THE MANAGEMENT OF POTENTIALLY POLLUTING WASTE. THE EFFECT OF THIS WORK WAS TO EVALUATE THE PHYSICAL EFFECT OF BIOCHAR ON THE WATER CHARACTERISTICS AND OBJECTIVE OF THE SOIL EFFECT AND ON "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "30MAY2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "EFEITO DO BIOCHAR DE CAMA DE FRANGO NAS CARACTERÍSTICAS QUÍMICAS E FÍSICO-HÍDRICAS DO SOLO E PRODUTIVIDADE DO FEIJOEIRO"@pt ;
