<http://example.com/capes#thesis/228> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE FACT THAT BRAZIL WAS THE LAST NATION IN THE WORLD TO ABOLISH SLAVERY LARGELY JUSTIFIES THE PERSISTENCE OF RACISM AS A SOCIAL PRACTICE, AND ONE CAN EVEN SPEAK OF THE EXISTENCE OF STRUCTURAL RACISM. DESPITE TRADITIONAL HISTORIOGRAPHY APPROACHING ENSLAVEMENT AS A PROCESS OFSUBMISSION WITHOUT RESISTANCE, RESEARCH SHOWS THAT THE ESCAPES AND INSURRECTIONS OF ENSLAVED PEOPLE WERE CONSTANT SINCE THE BEGINNING OF COLONIZATION, AND RESULTED IN THE FORMATION OF QUILOMBOS PRESENT THROUGHOUT THE BRAZILIA"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
