<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22914> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "STUDIES ON AFRICAN-BRAZILIAN RELIGIONS, ALSO CALLED RELIGIONS OF TERREIRO OR AFRICAN-AMERINDIAN RELIGIONS, LIKE I CHOOSE TO USE HERE, HAVE FERTILE TERRAINS IN THE FIELDS OF SOCIOLOGY, ANTHROPOLOGY AND SCIENCE OF RELIGION IN BRAZIL, IN WHICH DIVERSE RESEARCHES AND DEBATES HAVE BEEN DEVELOPED FOR AT LEAST A CENTURY, SINCE THE PIONEERING TEXTS BY MARANHÃO-BORN DOCTOR AND ANTHROPOLOGIST NINA RODRIGUES. THE SAME CANNOT BE SAID ABOUT THE PLACE OCCUPIED BY THESE STUDIES IN THE HISTORIOGRAPHY. FOR A LON"@pt ;
