<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22961> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PHARMACOTHERAPY PROMOTES QUALITY OF LIFE, DESPITE THE BENEFICIAL EFFECTS, DRUGS CAN AFFECT USERS WITH NEGATIVE EFFECTS, ADVERSE DRUG EVENTS, WHICH WHEN SEVERE CAN CAUSE MORTALITY AND INCREASED HEALTH COSTS. IN THIS SENSE, THE STUDY AIMS TO ANALYZE THE NATIONAL PANORAMA OF NOTIFICATIONS OF ADVERSE DRUG EVENTS. METHODOLOGY: A RETROSPECTIVE, CROSS-SECTIONAL, OBSERVATIONAL STUDY WAS CARRIED OUT, WITH THE ANALYSIS OF THE ANVISA DATABASE. RESULTS: THE ANALYSIS OF THE DATABASE COLLECTED INFORMATION BET"@pt ;
