<http://example.com/capes#thesis/22969> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC HAS IMPACTED COMMUNITY CARE PRACTICE. PHARMACISTS ACTED ON THE COMMUNITY FRONTLINE OF PREVENTION, PREPAREDNESS, RESPONSE AND RECOVERY EXERCISES. COMMUNITY PHARMACIES HAD TO REORGANIZE AND ADAPT TO THE NEW CONTEXT, IMPLEMENTING SEVERAL DIFFERENT INTERVENTIONS AND MEASURES IN A SHORT PERIOD OF TIME. THE PRESENT RESEARCH AIMED TO CHARACTERIZE THE PANORAMA OF ACTION OF PHARMACEUTICAL AND PHARMACEUTICAL COMPANIES FROM EXPOSURE TO THE FACE OF THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC. THE STUDY WAS "@pt ;
