<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23053> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "URBAN PARKS ARE PLACES THAT OFFER QUALITY OF LIFE FOR THE POPULATION LIVING IN URBAN CENTERS, SINCE THEY ARE ENVIRONMENTS FOR SOCIALIZATION, RECREATION, PRACTICE OF SPORTS ACTIVITIES, LEISURE, AND ALLOW THE USER TO HAVE CONTACT WITH NATURE, EVEN LIVING IN CITIES. AND DURING THE PERIOD OF CONFINEMENT CAUSED BY THE PANDEMIC, THE POPULATION OF THE CITIES STARTED TO VALUE EVEN MORE THE IMPORTANCE OF HAVING THESE ENVIRONMENTS CLOSE TO THEIR HOMES. THUS, THE PRESENT WORK HAS AS A GENERAL OBJECTIVE TO "@pt ;
