<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23058> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WHEY IS ONE OF THE MAIN COMPONENTS OF LIQUID EFFLUENTS GENERATED BY CHEESE-PRODUCING DAIRY INDUSTRIES, AND CAN BE CONSIDERED A PROBLEM IF THERE IS NO ADEQUATE MANAGEMENT STRATEGY. BY KEEPING MOST OF THE NUTRIENTS FROM WHOLE MILK, WHEY CAN BE USED IN THE FOOD INDUSTRY, BEING PART OF THE COMPONENTS OF OTHER PRODUCTS. THUS, THIS WORK AIMED TO DEVELOP A FERMENTED, WHEYBASED ALCOHOLIC BEVERAGE, MEAD-LIKE, AS WELL AS TO CARRY OUT ITS PHYSICAL-CHEMICAL CHARACTERIZATION, EVALUATE ITS SENSORY ACCEPTANCE"@pt ;
