<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23394> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "OBSERVE PHENOMENA, RAISE QUESTIONS, TEST HYPOTHESES, SYSTEMATIZE INFORMATION. IT IS AT THESE POINTS THAT THE TEACHER CAN ORGANIZE ACTIVITIES WITH REFERENCE TO THE TEACHING OF BIOLOGY BY INVESTIGATION. IN THIS WAY, THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO DEVELOP STUDENT PROTAGONISM IN A PROPOSAL OF TEACHING BY INVESTIGATION TO APPROACH THE CONTENT FIRST AID (FA) IN THE DISCIPLINE OF BIOLOGY. THEREFORE, THIS WORK IS A DESCRIPTIVE, LONGITUDINAL STUDY, OF AN APPLIED NATURE, WITH A QUALITATIVE AND QUANTITATIVE APPROACH"@pt ;
