<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23570> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE MODELING OF CROP YIELD SIMULATION IS AN ALTERNATIVE TO ASSIST IN THE STUDY AND RECOMMENDATION OF THE BEST WATER TECHNIQUES, THAT IS, PRACTICES OF WATER USE EFFICIENCY IN AGRICULTURE. ADEMAIS, AVALIAR AS MELHORES ESTRATÉGIAS PARA A PRODUÇÃO DE FORRAGEM EM REGIÕES DE CLIMA SEMÁRIDO É DE GRANDE RELEVÂNCIA, CONSIDERANDO AS CARACTERÍSTICAS AMBIENTAIS E A VULNERABILIDADE SOCIAL DESSAS ÁREAS. THE AIM OF THIS RESEARCH WAS TO APPLY THE AQUACROP-FAO MODEL TO DIFFERENT FORAGE PLANT PRODUCTION SYSTEMS, "@pt ;
