    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOCIÊNCIA_ANIMAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23757> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CLINICAL STAGING CAN HELP TO BETTER UNDERSTAND THE PATIENT'S PROGNOSIS AND DECISION MAKING IN THE TREATMENT OF DOGS WITH CANINE VISCERAL LEISHMANIASIS (CVL). THUS, THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO PERFORM CLINICAL STAGING OF DOGS WITH NATURAL INFECTION BY LEISHMANIA INFANTUM AND COMPARE THE PROFILE OF SEROLOGICAL TESTS WITH THE DIFFERENT STAGES OF CVL. FOR THAT, DOMICILED DOGS OF BOTH SEXES AND DIFFERENT AGES WERE USED, WITH A POSITIVE DIAGNOSIS FOR CVL THROUGH BONE MARROW BIOPSY. CLINICAL STAGING WAS PERFO"@pt ;
