<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23758> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO EVALUATE THE OCCURRENCE OF IGG ANTI-TOXOPLASMA GONDII ANTIBODIES AND THE DNA OF PROTOZOA OF THE SARCOSCYSTIDAE FAMILY IN BIRDS AND WILD MAMMALS FROM THE CAATINGA BIOME AND FROM THE PERNAMBUCO WILD ANIMAL SCREENING CENTER (CETRAS-TANGARA) IN THE ATLANTIC FOREST. IN THE FIRST STUDY, THE INVESTIGATION OF ANTIBODIES AGAINST T. GONDII AND DNA OF PROTOZOA OF THE FAMILY SARCOCYSTIDAE WAS CARRIED OUT IN 55 FREE-LIVING ANIMALS FROM THE CAATINGA BIOME USING THE MAT TECHNIQUE AND NESTE"@pt ;
