<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23759> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT STUDY PROVIDES EPIDEMIOLOGICAL DATA ON LUNGWORM INFECTION IN RUMINANTS IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO, INCLUDING THE FOLLOWING ASPECTS: 1) EPIDEMIOLOGICAL, MORPHOLOGICAL, AND MOLECULAR DATA ON THE LUNGWORM LARVA OF A SPECIES OF PROTOSTRONGYLUS FROM GOATS. FECAL SAMPLES FROM GOATS (N = 217) WERE ANALYZED BY THE BAERMANN TECHNIQUE AND LARVAE WERE DETECTED IN 18.9% (41/217) OF THE SAMPLES. THESE LARVAE HAD A MEAN LENGTH OF 339¿M (±52.99¿M) AND A MEAN WIDTH OF 18 ¿M (±1.46¿M). MORPHOLOGICALL"@pt ;
