<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23764> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AIM OF THIS RESEARCH WAS TO CARRY OUT AN EPIDEMIOLOGICAL STUDY OF BURKHOLDERIA MALLEI INFECTION IN EQUINES FROM PROPERTIES IN PERNAMBUCO AND ALAGOAS STATES. FOR THE EPIDEMIOLOGICAL STUDY, INVESTIGATIVE QUESTIONNAIRES WERE APPLIED TO 6 OUTBREAK PROPERTIES (2017-2021) AND 11 NON-FOCUS PROPERTIES, AND STATISTICAL ANALYSIS OF THE FACTORS ASSOCIATED WITH GLANDERS'S OCCURRENCE WAS PERFORMED. IN THE STUDY, A SIGNIFICANT ASSOCIATION WAS OBSERVED FOR THE FOLLOWING VARIABLES: PURPOSE OF BREEDING (TRAD"@pt ;
