<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23765> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ANTIMICROBIAL RESISTANCE IS ONE OF THE MAIN THREATS TO PUBLIC HEALTH. STAPHYLOCOCCUS AUREUS RESISTANT TO DIFFERENT CLASSES OF ANTIMICROBIALS IS A PRIORITY FOR THE IMPLEMENTATION OF PREVENTIVE MEASURES. THEREFORE, THE OBJECTIVE OF THE STUDY WAS TO IDENTIFY THE BACTERIUM IN DOGS AND CATS, IN HUMANS WITH CLOSE CONTACT WITH THESE ANIMALS (GUARDIANS AND VETERINARIANS), VETERINARY INSTRUMENTS AND VETERINARY HOSPITAL SURFACES ENVIRONMENT, TO EVALUATE THE GENOTYPIC AND PHENOTYPIC PROFILE OF ANTIMICROBIA"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "IDENTIFICAÇÃO E PERFIL DE RESISTÊNCIA FENOTÍPICO E GENOTÍPICO DE STAPHYLOCOCCUS AUREUS ISOLADOS DE MÉDICOS VETERINÁRIOS, TUTORES, ANIMAIS E AMBIENTE HOSPITALAR NA CIDADE DO RECIFE, BRASIL"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/DENNY_PARENTE_DE_SA_BARRETO_MAIA_LEITE> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOCIÊNCIA_ANIMAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23766> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO DESCRIBE THE SITUATIONAL ANALYSIS OF EXOGENOUS INTOXICATIONS AND TO CARRY OUT HEALTH EDUCATION ACTIONS IN THE MUNICIPALITIES BELONGING TO THE V HEALTH REGION OF THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO, BRAZIL. A DESCRIPTIVE QUANTITATIVE AND QUALITATIVE EPIDEMIOLOGICAL STUDY WAS CARRIED OUT. IN THE FIRST STAGE, DATA FROM THE INFORMATION SYSTEM ON NOTIFIABLE DISEASES (SINAN) AND THE INFORMATION SYSTEM ON MORTALITY (SIM), FROM 2008 TO 2018 ON EXOGENOUS INTOXICATIONS, WERE ANALYZE"@pt ;
