<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23768> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS AIMED TO DESCRIBE THE DISTRIBUTION OF THE INCIDENCE OF ARBOVIRUSES AND MORTALITY INDICATORS IN THE POPULATION OF THE 12 DEVELOPMENT REGIONS OF PERNAMBUCO FROM 2015 TO 2018. AN EPIDEMIOLOGICAL, OBSERVATIONAL, CROSS-SECTIONAL AND DESCRIPTIVE STUDY OF PROBABLE CASES AND CONFIRMED DEATHS FROM ARBOVIRUSES WAS CARRIED OUT. THE ANALYZED DATA ARE SECONDARY, COLLECTED AT THE STATE HEALTH DEPARTMENT (SES-PE), THE CASES WERE EXTRACTED FROM THE INFORMATION SYSTEMS OF THE MINISTRY OF HEALTH (SINA"@pt ;
