    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIODIVERSIDADE_E_CONSERVAÇÃO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23873> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "\"THE LAMBARI, ASTYANAX LACUSTRIS, IS A FISH THAT HAS A WIDE DISTRIBUTION, BEING FOUND IN SEVERAL WATER BODIES OF THE SEMI-ARID REGION OF THE NORTHEAST. HOWEVER, THERE IS A LACK OF BASIC KNOWLEDGE ABOUT THE CHARACTERIZATION OF THEIR NATURAL DIET IN THE NORTHEAST REGION. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO ANALYZE THE FEEDING OF THE SPECIES A. LACUSTRIS FROM DIFFERENT WATER BODIES OF THE PAJEÚ RIVER BASIN, CORRELATING IT WITH ENVIRONMENTAL CHARACTERISTICS. THE COLLECTIONS WERE CARRIED OUT IN SIX AQ"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "BIOLOGIA REPRODUTIVA E ALIMENTAÇÃO DO PEIXE LAMBARI, ASTYANAX LACUSTRIS (LÜTKEN, 1875) (CHARACIFORMES: CHARACIDAE) NA BACIA DO RIO PAJEÚ, PERNAMBUCO"@pt ;
