<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23874> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH OBJECTIVE THE DIAGNOSIS OF MELIPONICULTURE IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO TO PROPOSE A DRAFT FOR DEBATE BETWEEN BREEDERS AND INSTITUTIONS TO BUILD STATE LEGISLATION ON THE MANAGEMENT OF NATIVE BEES. THE ANALYZED RESULTS WERE COMPARED WITH A CENSUS CARRIED OUT IN THE STATE OF RIO GRANDE DO NORTE, CEARÁ, WITH ANOTHER DIAGNOSIS. OUR STUDIES SHOW THAT, AS THEY OCCUR IN THE STATES OF BRAZIL, STINGLESS BEEKEEPING IS LACKS TECHNOLOGY. MOST MELIPONARIES ARE LOCATED ON SMALL PROPERTIES, AND BEE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "31MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DIAGNÓSTICO DA MELIPONICULTURA DO ESTADO DE PERNAMBUCO: NOVOS MERCADOS E LEGISLAÇÃO"@pt ;
