<http://example.com/capes#thesis/23880> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "\"STINGLESS BEES (APIDAE, MELIPONINI) ARE RATIONALLY BRED INSECTS THAT ARE AN ESSENTIAL SOURCE FOR PROVIDING ENVIRONMENTAL POLLINATION SERVICES TO NATURAL ENVIRONMENTS AND AGROECOSYSTEMS. WITH PERENNIAL COLONIES, LARGE NUMBERS OF INDIVIDUALS, HIGH SPECIES RICHNESS, INABILITY TO STING AND EASILY MANAGED, THE RATIONAL BREEDING OF THESE ANIMALS HAS A HUGE MARKET STILL LITTLE EXPLORED. THE HIGH DEMAND THAT BEEKEEPERS WILL HAVE FOR THE SUPPLY OF NESTS SOON, HOWEVER, COMES UP AGAINST THE ABILITY TO ART"@pt ;
