<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24040> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO CARRY OUT THE HISTOLOGICAL CHARACTERIZATION AND HISTOMORPHOMETRICALLY EVALUATE THE ACCESSORY SEX GLANDS OF CATTLE, VERIFYING THE INFLAMMATORY CHANGES FOUND. FOR THIS, SETS OF ACCESSORY SEX GLANDS CONTAINING VESICULAR GLANDS, AMPOULES AND PROSTATES WERE COLLECTED FROM 40 ANIMALS AT THE SLAUGHTERHOUSE IN THE CITY OF GARANHUNS-PE. IN THE FIRST STUDY, THE VESICULAR GLANDS WERE DESCRIPTIVELY EVALUATED AND THE NUMBER OF ACINI WAS COUNTED IN AN AREA OF 25MM². THE PRES"@pt ;
