<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24210> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS WORK AIMS TO ANALYZE THE APPROPRIATION OF MATHEMATICS TEACHERS REGARDING THE USE OF GAMES TO TEACH FIRST-DEGREE EQUATIONS PROPOSED IN BOOKS FOR THE 7TH GRADE OF SECONDARY SCHOOL. WE TAKE AS REFERENCE THE APPROPRIATION MODEL OF A NEW RESOURCE, STRUCTURED IN THREE PHASES: PREAPPROPRIATION, ORIGINAL APPROPRIATION, AND REAPPROPRIATION. THIS MODEL IS BASED IN THE INSTRUMENTAL APPROACH, DOCUMENTAL APPROACH, AND IN THE INSTRUMENTAL ORCHESTRATION, BESIDES PROFESSIONAL TEACHING KNOWLEDGE. WE DEVELOP"@pt ;
