    capes:hasAbstract "THE THESIS WORK PRESENTED HERE AIMS TO IDENTIFY THE ROLE OF NOOSPHERE IN THE FACE OF PROPOSITIONS FOR TEACHING ALGEBRA IN THE EARLY YEARS OF ELEMENTARY EDUCATION IN THE NATIONAL CURRICULUM FRAMEWORK FOR MATHEMATICS. IN THIS WAY, WE SURROUND OURSELVES WITH THE THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK WITH THE IDEAS OF DIDACTIC TRANSPOSITION (CHEVALLARD, 1991), IN WHICH HE BRINGS THE CONCEPT OF NOOSPHERE AND WITH THE ANTHROPOLOGICAL THEORY OF DIDACTICS (CHEVALLARD, 1999) WHICH PRESENTS CONCEPTS THAT DEEPEN THE DIDAC"@pt ;
