<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24746> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK AIMED TO EVALUATE THE ADAPTABILITY AND PRODUCTIVE STABILITY OF BLACK BEAN GENOTYPES IN SEVEN ENVIRONMENTS, IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO, ACCORDING TO THE METHODOLOGIES OF LIN AND BINNS AND AMMI. THE EXPERIMENTS WERE CARRIED OUT IN 2011 IN ARARIPINA, SÃO JOÃO, BELÉM DE SÃO FRANCISCO, PETROLINA AND CARUARU; AND IN 2012, IN THE MUNICIPALITIES OF BELÉM DE SÃO FRANCISCO AND PETROLINA, WITH EACH ENVIRONMENT BEING DETERMINED BY THE COMBINATION OF LOCATION X YEAR OF CULTIVATION. THE EXPER"@pt ;
