<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24751> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK WAS CARRIED OUT WITH THE FOLLOWING OBJECTIVES: (A) TO VERIFY IF THERE IS GENETIC VARIABILITY IN PIGEON PEA COLLECTION FOR IMPORTANT CHARACTERS IN FORAGE PRODUCTION, AS WELL AS TO ESTIMATE GENETIC PARAMETERS. IN ADDITION TO IDENTIFYING GENOTYPES WITH POTENTIAL FORAGE USE IN THE SOIL AND CLIMATE CONDITIONS OF THE CARIRI PARAIBANO REGION, IN ORDER TO GUIDE THE LATER STAGES OF THE BREEDING PROGRAM AND (B) DETERMINE IF THERE IS A BETTER TIME/PERIOD OF THE DAY TO CARRY OUT ARTIFICIAL "@pt ;
