<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24754> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE VINE IS ONE OF THE MOST IMPORTANT CROPS OF BRAZILIAN FRUIT GROWING, ITS GROWING MARKET SHARE HAS DRIVEN AND EXPANDED PRODUCTION IN BRAZILIAN TERRITORY, ESPECIALLY IN THE SEMI- ARID REGION. IN THIS REGION, THE SEMI-ARID CLIMATE IS PREDOMINANT, HAVING AS CHARACTERISTIC MODERATE PERIODS OF DRY WEATHER THAT CAUSES WATER DEFICIT, ONE OF THE ABIOTIC FACTORS THAT HAS MOST CONTRIBUTED TO THE REDUCTION OF PRODUCTION IN THE FIELD, WHICH MAY LEAD TO LOW PRODUCTIVITY IN VINE CULTIVATION. PLANT GENETIC I"@pt ;
