<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24795> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "GOAT AND SHEEP FARMING IN THE BRAZILIAN NORTHEAST IS AN ACTIVITY THAT MOBILIZES THE REGION'S ECONOMY. IN THIS PRODUCTION, HANDCRAFTED MILK AND DAIRY PRODUCTS ARE PRODUCTS THAT STAND OUT AND HAVE A COMMERCIAL VALUE, MAINLY BECAUSE IT IS A FOOD OF HIGH BIOLOGICAL VALUE, CONTAINING A COMPOSITION RICH IN ESSENTIAL NUTRIENTS. HOWEVER, THERE IS STILL RESISTANCE REGARDING THE SENSORY ACCEPTANCE OF DAIRY PRODUCTS, WHICH IS JUSTIFIED BY THE STRONG TYPICAL FLAVOR AND MICROBIOLOGICAL INSECURITY. THEREFORE,"@pt ;
