<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24878> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE INFORMATION AND COMMUNICATION TECHNOLOGIES HAS HAD AN IMPACT ON THE DISTANCE BETWEEN PEOPLE AND THE WAY INFORMATION IS SOUGHT IN DIFFERENT PARTS OF THE WORLD, THUS REDUCING THE ISOLATION BETWEEN PEOPLE AND ALLOWING ACCESS TO INFORMATION BEFORE IT IS DIFFICULT TO ACCESS. CONSIDERING THIS VIEW IT IS POSSIBLE TO SAY THAT COMPUTERIZED COLLABORATION SYSTEMS HAVE A SIGNIFICANT IMPACT ON THE PROPAGATION OF INFORMATION AND USERS INTERESTED IN INCREASING THE NUMBER OF INFORMATION, FOR VARIOUS REASONS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22APR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SISTEMA COLABORATIVO PARA USUÁRIOS ENVOLVIDOS COM MUCOPOLISSACARIDOSE VI: UM ESTUDO DE CASO COM PROFISSIONAIS DE SAÚDE PÚBLICA"@pt ;
