<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24881> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CLOUD COMPUTING IS EMERGING AS THE MAIN MECHANISM FOR PROCESSING LARGE AMOUNTS OF DATA. IN THIS CONTEXT, PRIVATE CLOUDS PROVIDE EFFICIENT INFRASTRUCTURES THAT SUPPORT THE ANALYSIS OF DATA SETS GENERATED BY DIFFERENT SOURCES, SUCH AS SOCIAL NETWORKS, HEALTH DATA, AND CLIMATOLOGY DATA. UNDERSTANDING HOW BIG DATA PARSING BEHAVES IN PRIVATE CLOUD ENVIRONMENTS IS AN IMPORTANT APPROACH TO IDENTIFYING CRITICAL PERFORMANCE AND COST FACTORS IN THESE ENVIRONMENTS. PERFORMANCE AND COST EVALUATION PROVIDES "@pt,
        "NOWADAYS, THE GREAT CHALLENGE FOR PUBLIC ORGANIZATIONS IS TO PROMOTE A MANAGEMENT CAPABLE OF DIALOGUING WITH THE INTERESTS OF CITIZENS, ACHIEVING PLANNED RESULTS AND MATERIALIZING THE STRATEGIC OBJECTIVES FOR INSTITUTIONAL STRENGTHENING AND THE PROVISION OF PUBLIC SERVICES CONCERNED WITH SOCIAL AND SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT. FOR THIS, IN ADDITION TO STRENGTHENING THE MANAGERIAL SKILLS OF MANAGERS AND PUBLIC SERVANTS, IT IS NECESSARY TO BRING TOGETHER AN EFFECTIVE COMBINATION OF STRATEGY, CONTROL A"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "13JAN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "29APR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
