<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24889> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT STUDY IS INTENDED TO PROPOSE THE SCOPE FOR THE CREATION OF A SUSTAINABLE CERTIFICATION, SUPPORTED BY THE USE OF DIGITAL TECHNOLOGIES, FROM THE PERSPECTIVE OF THE EVOLUTION OF SUSTAINABILITY MEASURES THAT GUIDE CERTIFICATIONS AND WITH A FOCUS ON DIGITAL TECHNOLOGIES THAT SUPPORT SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT. FOLLOWING A SCRIPT BASED ON THREE ARTICLES OF ITS OWN AUTHORSHIP, THIS DISSERTATION MAKES A SEQUENCE OF STEPS, WHERE THE FIRST TWO ARTICLES SUPPORT THE ELABORATION OF THE THIRD ARTICLE"@pt ;
