    capes:hasAbstract "THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC AND THE LOCKDOWN MEASURES TO HALT THE VIRUS SPREAD LED TO MAJOR SOCIO-ENVIRONMENTAL AND ECONOMIC IMPACTS ACROSS THE PLANET. THIS RESEARCH AIMED TO ANALYZE SUCH IMPACTS, BOTH AT A GLOBAL AND LOCAL SCALE, IN ORDER TO PROVIDE TOOLS FOR DEVELOPING AND IMPLEMENTING MORE EFFECTIVE SOCIAL AND ENVIRONMENTAL PUBLIC POLICIES TO FACE THE POST- PANDEMIC WORLD. AT A GLOBAL SCALE, A SYSTEMATIC LITERATURE REVIEW ON THE SOCIO- ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACTS OF THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC AND ITS ECONOMIC"@pt ;
