<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24894> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS DISSERTATION, ORGANIZED IN MULTIPAPER FORMAT, WAS DEVELOPED WITHIN THE SCOPE OF THE GRADUATE PROGRAM IN MANAGEMENT OF SUSTAINABLE LOCAL DEVELOPMENT AT THE UNIVERSITY OF PERNAMBUCO - FACULTY OF ADMINISTRATION AND LAW - (GDLS/FCAP), AS PART OF THE RESEARCH LINE ENVIRONMENTAL AND SOCIAL ASPECTS OF SUSTAINABLE LOCAL DEVELOPMENT. ITS GENERAL OBJECTIVE WAS TO LEARN ABOUT ENVIRONMENTAL EDUCATION ACTIONS IN THE CITY OF RECIFE THAT SIGNAL THE EXPERIENCE OF TRANSDISCIPLINARITY. THE SPECIFIC OBJECTIVE"@pt ;
