<http://example.com/capes#thesis/24895> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE (AI) HAS HAD A SIGNIFICANT IMPACT ON THE LEGAL SECTOR. AI ADDS AGILITY, ASSERTIVENESS, AND REDUCED REWORK TO PROCESSES, AS WELL AS MORE INFORMED INFORMATION FOR BUSINESS DECISION MAKERS. HOWEVER, LAW FIRMS ARE UNSURE OF HOW TO BEGIN AND IMPLEMENT AUTOMATION IN THEIR BUSINESSES. AS A RESULT, THIS WORK FOCUSES ON THE TECHNOLOGICAL ADVANCEMENT OF LAW FIRMS AND PROPOSES A CONCEPTUAL REFERENCE MODEL FOR AI IMPLEMENTATION IN LAW FIRMS. THE DEVELOPMENT OF THIS APPROACH CONSISTS "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03NOV2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
