<http://example.com/capes#thesis/25554> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THIS THESIS, Y2O3 (YTTRIA) NANOPARTICLES (NPS) DOPED WITH RARE-EARTH IONS, NAMELY ND3+ AND ER3+,YB3+ ARE INVESTIGATED AS TEMPERATURE SENSORS FOR WHISPERING-GALLERY-MODE (WGM) RESONATORS. THE IONS WERE CHOSEN TO MATCH THE AVAILABLE PUMP LASERS FOR WGM COUPLING IN A SILICA MICROSPHERE, SO THAT MULTIPLE SENSING PARAMETERS CAN BE ACHIEVED WITH A SINGLE EXCITATION WAVELENGTH. THE SILICA MICROSPHERES AND THE NPS USED FOR THIS THESIS HAVE DIAMETERS OF ABOUT 100 ¿M AND 150 NM RESPECTIVELY. THE MUCH S"@pt ;
