<http://example.com/capes#thesis/25981> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: MANOMETRY IS ONE OF THE MOST USED METHODS FOR ASSESSING THE MAXIMUM VOLUNTARY CONTRACTION (MVC) OF THE PELVIC FLOOR MUSCLES (PFM). SEVERAL STUDIES HAVE SHOWN THAT THERE IS GOOD INTRA-EXAMINER RELIABILITY FOR THE MANOMETER. HOWEVER, A MODERATE LEVEL OF RELIABILITY HAS BEEN EVIDENCED IN THE INTER-EXAMINER ASSESSMENT. IN ADDITION, FEW STUDIES ASSESS THE CORRELATION BETWEEN THE VALUES OBTAINED BY DIFFERENT BRANDS OF MANOMETERS AND THERE IS EVIDENCE OF THE EXISTENCE OF SIGNIFICANT DIFFE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
