    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/REABILITAÇÃO_E_DESEMPENHO_FUNCIONAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/25984> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BACKGROUND: THE USE OF VALID INSTRUMENTS THAT CONSIDER THE PATIENT'S SELF-PERCEPTION REGARDING THEIR PHYSICAL-FUNCTIONAL CAPABILITIES IS ESSENTIAL FOR BETTER TARGETING THE PROCESSES OF PHYSICAL REHABILITATION AND SHARED HOSPITAL DISCHARGING OF OLDER ADULTS DIAGNOSED WITH HIP FRACTURES. STUDY RELEVANCE: THIS INSTRUMENT WAS PROPOSED TO ASSESS THE SELF-REPORTED EXPERIENCE OF OLDER ADULT PATIENTS HOSPITALIZED IN WARDS AFTER HIP FRACTURE SURGERY. THIS INSTRUMENT TAKES INTO ACCOUNT PHYSICAL-FUNCTIONAL"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25JUL2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
