<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2618> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS DEALS WITH THE RELEVANCE OF METAPHYSICS BEFORE THE SCIENTIFIC DEMARCATION OF KARL POPPER. THIS APPROACH IS NECESSARY, SINCE THE SPECIFIC ATTRIBUTIONS OF METAPHYSICS REGARDING THE SCIENTIFIC KNOWLEDGE ARE NOT CLEAR THROUGHOUT THE AUTHOR'S WORKS, EVEN THOUGH POPPER DOES NOT DENY THEIR REAL VALUE IN SCIENTIFIC PRODUCTION. THEREFORE, THIS WORK AIMS TO MAKE THE IMPORTANCE OF METAPHYSICS AND WHAT KIND OF FUNCTION IT HAS IN THE ELABORATION OF SCIENTIFIC KNOWLEDGE CLEAR. THE PHILOSOPHER AGRE"@pt ;
