<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2652> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PREVALENCE OF EXCESS WEIGHT IN PRESCHOOLERS AND SCHOOLCHILDREN HAS INCREASED CONSIDERABLY IN THE LAST DECADES, ESPECIALLY IN THE POPULATION WITH LOWER PURCHASING POWER. CHILDHOOD OBESITY IS A COMPLEX PROBLEM DUE TO ITS MULTIFACTORIAL ETIOLOGY THAT INVOLVES WEIGHT AND GESTATIONAL AGE AT BIRTH, EARLY WEANING, INADEQUATE INTRODUCTION OF COMPLEMENTARY FEEDING, RAPID WEIGHT GAIN IN THE FIRST MONTHS OF LIFE, PHYSICAL INACTIVITY AND EARLY SUPPLY OF OBESOGENIC FOODS INFLUENCED BY THE MEDIA. BESIDES "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "16FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "FATORES ASSOCIADOS AO EXCESSO DE PESO EM PRÉ-ESCOLARES E ESCOLARES RESIDENTES EM UMA ÁREA URBANA DE BAIXA RENDA"@pt ;
