<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2655> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ADOLESCENCE IS A PHASE MARKED BY VARIOUS BIOPSYCHOSOCIAL TRANSFORMATIONS AND DISSATISFACTION WITH BODY IMAGE, BEING CONSIDERED AS AN INCENTIVE FACTOR FOR THE SEARCH FOR BETTER OVERALL HEALTH, INCLUDING ORAL HEALTH. MANY STUDIES HAVE ALREADY PROPOSED TO STUDY THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN PSYCHOSOCIAL FACTORS AND ADOLESCENTS' ORAL HEALTH AND THE IMPACT ON QUALITY OF LIFE. IN THIS CONTEXT, THIS STUDY AIMS TO VERIFY IF THERE IS AN ASSOCIATION BETWEEN BODY IMAGE AND THE IMPACT OF ORAL HEALTH ON QUALITY O"@pt ;
