<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2657> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SEVERAL STUDIES HAVE BEEN UNDERTAKEN ON THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN HEALTH BEHAVIOR AND SOCIO-DEMOGRAPHIC AND PSYCHOSOCIAL CHARACTERISTICS IN ADOLESCENTS DUE TO THE LATTER´S GREAT VULNERABILITY TO SOCIAL AND HEALTH HARM. IT IS ALSO DUE TO HABITS, WITH FORESEEABLE FUTURE CHRONIC DISEASES, ACQUIRED DURING THIS LIFE PHASE AND WHICH WILL ACCOMPANY THEM DURING ADULTHOOD. ALTHOUGH THE IMPORTANCE OF ANALYZING ADOLESCENTS´ BEHAVIOR CHANGES IS WELL KNOWN AND ALTHOUGH PSYCHOSOCIAL FACTORS TO BASE HEALTH ASSI"@pt ;
