<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2663> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE USE OF GAMES IN DIGITAL VERSIONS (SERIOUS GAMES) AND PHYSICAL AS FACILITATORS IN HEALTH EDUCATION ACTIONS WITH ADOLESCENTS CAN HELP TO ACHIEVE TEACHING-LEARNING OBJECTIVES MORE EASILY AND CONTRIBUTE TO DISCUSS IDEAS; FOR LEARNING IN A MORE ACTIVE WAY; REINFORCING COMPETENCIES AND MAKING DECISIONS IN A MORE PARTICIPATORY CONTEXT. IN ADDITION, THE ADOPTION OF SEVERAL TECHNOLOGICAL INNOVATIONS AWAKEN FOR DIGITAL GAMES WHICH ARE SYNONYMS OF PLEASURE AND INCLUSION. IN THIS WAY, THEY CAN BE AN IMP"@pt ;
