<http://example.com/capes#thesis/2670> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SOURCE MATERIAL ACTS PREDOMINANTLY IN THE FORMATION OF SOILS IN THE SEMIARID REGION OF NORTHEASTERN BRAZIL, DUE TO THE LOW INTENSITY OF THE EFFECT OF CLIMATE FACTOR, THE SOILS FORMED TEND TO HAVE A GREATER CORRELATION WITH THEIR SOURCE MATERIAL, THAT IS, YOUNG SOILS. THE SEMI-ARID REGION HAS THE GREATEST SOIL DIVERSITY IN THE COUNTRY, AMONG THEM THE CHARACTERISTIC VERTISOLS ARE PRESENT DUE TO THEIR POTENTIAL FOR CONTRACTION AND EXPANSION AND THE CAMBISOLS, RELATIVELY YOUNG SOILS WITH A LARGE"@pt ;
