<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27340> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "GYPSUM HAS SHOWN SIGNIFICANT GROWTH IN ITS USE IN CIVIL CONSTRUCTION, BEING A LOW-COST AND EASY-TO-HANDLE MATERIAL. GRAPHENE OXIDE (GO), A MATERIAL DERIVED FROM GRAPHITE POWDER, HAS BEEN EXTENSIVELY STUDIED IN THE SCIENTIFIC COMMUNITY AND APPLIED IN THE BUILDING CONSTRUCTION AS A FILLER IN CEMENTITIOUS MATERIALS, CREATING MORE RESISTANT COMPOSITES. AMONG THE METHODS FOR OBTAINING GO, THE MODIFIED HUMMERS METHOD STANDS OUT, BECAUSE OF ITS LOW-COST PRODUCTION, HIGH YIELD, AND WATER PROCESSABILITY,"@pt ;
