    capes:hasAbstract "TECHNOLOGICAL ADVANCES ARE BECOMING MORE ACTIVE EVERY DAY, INDUSTRY 4.0 IS CHARACTERIZED BY A GLOBAL ARTICULATION OF THE WORLD ECONOMIC MARKET AND CHANGES IN WORK, ORGANIZATION, PRODUCTION OF CONSUMER GOODS, STRONGLY IMPACTING THE PROFESSIONAL FORMATION OF MEN TO BE INSERTED IN THE TRANSFORMATIONS THAT PERMEATES SOCIETY. THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN EDUCATION AND TECHNOLOGY BECOMES VERY CLOSE, RAISES QUESTIONS ABOUT THE FOURTH INDUSTRIAL REVOLUTION, THE INCREASE OF INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS, THE ADVAN"@pt ;
