    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_BIOLÓGICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27811> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "NEUROLOGICAL DISEASES SUCH AS DEPRESSION AND ANXIETY CAN CAUSE SERIOUS DAMAGE TO BEHAVIOR AND QUALITY OF LIFE. PLANT EXTRACTS CONTAINING PROTEINS AND SECONDARY METABOLITES HAVE BEEN USED AS THERAPEUTIC ALTERNATIVES FOR THESE DISEASES. PLANT COMPOUNDS THAT CAUSE DAMAGE TO THE HUMAN ORGANISM HAVE BEEN DESCRIBED AND ACUTE TOXICITY TESTS ARE NECESSARY TO PROMOTE THE SAFETY OF THE EXTRACT USED. THE LEAVES OF MORINGA OLEIFERA (MORINGACEAE FAMILY) ARE WIDELY USED IN HUMAN FOOD DUE TO THEIR HIGH NUTRITI"@pt ;
