    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_BIOLÓGICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27825> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "LECTINS ARE ABLE TO RECOGNIZE AND BIND SPECIFICALLY, BUT REVERSIBLY, TO MONOSACCHARIDES, OLIGOSACCHARIDES, POLYSACCHARIDES, AND EVEN GLYCOCONJUGATES. ONCE CONJUGATED TO FLUOROPHORES, THEY CAN CONSTITUTE INTERESTING PROBES FOR GLYCOBIOLOGICAL STUDIES. THIS STUDY DESCRIBES THE DEVELOPMENT OF TWO NEW NANOCONJUGATES BASED ON CARBOXYLATED QUANTUM DOTS (QDS) CONJUGATED TO SCHINUS TEREBINTHIFOLIA LEAF LECTIN (STELL) OR TO THE LECTIN OF PUNICA GRANATUM SARCOTESTA (PGTEL). DUE TO THEIR COMPLEX GLYCOCOMPO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28JAN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "PONTOS QUÂNTICOS CONJUGADOS ÀS LECTINAS DAS FOLHAS DE SCHINUS TEREBINTHIFOLIA (STELL) E SARCOTESTA DE PUNICA GRANATUM (PGTEL) COMO POTENCIAIS NANOFERRAMENTAS FLUORESCENTES PARA ESTUDOS GLICOBIOLÓGICOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ABDENEGO_RODRIGUES_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_BIOLÓGICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27826> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ARBOVIRUSES ARE RNA VIRUSES TRANSMITTED PRIMARILY BY BLOOD-SUCKING MOSQUITOES TO VERTEBRATE HOSTS. THE AEDES AEGYPTI MOSQUITO (DIPTERA: CULICIDAE) IS RESPONSIBLE FOR THE TRANSMISSION OF SOME OF THE MAIN ARBOVIRUSES WORLDWIDE, SUCH AS DENGUE, THE DISEASE CAUSED BY THE ZIKA VIRUS, CHIKUNGUNYA AND YELLOW FEVER. THE DEVELOPMENT OF NEW INSECTICIDES, PREFERABLY NATURAL, IS IMPORTANT TO EXPAND THIS LIST OF AVAILABLE ALTERNATIVES, AIMING THE USE IN INTEGRATED MANAGEMENT AND ROTATION STRATEGIES. LECTINS "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28JAN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "POTENCIAL INSETICIDA DE LECTINAS VEGETAIS CONTRA AEDES AEGYPTI: DEFININDO MECANISMOS DE AÇÃO A NÍVEIS HISTOLÓGICO, CELULAR E MOLECULAR"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LEONARDO_PREZZI_DORNELLES> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_BIOLÓGICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27827> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE STUDY DESCRIBES THE CLINICAL, LABORATORY AND IMMUNOLOGICAL CHARACTERISTICS OF SARS-COV-2 INFECTION IN HEALTHCARE WORKERS AT A HOSPITAL IN NORTHEAST BRAZIL BEFORE THE VACCINATION PHASE. FOR THIS, 50 PROFESSIONALS WHO WORKED DURING THE COVID-19 PANDEMIC WITH INFECTED PATIENTS WERE INVESTIGATED. SOCIODEMOGRAPHIC, CLINICAL AND EPIDEMIOLOGICAL DATA WERE OBTAINED TO CHARACTERIZE THE POPULATION. BLOOD SAMPLES WERE COLLECTED AND USED TO INVESTIGATE LABORATORY AND IMMUNOLOGICAL PARAMETERS. THE RESULT"@pt ;
