    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIAS_BIOLÓGICAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27828> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ALTHOUGH THERE IS A WORLDWIDE TREND TOWARDS THE CENTRALIZATION OF DIAGNOSTIC TESTING SERVICES, SOME DISEASES DO NOT RESPOND WELL TO THIS MODEL. THIS IS THE CASE OF INFECTIOUS AND CONTAGIOUS DISEASES OR THOSE THAT REQUIRE FREQUENT MONITORING OF ANALYTES, AS WELL AS INJURIES THAT REQUIRE RAPID INTERVENTION BECAUSE THEY REPRESENT A RISK TO THE LIFE OR HARM TO THE PATIENT. THIS NEED HAS SUPPORTED THE GROWTH OF THE SEARCH, DEVELOPMENT, AND OFFER OF DIAGNOSTIC METHODS CAPABLE OF EXPRESSING QUICK ANSWE"@pt ;
