<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27832> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CHANGES IN THE WAY OF THINKING ABOUT FOOD, IN ADDITION TO THE GROWING INCIDENCE OF PATHOLOGIES RELATED TO THE EXAGGERATED CONSUMPTION OF SOME COMPONENTS, THE FOOD INDUSTRY AND THE POPULATION WITH NEW INFORMATION HAVE BEEN LOOKING FOR ALTERNATIVES THAT BRING HEALTH BENEFITS, LIKE THE FUNCTIONAL FOODS. ONE OF THE SECTORS THAT HAVE TAKEN ADVANTAGE OF THIS STRATEGY IS THE BAKERY, WITH THE USE OF MIXED FLOURS FROM VEGETABLES. MESQUITE POD FLOUR IS A FLOUR OPTION, RICH IN NUTRIENTS AND EASILY ACCESSIB"@pt,
        "THE SÃO FRANCISCO RIVER BASIN IS HOME TO ABOUT 160 SPECIES OF FISH, AROUND 10% OF WHICH ARE THREATENED WITH EXTINCTION. AMONG THESE, ONE OF THE MOST CRITICAL IS THE ENDEMIC CATFISH PACAMÃ (LOPHIOSILURUS ALEXANDRI), WHICH WAS INCLUDED IN 2015 IN THE PAN SÃO FRANCISCO. RESTOCKING PROGRAMS HAVE BEEN DEVELOPED FOR SEVERAL SPECIES IN THE LAST 30 YEARS BY PUBLIC AND PRIVATE AGENCIES. HOWEVER, THESE ARE CONDUCTED WITHOUT GENETIC CRITERIA, WHICH MAY COMPROMISE THE DIVERSITY AND EVOLUTIONARY POTENTIAL OF"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "25FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
