        "CARACTERIZAÇÃO FÍSICO-QUÍMICA DE FARINHA DE ALGAROBA E SUA UTILIZAÇÃO NA PANIFICAÇÃO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LAIS_ALANNA_DE_SA_JARDIM>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/RENATA_DA_SILVA_FARIAS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_E_TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/RECURSOS_PESQUEIROS_E_AQUICULTURA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27833> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE APPROACH IN TERMS OF DIVERSITY AND FUNCTIONAL COMPOSITION OF BIOLOGICAL COMMUNITIES IS IMPORTANT FOR A BETTER UNDERSTANDING OF THE STRUCTURE AND UNDERSTANDING OF THE PROCESSES THAT INFLUENCE THEM. CHANGES IN DIVERSITY AND FUNCTIONAL COMPOSITION MAY BE RELATED TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONDITIONS, SUCH AS INCREASED HUMAN DISTURBANCE, AVAILABILITY OF RAINFALL, SOIL TYPES, AMONG OTHERS. UNDERSTANDING THESE CHANGES IS ESPECIALLY IMPORTANT IN BIOMES SUCH AS TROPICAL SEASONALLY DRY FORESTS - FTSS WHICH ARE"@pt,
        "THIS STUDY ANALYZED THE SUSTAINABILITY OF COASTAL SMALL-SCALE FISHERIES IN THE STATE OF AMAPÁ THROUGH THREE COMPLEMENTARY APPROACHES: A DESCRIPTION OF THE DYNAMICS OF FISHERIES AND ITS VALUE CHAIN, A CHARACTERIZATION OF FISHERIES CONFLICTS AND THE STATUS OF EXPLOITED RESOURCES ACCORDING TO FISHERS' PERCEPTION AND AN ASSESSMENT OF FISHERIES BASED ON 32 MULTIDISCIPLINARY INDICATORS (ECOLOGICAL, ECONOMIC, ETHICAL, INSTITUTIONAL, SOCIAL AND TECHNOLOGICAL) USING THE RAPFISH METHOD. DATA WERE COLLECTE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "03DEC2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "10JUN2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
