<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27835> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AGRICULTURE IN BRAZIL IS, HISTORICALLY, ONE OF THE MAIN BASES OF THE ECONOMY, CONSTANTLY EVOLVING IN THE DIFFERENT REGIONS OF THE COUNTRY. THE DIVERSIFICATION IN FRUIT PRODUCTION AND THE CONSIDERABLE AVAILABILITY OF SOLAR ENERGY AS AN ENERGY RESOURCE, AMONG OTHER ASPECTS, BROUGHT VISIBILITY TO THE BRAZILIAN NORTHEAST. IN ADDITION, RESEARCH ON INNOVATION AND TECHNOLOGICAL DIFFUSION IS INCREASINGLY LOOKING FOR SOLUTIONS TO REDUCE AGRICULTURAL LOSSES, ESPECIALLY IN THE POST-HARVEST PERIOD. IN AN AT"@pt,
        "THE WAY THE COLONIES HAVE BEEN STRUCTURED, SINCE THE ACTIONS OF THE NAVY ARE REFLECTED IN THE WAY OF LIFE OF FISHERMEN AND IN EVERY ORGANIZATION OF THE CATEGORY. THE ARTISANAL FISHERMEN OF PERNAMBUCO SURVIVE IN THE FACE OF UNCERTAINTIES THAT LEAD TO THE DECONSTRUCTION OF MODELS OF ASSOCIATIVISM AND COOPERATIVISM PRACTICED IN BRAZIL. THE CITY OF SÃO JOSÉ DA COROA GRANDE HAS A SIGNIFICANT IMPORTANCE IN THE FISHING PRODUCTION OF THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO AND IS INCLUDED IN THE AREA OF ENVIRONMENTAL P"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "19AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "27FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CARACTERIZAÇÃO DO ASSOCIATIVISMO PESQUEIRO PRATICADO NO LITORAL DO ESTADO DE PERNAMBUCO COM FOCO NA COLÔNIA DE PESCADORES Z9 (SÃO JOSÉ DA COROA GRANDE)"@pt,
        "DESENVOLVIMENTO DE UM SISTEMA DE SECAGEM SOLAR ADAPTADO ÀS CONDIÇÕES CLIMÁTICAS DO SEMIÁRIDO NORDESTINO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/FABRICYO_VILLA_VERDE_SILVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/JOSIMAR_ROBSON_DA_CRUZ_LIMA> ;
