<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27840> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CHAGAS DISEASE IS A NEGLECTED DISEASE CAUSED BY THE PROTOZOAN TRYPANOSOMA CRUZI, WHICH HAS TRIATOMINE INSECTS AS VECTORS. GLOBALLY, IT AFFECTS MORE THAN 8 MILLION PEOPLE, CONSTITUTING AN IMPORTANT PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM IN SEVERAL ENDEMIC COUNTRIES IN LATIN AMERICA. THE THERAPEUTIC TREATMENT FOR THIS DISEASE BASED ON THE USE OF BENZNIDAZOLE AND NIFURTIMOX, THE ONLY DRUGS FOR CLINICAL USE IN THE WORLD, HAS ALWAYS BEEN THE SUBJECT OF DEBATES AND THE STUDY AND DISCOVERY OF DRUGS THAT ARE MORE SELECT"@pt,
        "SURF ZONES ARE KEY HABITATS IN FISH ECOLOGY, PROVIDING SHELTER AGAINST PREDATORS AND HIGH ABUNDANCE OF FOOD. THE RESULTING CHAPTERS OF THIS RESEARCH, AIMED TO DESCRIBE THE STRUCTURE AND FUNCTIONING OF THE ASSEMBLAGE OF INVENTORIED FISH IN THE SURFZONE AND DEPOSITED IN THE ICHTHYOLOGY LABORATORY REFERENCE COLLECTION / DEPAQ / UFRPE (LIUFRPE), ANALYZING THE OCCURRENCE OF THESE SPECIES CONSIDERING THE INFLUENCE OF THE TIME SCALE (YEARS 2005 TO 2008), CRESCENT AND NEW MOON, DRY AND RAINY SEASONS AND"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "08AUG2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "DIVERSIDADE FUNCIONAL DA ICTIOFAUNA DA ZONA DE ARREBENTAÇÃO DE JAGUARIBE, ITAMARACÁ, LITORAL NORTE DE PERNAMBUCO"@pt,
        "INÉDITAS TIAZOLIDIN-4-ONAS COMO AGENTES ANTICHAGÁSICOS: SÍNTESE E AVALIAÇÃO DA ATIVIDADE ANTI-TRYPANOSOMA CRUZI"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/DANIELLE_DE_SOUSA_ALVES>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/FERNANDA_DE_LIMA_TOLEDO_FAVERO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_E_TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/RECURSOS_PESQUEIROS_E_AQUICULTURA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27841> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AMONG THE TACTICS USED TO INCREASE SELECTIVITY AND THE CATCH RATE OF THE TARGET SPECIES IN THE FISHING FOR TUNAS AND TUNA-LIKE FISH WITH PELAGIC OCEANIC LONGLINE, THE CHOICE OF BAIT HAS SHOWN GOOD RESULTS. IN THE PRESENT WORK THREE MAIN BAITS (MACKEREL, SQUID AND SARDINE) USED IN JAPANESE LONGLINE VESSELS THAT OPERATED IN BRAZIL IN THE COMMERCIAL TUNA FISHERY WERE EVALUATED IN 2012. THE VESSEL USED A DEEP PELAGIC LONGLINE, ACTING IN THE MESOPELAGIC REGION. THE EFFECT OF THE DIFFERENT FACTORS AND"@pt,
        "UNDERSTANDING THE THERMAL BIOLOGY OF SPECIES IS CRUCIAL TO ASSESS THE VULNERABILITY OF ORGANISMS TO CLIMATE CHANGE. THIS IS ESPECIALLY IMPORTANT FOR ANTS, GIVEN THEIR ECOLOGICAL IMPORTANCE IN TERRESTRIAL ECOSYSTEMS. THE GENERAL OBJECTIVE OF THIS DISSERTATION IS TO ANALYZE THE MAIN BIOTIC (EG. PHYLOGENY, BODY SIZE) AND ABIOTIC (EG. MICROHABITAT) FACTORS THAT GOVERN THE THERMAL LIMITS OF ANTS (MAXIMUM CRITICAL TEMPERATURE, HENCEFORTH CTMAX, AND MINIMUM CRITICAL TEMPERATURE, CTMIN) AT A GLOBAL AND "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "06FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "25FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO COMPARATIVO DA EFICIÊNCIA DE TRÊS TIPOS DE ISCA UTILIZADOS NA PESCA COMERCIAL DE ATUNS NA ZONA ECONOMICA EXCLUSIVA BRASILEIRA"@pt,
        "LIMITES TÉRMICOS CRÍTICOS EM FORMIGAS: REVISÃO DA LITERATURA E ANÁLISE EXPERIMENTAL EM DIFERENTES NÍVEIS DE ORGANIZAÇÃO BIOLÓGICA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/GERALDO_MIRANDA_DO_NASCIMENTO>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/TIAGO_HILARIO_PEDROSA_CAMPELLO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_E_TECNOLOGIA_AMBIENTAL>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/RECURSOS_PESQUEIROS_E_AQUICULTURA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27842> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ABSTRACT THE SELECTION OF SORGHUM CULTIVARS (SORGHUM BICOLOR L. MOENCH) TOLERANT TO HIGH TEMPERATURES FOR THE ARARIPE PLASTER POLE IS OF FUNDAMENTAL IMPORTANCE TO MINIMIZE THE NEGATIVE EFFECT OF FUTURE CLIMATE CHANGES. WITH THIS, THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO EVALUATE THE INFLUENCE OF THE INCREASE IN AIR TEMPERATURE ON EMERGENCE, INITIAL GROWTH, BIOMETRIC, ENZYMATIC, PRODUCTIVE PARAMETERS AND PRINCIPAL COMPONENT ANALYSIS. THE EXPERIMENTS WERE CARRIED OUT IN GROWTH CHAMBERS, USING SEVEN SORGHUM CULTIVARS "@pt,
        "REPRODUCTION AND MORPHOPHYSIOLOGY OF THE ELASMOBRANCH REPRODUCTIVE ORGANS BECAME BETTER UNDERSTOOD IN THE LAST YEARS OF THE PAST CENTURY. STILL LITTLE IS KNOWN ABOUT THE REPRODUCTION MORPHOLOGY OF SEVERAL SPECIES. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO DETERMINE THE REPRODUCTIVE STRATEGY OF RHIZOPRIONODON POROSUS AND RHIZOPRIONODON LALANDII SPECIES FROM THE COAST OF BRAZIL. THE CAPTURED SPECIMEN WAS MORPHOMETRICALLY CHARACTERIZED, WHERE TOTAL LENGTH (CT) AND PRE-CAUDAL LENGTH (PC) WERE MEASURED IN C"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "24FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO MORFOFISIOLÓGICO DA ESTRATÉGIA REPRODUTIVA EM DUAS ESPECIES DE RHIZOPRIONODON SP CAPTURADOS NA COSTA DO BRASIL"@pt,
        "TOLERÂNCIA DE CULTIVARES DE SORGO À ALTA TEMPERATURA PARA O POLO GESSEIRO DO ARARIPE"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/GLAUCIA_SUERDA_GOMES_DO_NASCIMENTO>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/LEONARDO_MORAIS_DA_SILVEIRA> ;
