<http://example.com/capes#thesis/27847> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "MACROBRACHIUM ROSENBERGII IS THE SECOND MOST FARMED FRESHWATER PRAWN SPECIES. IT BECOMED A TARGED SPECIE FOR PRODUCTION IN BRAZIL BECAUSE IT'S EASILY ACCLIMATIZATION. THE USE OF BIOFLOC SYSTEM FOR IMPROVEMENT OF FISHERIES PRODUCTION HAS BEEN RESEARCHED AND APPLIED IN THE LAST YEARS. HOWEVER, THERE ARE NO CONCLUSIVE STUDIES TO SHOW THE GROW OUT AND POST PRODUCTION VIABILITY OF THIS SPECIE IN BIOFLOC SYSTEM. THUS, THE AIM OF THIS EXPERIMENTE WAS TO EVALUATE THE GROWTH OF FRESHAWATER PRAWN M. ROSEN"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28AUG2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
