<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28471> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE INCREASE IN NOSOCOMIAL INFECTIONS CAUSED BY PSEUDOMONAS AERUGINOSA RESISTANT TO MULTIPLE CLASSES OF ANTIBIOTICS, INCLUDING LAST-LINE ONES, SUCH AS POLYMYXINS, HAS BEEN A GLOBAL CONCERN FOR SOME YEARS. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO CARRY OUT A DESCRIPTIVE AND COMPARATIVE ANALYSIS BETWEEN THREE GENOMES OF P.AERUGINOSA RESISTANT TO COLISTIN (POLYMYXIN E) AND TO IDENTIFY THE POSSIBLE GENES THAT MAY BE INVOLVED WITH THE PROFILE OF RESISTANCE TO MULTIPLE ANTIBIOTICS, PRESENTED BY THE ISOLATES"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "16DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
