    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28475> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BURKITT LYMPHOMA (BL) BELONGS TO THE GROUP OF NON-HODGKIN LYMPHOMAS. ALTHOUGH HIGHLY CURABLE IN EARLY STAGES, THIS DISEASE CAN TAKE A NEGATIVE COURSE IN SOME CASES. IN THIS CONTEXT, THIS STUDY AIMED TO USE COMPUTATIONAL METHODS BASED ON MACHINE LEARNING TO DEMONSTRATE THE VALUE OF MBL-2 GENE POLYMORPHISMS ON THE BL DEVELOPMENT AND THE INFLUENCE OF THESE POLYMORPHISMS AND MUTATIONS IN THE FLT3 GENE ON THE PROGNOSIS OF THIS DISEASE. IN ADDITION, IT ALSO ASPIRES TO CLASSIFY PATIENTS AND CONTROLS TH"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25MAR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DE POLIMORFISMOS DO GENE MBL-2 E MUTAÇÕES DO GENE FLT3 NA PATOGÊNESE E PROGNÓSTICO DE PACIENTES PEDIÁTRICOS COM LINFOMA DE BURKITT: UMA ANÁLISE BASEADA EM MACHINE LEARNING"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JONATHAN_WAGNER_DE_MEDEIROS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28476> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "COLLAGENASES ARE DEFINED AS PROTEASES CAPABLE OF DEGRADING THE TRIPLE HELIX OF NATIVE AND DENATURED COLLAGEN AND HAVE HIGH SPECIFICITY FOR THESE MOLECULES. THE ACTIVITY OF THESE ENZYMES HAS IMPORTANT MEDICAL AND INDUSTRIAL APPLICATIONS, BUT THE HIGH COST OF THEIR COMMERCIALIZATION HINDERS THEIR USE IN THE COMPOSITION OF MEDICINES. BECAUSE OF THIS, THE SEARCH FOR NEW PRODUCING MICROORGANISMS HAS GROWN IN RECENT YEARS, CONSIDERING THE POSSIBILITY OF OBTAINING THEM AT LOW COST. IN THIS CONTEXT, COL"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22DEC2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DO POTENCIAL COLAGENOLÍTICO DAS ENZIMAS PRODUZIDAS POR LEVEDURAS DO GÊNERO TRICHOSPORON SP. ISOLADAS DE PÓLEN ENCONTRADO EM ABELHAS MELIPONA SEMINIGRA SEMINIGRA"@pt ;
