    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28477> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SCHISTOSOMIASIS IS A PARASITOINFECTIOUS DISEASE CAUSED BY WORM OF GENRE SCHISTOSOMA, IT IS FOUND IN SEVERAL GEOGRAPHICS AREAS AROUND THE WORLD. IN BRAZIL, SCHISTOSOMIASIS IS IN GREATER ENDEMICITY IN THE STATE OF PERNAMBUCO. CURRENTLY, INFECTED PEOPLE ARE TREATED BY PRAZIQUANTEL (PZQ), IT IS USED AS THE ONLY DRUG OF CHOICE. HOWEVER, AS PZQ-RESISTANT STRAINS HAVE EXPANSIVE DEVELOPMENT, THE DEVELOPMENT OF NEW THERAPEUTICS APPROACHES IS EXTREMELY IMPORTANT. THE QUERCETIN (QUER) IS A FLAVONOID WIDELY"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "13OCT2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DOS EFEITOS TERAPÊUTICOS DO PRAZIQUANTEL E DA QUERCETINA NA PATOGÊNESE DA ESQUISTOSSOMOSE MANSÔNICA E DA DOENÇA HEPÁTICA GORDUROSA NÃO ALCOÓLICA EM MODELOS EXPERIMENTAIS IN VITRO E IN VIVO."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/KEYLLA_WALESCA_DA_SILVA_SANTIAGO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28478> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BREAST CANCER IS A MULTIFACTORIAL AND HETEROGENEOUS DISEASE, IN WHICH NUMEROUS CLINICAL RESPONSES WITH DIFFERENT GENETIC SIGNATURES CAN BE OBSERVED, RESULTING IN VARIATIONS IN THERAPIES. THE NUMBER OF CASES AND DEATHS OF AFFECTED PEOPLE INCREASES EVERY YEAR, DUE TO GREATER EXPOSURE TO RISK FACTORS AND LATE DIAGNOSIS. OBJECTIVE: THIS STUDY AIMED TO ANALYZE THE EXPRESSION OF THE CYTOKINE CXCL-12 AND ITS RECEPTOR CXCR-4, AND OF HORMONE RECEPTORS (ESTROGEN AND PROGESTERONE) IN BREAST CANCER BIOPSIES"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "23FEB2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO IMUNO-HISTOQUÍMICA DO MICROAMBIENTE TUMORAL DO CÂNCER DE MAMA E SUAS RELAÇÕES COM DADOS CLÍNICO-PATOLÓGICOS."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CINDY_JULIANE_DA_SILVA_FERREIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28479> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE INCREASE IN NOSOCOMIAL INFECTIONS CAUSED BY PSEUDOMONAS AERUGINOSA ISOLATES RESISTANT TO ANTIBIOTICS CONSIDERED OF \"LAST CHOICE\" SUCH AS POLYMYXINS (POLYMYXIN B AND COLISTIN) HAS BEEN CONSIDERED A SERIOUS PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM. ADAPTIVE RESISTANCE TO THIS CLASS OF ANTIBIOTICS IS MAINLY RELATED TO THE PRESENCE OF SPECIFIC MUTATIONS IN GENES THAT EXPRESS PROTEINS OF THE SO- CALLED TWO-COMPONENT SYSTEM (STIMULUS-RESPONSE MECHANISM TO SPECIFIC ENVIRONMENTAL CONDITIONS): PMRA/B; PHOP/Q; PAIRR/S; "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25APR2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CARACTERIZAÇÃO MOLECULAR DE PSEUDOMONAS AERUGINOSA RESISTENTE A COLISTINA: ANÁLISE GENÔMICA DE LINHAGENS INDUZIDAS AO FENÓTIPO DE RESISTÊNCIA E DE SENSIBILIDADE."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2022"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/KARITAS_FARIAS_ALVES_LIMA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28480> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE HUMAN ORAL CAVITY IS COMPOSED OF A DIVERSE AND COMPLEX BACTERIAL COMMUNITY, AMONG THE PHYLA THAT COLONIZE THIS MICROBIOTA, FIRMICUTES AND BACTEROIDETES ARE PREDOMINANT. THESE TWO PHYLA ARE RELATED TO SOME ORAL AND SYSTEMIC DISEASES. FOR A GOOD MOLECULAR ANALYSIS OF THIS ORAL MICROBIOTA, AN ADEQUATE BIOLOGICAL MATERIAL IS REQUIRED. THE AIM OF THIS STUDY WAS TO EVALUATE THE FIRMICUTES/BACTEROIDETES RATIO IN DIFFERENT ORAL SOURCES. SAMPLES OF UNSTIMULATED SALIVA, MOUTHWASH, CYTOLOGICAL BRUSHING"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "29AUG2022:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "COMPARAÇÃO DE DIFERENTES MATERIAIS BIOLÓGICOS PARA AVALIAR A RAZÃO FIRMICUTES/BACTEROIDETES DA MICROBIOTA ORAL"@pt ;
