    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_CELULAR_E_MOLECULAR_APLICADA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/28483> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY SOUGHT TO EVALUATE THE EFFECT OF NATURAL RADIATION, ANALYZING BOTH THE GENOTOXIC EFFECTS ON HEMOLYMPH CELLS OF JAGUAJIR ROCHAE AND BOTHRIURUS ROCHAI, AS WELL AS THE BODY VARIATION IN ADULTS SOON AFTER COLLECTION IN THE FIELD, IN ADULTS KEPT FOR A FEW MONTHS UNDER CONTROLLED LABORATORY CONDITIONS, AND IN THEIR DESCENDANTS. THE SAMPLES WERE OBTAINED FROM SEMI-ARID LOCATIONS IN THE CAATINGA BIOME, IN THREE MUNICIPALITIES IN THE STATE OF RIO GRANDE DO NORTE AND IN TWO OF PERNAMBUCO. IN AL"@pt ;
