<http://example.com/capes#thesis/286> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY EXAMINED THE ORGANIZATIONAL STORYTELLING APPROACH IN A 21ST CENTURY PRIVATE EARLY CHILDHOOD EDUCATION SCHOOL OF THE METROPOLITAN REGION OF RECIFE - PE, SEEKING TO ANALYZE ITS STRATEGIC CONTRIBUTION TO INNOVATIVE MANAGEMENT STRATEGIES. THE THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK CLARIFIES THE DEFINITION OF INNOVATION, ITS MYTHS, RULES AND TYPES, AS WELL AS THE NEW EXPANSION AND PROFESSIONALIZATION CONTEXT OF THOSE INVOLVED IN EARLY CHILDHOOD EDUCATION IN BRAZIL AND THE PURPOSEFUL NARRATIVE AS A STRATEGY"@pt ;
