<http://example.com/capes#thesis/29416> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS WORK HAS AS MAIN OBJECTIVE TO PERFORM A CONTRASTIVE STUDY AMONG THE AFRICAN VARIETIES OF PORTUGUESE (THE PORTUGUESE OF ANGOLA, GUINÉ-BISSAU AND SÃO TOMÉ AND PRÍNCIPE), FOCUSING ATTENTION ON THE NATURE OF THE VERBAL INFLECTION MORPHOLOGY AND ITS POSSIBLE IMPLICATIONS FOR THE PARAMETER BASED ON ESSAYS PRODUCED BY AFRICAN STUDENTS AS A REQUIREMENT FOR ADMISSION TO THE INTERNATIONAL UNIVERSITY OF AFRO-BRAZILIAN LUSOPHONY - UNILAB, LOCATED IN REDENÇÃO, CEARÁ. IN THE LIGHT OF THE GENERATIVE THEOR"@pt ;
