<http://example.com/capes#thesis/29433> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CONTEMPORARYBRAZILIANPOETRYFINDS, IN ITS PLURALITY, DIFFERENTFORMSOFRELATIONSWITHTHEFIELDOFVISUALITY. THE WORKOF MINAS GERAIS POET ANA MARTINS MARQUES ISCREATED, IN THISSENSE, IN ITS RELATIONSHIPWITH VISUAL SUPPORTS, SUCH AS VISUAIS ARTSANDPHOTOGRAPHY, AS WELL AS IN THE FORCE THATCERTAINIMAGESEXERTONHERPRODUCTIONDUETOTHEIRRECURRENCEANDTHE AMPLITUDE OFMEANINGSTHAT ARE REMADEINTOPOETRY. AMONGTHEM, THEIMAGEOFTHEHOUSEISONEOFTHEMOSTCONSTANT. BESIDES, IT HIGHLIGHTSTHEFIGURATIONOFDAILYLIFEANDTHEVALUESO"@pt ;
