<http://example.com/capes#thesis/29454> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SPACES AND ACKNOWLEDGEMENT OF AFRICAN AND AFRO-DESCENDANT CONTRIBUTIONS TO THE FORMATION PROCESS OF LATIN-AMERICAN LITERATURE AND LITERARY CRITICISM ARE MINIMAL. THIS IS ATTRIBUTED TO THE PREDOMINANCE OF EUROCENTRIC CIVILIZATIONAL REFERENCES IN LATIN AMERICA DUE TO THE COLONIAL RELATIONS IN THE CONTINENT. BY PRESENTING HOW AFRICAN COSMOGONY AND COSMOVISION OPERATE AND HOW THEY ARE ARRANGED IN THE AMERICAN CONTINENT, WE AIM TO FOSTER SENSIBILITIES TO BETTER UNDERSTAND AND ARTICULATE HUMAN RES"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "02SEP2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
