<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3445> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT STUDY HAD THE OBJECTIVE OF EVALUATING THE QUALITY OF INFORMATION ABOUT ORAL CANCER FROM AVAILABLE CONTENT IN PORTUGUESE (BRAZIL) ON GOOGLE, YOUTUBE AND INSTAGRAM. THE INITIAL SAMPLE FOR EACH PLATFORM WAS COMPOSED OF THE FIRST 100 LINKS FOUND. THE TEXTS OF INSTAGRAM'S WEBSITES AND POSTS WERE EVALUATED USING THE JAMA CRITERIA AND THE DISCERN INSTRUMENT. ANOTHER PARAMETER USED WAS THE FLESCH INDEX OF INTELLIGIBILITY AND ITS VALUES WERE CORRELATED WITH THE LEVEL OF BRAZILIAN SCHOOLING. O"@pt ;
