<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3447> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "\"THIS STUDY AIMS TO EVALUATE L-PRF AS A PREVENTIVE FACTOR FOR BISPHOSPHONATE-INDUCED OSTEONECROSIS LESIONS IN RATS AFTER SURGICAL, CLINICAL, HISTOLOGICAL AND IMAGING STUDIES, IMPROVING THE UNDERSTANDING OF ITS ACTION ON THE PATHOPHYSIOLOGY OF THE DISEASE BASED ON ITS BIOLOGICAL EFFECTS. TWENTY-NINE RATS WERE DIVIDED INTO FOUR GROUPS. ALL ANIMALS RECEIVED INTRAPERITONEAL INJECTIONS FOR 8 WEEKS (G1-SALINE / G2, G3 AND G4-ZOLENDRONIC ACID 0.15MG / KG), AFTER WHICH THEY UNDERWENT SURGERY FOR FIRST L"@pt ;
