    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/THAYANARA_SILVA_MELO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/ODONTOLOGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3449> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION: COMPLICATIONS SUCH AS PAIN, HEMATOMA, EDEMA AND TRISMUS ARE COMMON IN THE POSTOPERATIVE OF REMOVAL SURGERY OF THIRD MOLARS INCLUDED. CRYOTHERAPY AND THERMOTHERAPY AFTER THIS PROCEDURE HAS NOT YET BEEN DEFINED IN THE LITERATURE AS A TREATMENT OPTION, REGARDING METHOD, DURATION, INTERVAL AND MODE OF USE. THE INFLUENCE OF THESE THERAPIES ON THE REDUCTION OF POSTOPERATIVE SEQUELAE NEEDS TO BE DETERMINED. OBJECTIVE: THIS SYSTEMATIC REVIEW AND META-ANALYSIS AIMED TO ANSWER THE QUESTION P"@pt ;
