<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3724> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DECREASE THE CARBON DIOXIDE EMISSIONS WITHOUT AFFECTING THE SUPPLY OF ENERGY, MADE THE SEARCH OF NEW SOURCES OF ENERGY AN ALTERNATIVE TO SOLVE THIS PROBLEM. THE REUSE AGRICULTURAL RESIDUES APPEARS AS A GOOD ALTERNATIVE. IN 2014, BRAZIL PRODUCED APPROXIMATELY 5.5 MILLIONS OF COCONUT PER DAY, AND THIS BIG PRODUCTION ALSO GENERATES A VAST QUANTITY OF RESIDUES. THEREFORE THIS PAPER AIMS TO PRESENT A STUDY OF THE USE OF RESIDUES FROM COCONUT AGRICULTURE (DRY HUSK, LEAF AND COCONUT TRUNK). IT WAS PROP"@pt ;
