<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3725> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE WORLD ENERGY MATRIX, WHICH IS BASED ON FOSSIL FUELS, MAY CAUSE ECONOMIC IMPACTS, DUE TO PRICE FLUCTUATION AND AVAILABILITY PROBLEMS, AS WELL AS ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACT, SINCE THE USE OF THESE FUELS LEADS TO GREENHOUSE EFFECT AND ACID RAIN. THE BRAZILIAN MATRIX IS ALREADY ONE OF THE MOST RENEWABLE AND CLEAN OF THE GLOBE, BEING BASED ON HYDROPOWER PLANTS AND SUGAR CANE, WHICH IS USED TO PRODUCE ETHANOL AND ALSO ELECTRICAL ENERGY FROM ITS BAGASSE BURN. HOWEVER, THE CHARACTERISTIC OF ITS MATRIX MAK"@pt ;
