<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3727> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE GYPSUM INDUSTRY FACES TWO HUGE PROBLEMS, ONE OF THEM IN ITS PRODUCTION FIELD AND THE OTHER ON THE DISPOSAL OF THE GYPSUM WASTE. ON THE PRODUCTION FIELD, THE PROBLEM IS RELATED TO THE STRONG AND GROWING ENERGY CRISIS FACED BY THE ARARIPE POLE AREA, WHICH IS LOCATED IN A REGION WITH SCARCE SOURCE OF ENERGY. THIS WAY, FIREWOOD BECOMES THE BEST ENERGY SOLUTION DUE ITS LOW COST. ALTHOUGH THE GYPSUM INDUSTRY IS THE REGION'S LARGEST SOURCE OF EMPLOYMENT AND INCOME, IN A SHORT TERM, THERE IS NO PROS"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "31OCT2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "MODELAGEM DA DISTRIBUIÇÃO DE CALOR E TEMPERATURA, NA FASE TRANSITÓRIA, PARA O PROCESSO DE CALCINAÇÃO DE GESSO."@pt ;
