    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/TECNOLOGIA_DA_ENERGIA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3729> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE WORLDWIDE ENERGY SUPPLY HAVE ITS BIGGEST CONTRIBUTION FROM FOSSIL FUELS, WHICH ARE NOT RENEWABLE. THE CONSTANT USAGE OF THESE FUELS BROUGHT SIGNIFICANT ECONOMICAL, SOCIAL AND ENVIRONMENTAL IMPACT. DUE TO THESE IMPACTS, THERE WERE LARGER INCENTIVES TO FINDING NEW FUEL RENEWABLE SOURCES, AIMING MAINLY AT REDUCING THE ENVIRONMENTAL DAMAGE TO THE PLANET. IN BRAZIL, ONE OF THE STUDIED OPTIONS WAS USING BIODIESEL, WHICH IN 2004, WITH THE CREATION OF THE NATIONAL PROGRAM OF PRODUCTION AND USE OF BI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "09OCT2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
