<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3775> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "OVER THE YEARS, MEDICINAL PLANTS WERE THE MAIN SOURCE OF MEDICATION FOR THE MAJORITY OF THE POPULATION, WITHOUT ADEQUATE SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH TO PROVE THEIR SAFETY AND EFFICACY. MANDACARU (CEREUS JAMACARU D.C) IS A COLUMNAR CACTUS FOUND IN THE BRAZILIAN NORTHEAST, IS USED BY THE PEOPLE FOR INNUMERABLE PURPOSES INCLUDING, TREATMENT OF AFFECTIONS. THE PHYTOCHEMICAL PROFILE WAS EVALUATED BY HPLC, FTIR, UV, WHERE WE OBSERVED THE ABSORBANCE OF SEVERAL METABOLITES WITH IMPORTANT THERAPEUTIC PROPERTIES "@pt ;
