<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3849> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE DEVELOPMENT AND UNDERSTANDING OF COACHING ARE FUNDAMENTAL IN A PERIOD OF COMPETITIVENESS. FOR THIS, IT IS NECESSARY TO ALIGN THE NECESSARY COMPETENCIES TO FACILITATE THE WORK OF THE COACHES, USING SPECIFIC TECHNIQUES AND AUTONOMOUS TOOLS TO IMPROVE THE PERFORMANCE OF THE PROCESS. AS A RESULT OF THIS INVESTIGATION, WE SOUGHT TO VERIFY HOW THE COACHING PROCESS HAPPENS, WHICH ARE THE ACTORS INVOLVED, WHAT ARE THE AREAS OF COACHING AND THE CREDIBILITY OF THE SERVICE PROVIDER, CONSIDERING THAT CO"@pt ;
