<http://example.com/capes#thesis/3850> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE STUDIES ON SMART CITIES SHOW A CONSENSUS ON THE IMPORTANCE OF CITIZEN ENGAGEMENT FOR THE SUCCESS OF THE STRATEGY. HOWEVER, THERE ARE FEW STUDIES ON THE ROLE OF THE SMART CITIZEN IN ESTABLISHING THIS NEW GLOBAL FORM OF CITY PLANNING THAT CAN NOT BE CONFUSED WITH THE DIGITAL CITY. IT IS WORTH EMPHASIZING THAT THE FOCUS ON THE TECHNOLOGICAL TOOLS TO HAVE AN INTELLIGENT CITY CONTRIBUTES TO INCREASE THE EXISTING GAP OF THE ABSENCE OF STUDIES ON THE CITIZEN, TRUE PROTAGONIST OF THE HISTORY OF ANY "@pt ;
