<http://example.com/capes#thesis/4018> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE NUTRIENT ACQUISITION, STOCK AND FLOWS ARE DIRECTLY RELATED WITH ECOSYSTEM PRODUCTIVITY AND FACTORS THAT CAN CONTROL AND MODIFY THESE PROCESSES, SUCH AS WATER AVAILABILITY AND LOCAL ANTHROPOGENIC DISTURBANCES. IN SEASONALLY DRY TROPICAL FORESTS (FTSS) SUCH AS THE CAATINGA, ANTHROPOGENIC DISTURBANCES CAN ALTER PRODUCTIVITY AND NUTRIENT STOCKS IN ABOVEGROUND BIOMASS. IN ADDITION, THESE ECOSYSTEMS ARE EXPECTED TO FACE REDUCED RAINFALL LEVELS AS RESULT OF GLOBAL CLIMATE CHANGE. THUS, CAATINGA OFF"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTOQUES DE NUTRIENTES NA BIOMASSA ACIMA DO SOLO DE UMA FLORESTA SECA NA CAATINGA"@pt ;
