    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOLOGIA_VEGETAL> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/4137> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY AIMED TO VERIFY THE EFFICACY OF THE (E) -N- (4-BROMOPHENYL) -2- (THIOPHENE-2-YLMETHYLENE) -THIOSEMICARBAZONE (BTTSC) DERIVATIVE FOR THE TREATMENT OF ENDOMETRIOSIS AS WELL AS TO EVALUATE LIVER AND RENAL FUNCTION. THIRTY ALBINO RATS WERE DIVIDED INTO THREE GROUPS: GROUP I - RATS INDUCED ENDOMETRIOSIS (CONTROL); GROUP II- ENDOMETRIOSIS-INDUCED RATS TREATED WITH 0.8 MG / KG DEXAMETHASONE FOR 05 DAYS; GROUP III - ENDOMETRIOSIS-INDUCED RATS TREATED WITH BTTSC 30 MG / KG FOR 05 DAYS. GROUP I"@pt ;
