<http://example.com/capes#thesis/4146> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "POULTRY INDUSTRY IN BRAZIL IS A SECTOR OF GREAT IMPORTANCE IN THE ECONOMY FOR ITS GREAT PRODUCTIVE RESULTS, BEING RECOGNIZED WORLDWIDE AS ONE OF THE LARGEST PRODUCERS AND EXPORTERS OF CHICKEN MEAT. GOOD MANAGEMENT TECHNIQUES COMBINED WITH A BIOSECURITY SYSTEM ARE CRUCIAL TO SUCCESSFUL PRODUCTION. VACCINATION IS A PREVENTIVE WAY OF CONTROLLING OUTBREAKS OF NEWCASTLE DISEASE, CONSIDERED AS A HIGHLY CONTAGIOUS DISEASE THAT CAN HAVE DIRECT AND INDIRECT IMPACTS ON THE POULTRY SECTOR. 425 CHICKS WERE "@pt ;
