<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5044> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PRIMARY HEALTH CARE (PHC) REPRESENTS A COMPLEX SET OF KNOWLEDGE AND ACTIONS THAT REQUIRE A BROAD INTERVENTION IN SEVERAL ASPECTS SO THAT IT CAN HAVE A POSITIVE EFFECT ON THE QUALITY OF LIFE OF THE POPULATION. THINKING ABOUT THIS PERSPECTIVE, THE MINISTRY OF HEALTH CREATED THE FAMILY HEALTH SUPPORT CENTERS (NASF), WHICH AIMS TO SUPPORT THE INSERTION OF THE FAMILY HEALTH TEAM IN THE SERVICE NETWORK AND TO EXPAND ACTIVITIES IN BRAZIL. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY IS TO EVALUATE THE CONTRIBUTION OF T"@pt ;
