<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5045> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BASED ON THE FIELD OF ORAL HEALTH QUALITY EVALUATION IN PRIMARY CARE, THIS STUDY AIMED TO ANALYZE THE ASSOCIATIONS BETWEEN THE MUNICIPAL QUALITY STANDARDS (STRUCTURE AND WORK PROCESS) OF THE ORAL HEALTH TEAMS AND INDICATORS OF ORAL HEALTH (OUTCOME) OF PRIMARY CARE IN PERNAMBUCO. THE INFORMATION ELABORATED FOR THE CONSTRUCTION OF THE MUNICIPAL QUALITY STANDARDS WERE GENERATED FROM THE PMAQ-AB (2ND CYCLE) EXTERNAL EVALUATION INSTRUMENT IN PERNAMBUCO, WHILE DATA ON THE ANNUAL AVERAGES OF THE INDICA"@pt ;
