<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5046> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO EVALUATE THE ASSOCIATIONS BETWEEN QUALITY STANDARDS IN ORAL HEALTH OF STRUCTURE, PROCESS AND OUTCOME IN THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY OF RECIFE DURING THE SECOND CYCLE OF THE NATIONAL PROGRAM FOR IMPROVING ACCESS AND QUALITY OF PRIMARY CARE. A CROSS-SECTIONAL STUDY WITH QUANTITATIVE AND EVALUATIVE APPROACH WAS CARRIED OUT WITH THE 112 ORAL HEALTH TEAMS OF THE MUNICIPALITY THAT PARTICIPATED IN THE EXTERNAL EVALUATION OF THE PROGRAM IN 2014. SECONDARY DATA WERE OBTAINED BY "@pt ;
