<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5048> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AFTER YEARS OF MARGINALIZATION IN PUBLIC LIFE, LEGAL DEVICES BEGAN TO BE PRODUCED TO INSERT WOMEN INTO POWER SPACES. IN THIS SENSE, THE FOLLOWING WORK WILL SEEK TO SITUATE THE FEMALE FIGURE IN THE CURRENT POLITICAL CONTEXT, BESIDES ANALYZING THEIR PARTICIPATION AND POINTING OUT THE MAIN DETERMINANTS THAT INFLUENCE THEIR ELECTORAL SUCCESS. FINALLY, WE WILL EVALUATE THE ELECTIONS TO THE CHAMBER OF DEPUTIES FROM 1994 TO 2018 TO DETERMINE IF THE POLITICS OF ELECTORAL QUOTAS OF GENDER ARE, IN FACT, B"@pt ;
