<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5049> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WHAT IS THE EFFECT OF THE INSTITUTIONAL CAPACITY OF THE BRAZILIAN SUBNATIONAL ACCOUNTS COURTS IN DEFENDING THE PROBITY OF THE PUBLIC ADMINISTRATION? BASED ON THE PREMISE THAT THE INSTITUTIONAL CAPACITY OF AN ORGANIZATION IS ASSOCIATED WITH ITS ABILITY TO ACHIEVE COMPLIANCE WITH ITS COMPETENCIES, OBJECTIVES AND GOALS (FERNANDES, 2016), THIS RESEARCH PROPOSES TO ANSWER THE QUESTION RAISED BY THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN INSTITUTIONAL CAPACITY OF THE BRAZILIAN SUBNATIONAL ACCOUNTS COURTS ON THE ONE HAN"@pt ;
