<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5051> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WHAT DETERMINES THE LEVEL OF QUALITY IN THE HUMAN CAPITAL FORMATION OF A COUNTRY WITH STRONG REGIONAL ASYMMETRIES SUCH AS BRAZIL? THE UNIVERSALIZATION OF ACCESS TO EDUCATION IS ONLY AN INTEGRAL PART OF THE PROCESS ITSELF, MULTIFACETED, WHERE THE QUALITY OF EDUCATION IS ONE OF THE MAIN CHALLENGES OF CONTEMPORARY SOCIETIES. THIS PAGE IS NOT FOUND TO BE NOT SCHOOL, IS NOT DISABLED, AN ERROR TO SCHOOL, IS NOT BEHAVIOR SCHOOLS AND SOCIAL SCHOOLS, ARE IN THE AREA OF PARAÍBA, CONSIDERING THE YEARS OF 2"@pt ;
