<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5056> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY COMPARES THE NATIONAL STRATEGIES FOR FIGHTING POVERTY IN CHINA, INDIA, BRAZIL AD SOUTH AFRICA BETWEEN 2000 E 2015, THE TIME-FRAME OF THE UNITED NATIONS´ MILENIUM DEVELOPMENT GOALS. THE RESEARCH EXAMINES SOME OF THE MAIN OFFICIAL DOCUMENTS ON THE SUBJECT AND ALSO THE MOST RELEVANT NATIONAL PUBLIC POLICIES IN THE AREAS OF INCOME SECURITY AND EDUCATION. A TWO-LEVEL ANALYSIS (OF STRATEGIC DOCUMENTS AND OF PUBLIC POLICIES) IS CONDUCTED, IN THE LIGHT OF CONTEMPORARY THEORIES EXPLAINING MULT"@pt ;
