    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_POLÍTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5064> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DURING THE DECADE OF 80 AND THE BEGINNING OF THE DECADE OF 90, THE LATIN AMERICAN CONTEXT WAS SATED BY ECONOMIC, POLITICAL AND SOCIAL CRISES. HIGH UNEMPLOYMENT RATES, INCREASED POVERTY AND THE DILEMMAS EXPERIENCED BY SOCIAL PROTECTION ARE SOME OF THE FACTORS THAT CONTRIBUTED TO THIS SCENARIO. IN THIS CONTEXT, GOVERNMENTS SOUGHT TO PROMOTE POLICIES THAT MAXIMIZED THEIR CHANCES OF ELECTORAL SURVIVAL BY EXPANDING THEIR SPENDING ON POLICIES THAT REACHED MORE CLOSELY THE WELFARE OF VOTERS, AND SOCIET"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "22AUG2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
