<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5079> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE TWENTIETH CENTURY WAS MARKED BY A WORLDWIDE INCREASE IN THE INTERFERENCE OF THE JUDICIARY IN POLITICAL DECISIONS, FORMERLY EXCLUSIVE TO THE EXECUTIVE AND LEGISLATIVE BRANCHES, AND THE SPREAD OF JUDICIAL PROCEDURES BEYOND ITS SPHERE. THIS PHENOMENON, CALLED JUDICIALIZATION OF POLITICS, ALTHOUGH NOT UNANIMOUS IN THE LITERATURE, AROUSED THE CURIOSITY OF RESEARCHERS AROUND THE WORLD, WHO BEGAN TO ANALYZE THE JUDICIARY NOT ONLY FROM THE PHILOSOPHICAL-LEGAL POINT OF VIEW, BUT MAINLY FROM ITS POLIT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17SEP2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "SUPREMAS ESCOLHAS: REPERCUSSÃO GERAL E SELETIVIDADE NA REVISÃO JUDICIAL DIFUSA."@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LOUISE_DANTAS_DE_ANDRADE> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_POLÍTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5080> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DO CIVIL SOCIETY ORGANIZATIONS (CSOS) DELIVER RESULTS FOR MUNICIPAL HEALTH? THIS DISSERTATION AIMS TO VERIFY IF THESE NON-PROFIT INSTITUTIONS USE THEIR RESOURCES RECEIVED BY THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT IN ORDER TO IMPROVE HEALTH CONDITIONS OF THE BRAZILIAN LOCALITIES. I EXPECT THAT THE RESOURCES ALLOCATED TO CSOS IN HEALTH HAVE NO IMPACT ON HEALTH INDICATORS. TO DO SO, I WILL USE DATA FROM THE NATIONAL TREASURY SECRETARIAT, THE SYSTEM OF AGREEMENTS (SICONV) AND THE MAP OF ORGANIZATIONS OF CIVIL SOCIE"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
