<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5242> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "APIS MELLIFERA BEES HAVE ECOLOGICAL, ECONOMIC AND SOCIAL IMPORTANCE, AS THEY ARE ESSENTIAL FOR MAINTAINING THE BIODIVERSITY OF WILD AND AGRICULTURAL PLANTS, AND FOR THE PRODUCTION OF HONEY AND OTHER BEE PRODUCTS THAT ARE HIGHLY REQUESTED BY THE FOOD, PHARMACEUTICAL AND COSMETICS INDUSTRY. HOWEVER, A DECLINE IN BEE POPULATIONS HAS BEEN OBSERVED IN RECENT YEARS, OFTEN ATTRIBUTED TO COLONY COLLAPSE DISORDER (CCD), WHICH IS ASSOCIATED, AMONG OTHER FACTORS, WITH THE EXCESSIVE USE OF PESTICIDES. THUS,"@pt ;
