<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5807> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE ORGANIZATION OF WORK PLAYS A FUNDAMENTAL ROLE IN THE WORKER'S HEALTH / ILLNESS PROCESS, WHICH CAN BE CAUSE OF BOTH PLEASURE AND SUFFERING. THE THEME IS BASED ON THE THEORY OF WORK PSYCHODYNAMICS THAT SEEKS TO UNRAVEL THE PLEASURE-SUFFERING RELATIONSHIP AND COPING MECHANISMS DEVELOPED BY THE SUBJECT. THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY IS SEEN AS A RECENT FORM OF HEALTH ORGANIZATION THAT HAS GENERATED A STRONG PLEASURE-SUFFERING RELATIONSHIP. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO IDENTIFY THE INFLUENCE O"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
