<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5809> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE AREA OF PERSONNEL ADMINISTRATION IN BRAZIL IN THE LAST DECADES HAS UNDERGONE TRANSFORMATIONS STEMMING BOTH FROM THE CHANGES OF WORLD CAPITALISM AND FROM THE POLITICAL AND ECONOMIC CONTEXT EXPERIENCED IN THE COUNTRY. MAINLY AFTER THE REDEMOCRATIZATION ORGANIZATIONS HAVE HAD TO DEVELOP MANAGEMENT MECHANISMS BASED ON SOCIAL PARTICIPATION. IN THIS CONTEXT, COLLECTIVE BARGAINING IN PUBLIC MANAGEMENT EMERGES, WHICH, ALTHOUGH LITTLE USED, HAS BEEN HIGHLIGHTED AS A STRATEGY FOR THE SOLUTION OF CONFL"@pt ;
