<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5810> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN ORDER TO STRENGTHEN PRIMARY CARE AND CONSOLIDATE THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY, IT IS NECESSARY TO EVALUATE IT. IN THIS SENSE, THE MINISTRY OF HEALTH LAUNCHES THE PMAQ-AB IN 2011 AND BRINGS FINANCIAL INCENTIVE TO THE PERFORMANCE OF THE TEAMS. GIVEN THE IMPORTANCE OF THE WORK PROCESS FOR THE RESOLUTION OF ACTIONS IN BASIC CARE AND THE PERSISTENCE OF THE CENTERED MEDICAL MODEL, TEAMWORK BECOMES A CHALLENGE. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO ANALYZE THE WORK PROCESS IN THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY F"@pt ;
