<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5811> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE CENTERS OF DENTAL SPECIALTIES (CEO) CONSTITUTE AS REFERENCE SERVICES OF SECONDARY CARE IN ORAL HEALTH. BECAUSE THEY HAVE GREAT SOCIAL RELEVANCE, IT IS IMPERATIVE THAT THEY BE CONTINUOUSLY EVALUATED FOR THE ADOPTION OF BETTER QUALITY STANDARDS. THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO ANALYZE THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN QUALITY STANDARDS OF STRUCTURE AND WORK PROCESS WITH AN INDICATOR OF COMPLIANCE WITH CEO OUTPATIENT PRODUCTION GOALS. AN EXPLORATORY, EVALUATIVE, CROSS-SECTIONAL STUDY WAS CONDUCTED INVOLVING 929 CE"@pt,
        "THERE IS GROWING CONCERN ABOUT THE HIGH INCIDENCE OF ADAPTATION PROBLEMS AND MENTAL ILLNESS IN HIGHER EDUCATION. IN THIS SENSE, STUDIES HAVE HIGHLIGHTED THE IMPORTANCE OF EMOTIONAL INTELLIGENCE (IE) IN THE UNIVERSITY CONTEXT, SINCE HAVING THESE SKILLS IS ASSOCIATED WITH GREATER SOCIAL AND EMOTIONAL ADAPTATION. EMOTIONAL INTELLIGENCE IS THE ABILITY TO PROCESS EMOTIONAL INFORMATION BASED ON THE DEVELOPMENT OF COGNITIVE SKILLS SUCH AS PERCEPTION OF EMOTIONS, USE OF EMOTIONS TO FACILITATE THINKING, "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "11MAY2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "22MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ADAPTAÇÃO DE UM PROGRAMA DE DESENVOLVIMENTO DE HABILIDADES SOCIOEMOCIONAIS PARA UNIVERSITÁRIOS: IMPLEMENTAÇÃO E AVALIAÇÃO EM ESTUDANTES DE MEDICINA"@pt,
        "ANÁLISE DOS PADRÕES DE QUALIDADE DOS CENTROS DE ESPECIALIDADES ODONTOLÓGICAS EM RELAÇÃO AO CUMPRIMENTO DE METAS DE PRODUÇÃO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/LARYZA_NEVES_DELMONDES_MALHEIROS>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/TAINAH_DE_SOUZA_COSTA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
