<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5813> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "HEALTH PROMOTION ACTIONS ARE BASED ON THE PRECEPTS OF MODERN PROMOTION, AIMING THE FOCUS OF THEIR WORK ON THE SOCIAL DETERMINANTS OF HEALTH. MOST OF THESE ACTIONS ARE CARRIED OUT IN PRIMARY CARE BY THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY (ESF) PROFESSIONALS. THIS IS OF GREAT IMPORTANCE AS AN INTERVENTION INTERVENTION TO CHANGE THE LIFE CONTEXTS OF THE FAMILIES SERVED. HOWEVER, EVEN WITH ALL ITS EXPANSION AND POSITIVE RESULTS, MANY LOCALS STILL INSIST ON REMAINING WITH THE FOCUS OF CARE ON THE OLD BASIC ATTEN"@pt,
        "TRADITIONAL FORMS OF PERSONALITY MEASUREMENT MAKE USE OF EXPLICIT MEASURES, SUCH AS SELF-REPORT QUESTIONNAIRES. THESE MEASURES ARE SUSCEPTIBLE TO THE INFLUENCE OF SOCIAL DESIRABILITY AND CAN INHIBIT AND / OR SKEW THE RESULTS. AS AN ALTERNATIVE, SEEKING TO CONTROL THE TENDENCY FOR UNDERLYING RESPONSES, OTHER FORMS OF MEASUREMENT ARE BEING USED. THE PRESENT THESIS AIMED TO BUILD AND SEARCH FOR EVIDENCE OF VALIDITY OF AN IMPLICIT ASSOCIATION TEST TO ASSESS THE NEUROTICISM PERSONALITY TRAIT, BASED O"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "13MAY2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "22MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA IMPLEMENTAÇÃO DAS AÇÕES DE PROMOÇÃO DA SAÚDE EM UMA UNIDADE DE SAÚDE DE UM MUNICÍPIO BAIANO"@pt,
        "AVALIAÇÃO DO NEUROTICISMO PELO PROCESSAMENTO COGNITIVO IMPLÍCITO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/DEBORA_ALVES_DE_AMORIM>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/JASLENE_CARLOS_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5814> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN BRAZIL, THE EXPANSION OF PRIMARY HEALTH CARE (PHC) OCCURRED THROUGH THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY (FHP) AS OF 1994. HOWEVER, IT IS VERIFIED THAT ITS IMPLEMENTATION PRESENTS DIFFICULTIES REGARDING THE MONITORING AND EVALUATION OF ACTIONS. IN RECIFE, FROM 2013, NEW ORGANIZATIONAL ARRANGEMENTS OF THE ESF ARE CREATED, TITLING THESE NEW HEALTH UNITS UPINHA 24H OR UPINHA DIA. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS STUDY IS TO EVALUATE THE QUALITY OF THE DIFFERENT FHS ARRANGEMENTS IN THE CITY OF RECIFE. THIS IS AN EVAL"@pt,
        "THE PRESENT RESEARCH PEERS INTO THE DYNAMICS OF CREATIVE PROCESSES IN THE ACTIVITY OF GUITAR SINGING, FOCUSING ON ITS AESTHETIC-SUBJECTIVE, SEMIOTIC AND DIALOGIC INTERFACE. ALSO KNOWN AS REPENTE, CANTORIA DE VIOLA, OR VIOLA/GUITAR SINGING IS A TRADITIONAL ACTIVITY IN THE NORTHEAST OF BRAZIL, AND PRESENTS THE FOLLOWING CHARACTERISTICS AS ITS MAIN: IT IS AN ORAL, CARRIED OUT THROUGH IMPROVISE, FOLLOWING A SET OF RULES IN TERMS OF FORM (METRICS AND RHYME), PERFORMED BY A DUO OF SINGERS OR REPENTIST"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "20MAY2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "25MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA QUALIDADE DOS DIFERENTE ARRANJOS DA ESTRATÉGIA SAÚDE DA FAMÍLIA NO MUNICÍPIO DE RECIFE/PE"@pt,
        "COMO NASCEM AS METÁFORAS NO REPENTE? - UM ESTUDO EM PSICOLOGIA CULTURAL E DIALÓGICA SOBRE OS PROCESSOS CRIATIVOS DO CANTADOR DE VIOLA NO SERTÃO DO PAJEÚ"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CLAUDIA_MARIA_DOS_SANTOS_PEREIRA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/NATHALIA_ALBUQUERQUE_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5815> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ALTHOUGH THERE ARE A LARGE NUMBER OF STUDIES ON THE UNDERSTANDING OF TEXTS, THERE IS STILL MUCH TO INVESTIGATE ON THIS TOPIC DUE TO ITS COMPLEXITY AND RELEVANCE. IN RECENT YEARS, TWO ASPECTS HAVE DRAWN THE ATTENTION OF RESEARCHERS: THE MULTIPLICITY OF METHODOLOGICAL RESOURCES IN THE EXAMINATION OF THE COMPREHENSION OF TEXTS AND THE FACT THAT TEXTUAL COMPREHENSION IS NOT JUST ABOUT HISTORY, BUT EXTENDS TO OTHER TYPES OF TEXTS NARRATIVE TEXTS, TO ARGUMENTATIVE AND EXHIBITION TEXTS. ANALYZING THE L"@pt,
        "INTRODUCTION: DESPITE THE MANY ADVANCES AND ACHIEVEMENTS IN THE PUBLIC HEALTH, THE NETWORK FOR WOMEN'S HEALTH CARE ATTENTION (REDE DE ATENÇÃO À SAÚDE DAS MULHERES) IS STILL VERY FRAGMENTED RESULTING IN THE DISCONTINUATION OF CARE. THE HIGH MATERNAL MORTALITY RATE FOUND IN PERNAMBUCO SHOWS A NEED FOR SPECIFIC ACTIONS THAT WOULD HAVE A GREATER IMPACT FOR THE INVERSION OR THIS MATTER. OBJECTIVE: TO EVALUATE THE LEVEL OF IMPLEMENT OF THE ACTIONS OF THE STORK NETWORK (REDE CEGONHA) IN JABOATÃO DOS GU"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "01APR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "12MAR2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DA REDE CEGONHA NO MUNICÍPIO DE JABOATÃO DOS GUARARAPES/PE"@pt,
        "COMPREENSÃO DE FÁBULAS E HISTÓRIAS POR CRIANÇAS DO ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CAROLINA_PIEDADE_MORAIS_DE_FREITAS_SOARES_SILVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/PRISCYLLA_EMELINE_SILVA_DUARTE> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5816> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "INTRODUCTION. IN CONSIDERING THE COMPLEX HISTORICAL, ANTHROPOLOGICAL AND SOCIAL ASPECTS OF LEPROSY THAT TRANSCEND BIOLOGICAL ASPECTS, DIFFICULTIES ARE IDENTIFIED FOR THE INCORPORATION OF EPIDEMIOLOGICAL SURVEILLANCE ACTIONS INTO PRIMARY CARE. THE RESULTS HAVE NOT ALWAYS REACHED THE DESIRED GOAL, SINCE ISSUES THAT DEPEND ON MANAGEMENT (POLITICAL AND STRUCTURAL SUPPORT) PERPETUATE THEMSELVES AS PROBLEMS. OBJECTIVE. TO EVALUATE THE PERFORMANCE OF THE LEPROSY CONTROL PROGRAM (PCH) IN AN ENDEMIC MUNI"@pt,
        "OVER THE LAST FEW YEARS THE PREVALENCE OF CHILDREN WITH OBESITY HAS GROWN SIGNIFICANTLY AND HAS HAD A GREAT IMPACT ON THE LIVES OF CHILDREN, LEADING TO SERIOUS PHYSICAL AND PSYCHOLOGICAL CONSEQUENCES, WHICH LEADS TO WORRYING DISORDERS. THIS STUDY AIMED TO INVESTIGATE WHETHER OBESE CHILDREN ARE SUBJECT TO DIFFERENT PROCESSES OF DEVELOPMENT OF SELF-CONSCIOUSNESS, SELFCONCEPT AND SUBJECTIVE WELL BEING WHEN COMPARED TO NON-OBESE CHILDREN, IT ALSO SOUGHT TO INVESTIGATE THE DEVELOPMENT OF SELF-CONSCIO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "21MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28SEP2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO DE DESEMPENHO DO PROGRAMA DE CONTROLE DA HANSENÍASE EM UM MUNICÍPIO ENDÊMICO DE PERNAMBUCO"@pt,
        "DESENVOLVIMENTO DA AUTOCONSCIÊNCIA EM CRIANÇAS OBESAS: RELAÇÕES COM AUTOCONCEITO FENOMENAL E BEM ESTAR SUBJETIVO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ADRIELE_DE_SOUSA_MATOS>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/MORGANA_DE_FREITAS_CARACIOLO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5817> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "SYPHILIS DURING PREGNANCY IS A WORLDWIDE DISEASE THAT REMAINS A SIGNIFICANT CAUSE OF STILLMORTALITY AND INFANT MORBIDITY. VERTICAL TRANSMISSION OF THE DISEASE CAN OCCUR AT ANY TIME OF PREGNANCY AND ITS PREVENTION DEPENDS ON THE QUALITY OF CARE OFFERED TO PREGNANT WOMEN IN PRENATAL CARE, THROUGH EARLY DIAGNOSIS AND TIMELY AND APPROPRIATE TREATMENT, INCLUDING HER PARTNER. THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO EVALUATE THE QUALITY OF PRENATAL CARE FOR THE PREVENTION OF CONGENITAL SYPHILIS. FOR THIS, A NORMATI"@pt,
        "THIS STUDY HAS AS GENERAL OBJECTIVE TO UNDERSTAND WHAT IS THE UNDERSTANDING OF ECONOMIC CONCEPTS, AND, ESPECIALLY ON THE NOTION OF PROFIT, BY STUDENTS OF THE FINAL YEARS OF ELEMENTARY SCHOOL CONSIDERING THE ACCESS TO FORMAL CLASSES OF SCHOOL FINANCIAL EDUCATION. THE PIAGETIAN AND NEOPIAGETIAN ASSUMPTIONS (PIAGET; GRÉCO, 1974; VERGNAUD, 1983) ARE TAKEN AS A THEORETICAL BASIS TO UNDERSTAND THE FORMATION OF CONCEPTS, SEEKING TO ARTICULATE WITH THE STUDIES CARRIED OUT ON CHILDREN'S ECONOMIC KNOWLEDG"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "07MAY2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "20DEC2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "AVALIAÇÃO NORMATIVA DA QUALIDADE DA ASSISTÊNCIA PRÉ-NATAL PARA PREVENÇÃO DA SÍFILIS CONGÊNITA"@pt,
        "EDUCAÇÃO FINANCEIRA DE ESTUDANTES DO ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL II: O QUE SABEM SOBRE LUCRO?"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ANNA_BARBARA_BARROS_LEITE>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/KADJA_DE_FATIMA_PINHEIRO_FREITAS_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5818> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "DIABETES MELLITUS (DM) STANDS OUT AS ONE OF THE LEADING CHRONIC DISEASES IN THE WORLD AND IT IS RESPONSIBLE FOR A HIGH NUMBER OF PREMATURE DEATHS AND LOSS OF QUALITY OF LIFE. THEREFORE, THE INTEGRAL ATTENTION TO THE PATIENT WITH THAT CONDITION IS A CONSTANT NECESSITY AND IT IS FUNDAMENTAL THAT THE HEALTH PROFESSIONALS OF DIFFERENT AREAS HAVE KNOWLEDGE ABOUT THE RELATIONSHIPS BETWEEN DM AND THE ORAL DISEASES WICH ARE ONE OF ITS RISK FACTORS. THIS STUDY AIMS TO VERIFY THE KNOWLEDGE AND PRACTICES O"@pt,
        "MAJOR DEPRESSIVE DISORDER (MDD) HAS ACUTE FEATURES OF DEPRESSION AND IS THE MOST COMMON TYPE OF DEPRESSIVE DISORDER. ESTIMATES INDICATE THAT UNTIL THE PRESENT YEAR (2020) DEPRESSION WILL BE THE MOST DISABLING HEALTH PROBLEM IN THE WORLD, WITH LABOR, ECONOMIC, SOCIAL AND EMOTIONAL CONSEQUENCES. IN BRAZIL, DEPRESSION AFFECTS ABOUT 11.6 MILLION PEOPLE PER YEAR, AFFECTING INDIVIDUALS OF DIFFERENT AGE GROUPS. ONE OF THE COGNITIVE COMPONENTS THAT IS ALTERED IN THE FRAMEWORK OF TDM IS EMOTIONAL REGULAT"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "25MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CONHECIMENTOS E PRÁTICAS DOS PROFISSIONAIS DA ESTRATÉGIA DE SAÚDE DA FAMÍLIA NO MUNICÍPIO DE RECIFE-PE SOBRE DIABETES MELLITUS E DOENÇAS BUCAIS"@pt,
        "EFEITOS DA TERAPIA COGNITIVA BASEADA EM MIDFULNESS SOBRE A REGULAÇÃO EMOCIONAL DE PACIENTES COM TRANSTORNO DEPRESSIVO MAIOR"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/FLAVIA_INOJOSA_COUTINHO_DE_LIMA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/NORTHON_ROBERTO_FERREIRA_DE_MENDONCA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5819> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "\"THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO INVESTIGATE THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN MATERNAL PARENTING STYLES, CHILD ATTACHMENT PATTERNS WITH CHILDREN'S MORAL JUDGMENT ON MATERNAL JUSTICE AND QUALITY OF CHILDREN'S ACTION IN HYPOTHETICAL STORIES. MORAL JUDGMENT CONCERNS TYPES OF REASONING USED TO JUDGE AN ACTION AS \"\"RIGHT\"\" OR \"\"WRONG\"\" AND WHETHER SOMEONE IS \"\"FAIR\"\" OR \"UNFAIR\" IN THE LIGHT OF A SYSTEM OF NORMS, BEING CONSIDERED THE COGNITIVE ELEMENT OF THE MORAL DEVELOPMENT, WHICH EVOLVES THROUGHOUT CHILDHOOD. "@pt,
        "THE FAMILY HEALTH SUPPORT CENTERS EMERGED IN 2008 WITH THE SEARCH FOR THE EXPANSION OF THE HEALTH SERVICES OFFERED BY THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY AND THE PROPOSAL TO CONSOLIDATE INTEGRALITY IN PRIMARY CARE. SEVERAL EVALUATIONS ARE CARRIED OUT TO INVESTIGATE THE PROCESSES THAT INVOLVE THE BASIC ATTENTION AND ITS PRACTICES, TO CONTRIBUTE TO THE UNDERSTANDING OF SUCH COMPLEX ACTIONS, HOWEVER THERE IS A LACK OF SPECIFIC MODELS FOR NASF EVALUATION. THIS SCENARIO IS REPEATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF JABO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "20FEB2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CONTRIBUIÇÕES DO NÚCLEO DE APOIO À SAÚDE DA FAMÍLIA PARA A INTEGRALIDADE DA ATENÇÃO BÁSICA NO MUNICÍIO DE JABOATÃO DOS GUARARAPES: UM ESTUDO AVALIATIVO"@pt,
        "ESTILO PARENTAL MATERNO, APEGO INFANTIL E JULGAMENTO MORAL DE CRIANÇAS SOBRE JUSTIÇA MATERNA E INTENCIONALIDADE DO ATO"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CLAUDIA_MARIA_DE_OLIVEIRA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/MONICA_FRANCIELE_DA_SILVA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5820> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "AEDES AEGYPTI, A SPECIES NATIVE TO AFRICA, HAS BEEN RESPONSIBLE FOR THE RESURGENCE AND EXPANSION OF ARBOVIRUSES IN THE WORLD. IN BRAZIL, THE CO-CIRCULATION OF THE FOUR SEROTYPES OF THE DENGUE VIRUS AND THE RECENT INTRODUCTION OF THE CHIKUNGUNYA AND ZIKA VIRUSES ALERTED HEALTH AUTHORITIES TO THE NEED TO IMPROVE VECTOR CONTROL AND PREVENTION ACTIONS. THIS STUDY AIMED TO EVALUATE THE EFFECTIVENESS OF AN INTEGRATED VECTOR CONTROL MODEL OF AE AEGYPTI, CHARACTERIZED BY THE MASSIVE REMOVAL OF EGGS BY O"@pt,
        "THE EXECUTIVE FUNCTIONS (EF) ARE UNDERSTOOD AS PREDICTIVE SKILLS OF ACADEMIC PERFORMANCE, ALLOWING DECISION-MAKING, ASSESSMENT AND ADAPTATION OF BEHAVIORS AND STRATEGIES, BEEN A CONSENSUS ON SCIENTIFIC LITERATURE THEIR IMPORTANCE FOR MATHEMATICAL PERFORMANCE. HOWEVER, EVEN CONSIDERING ITS RELEVANCE, DATA FROM AVAILABLE STUDIES ON THE SUBJECT STILL DID NOT ALLOW TO INFER PRECISELY ABOUT THE RELATIONSHIPS ESTABLISHED BETWEEN EF AND STUDENTS'S PERFORMANCE IN MATHEMATICS. THUS, THIS STUDY AIMED TO E"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "EFETIVIDADE DE UM MODELO DE CONTROLE VETORIAL DO AEDES AEGYPTI GUIADO POR ARMADILHAS DE OVIPOSIÇÃO EM BAIRROS DA CIDADE DO RECIFE"@pt,
        "FUNÇÕES EXECUTIVAS E DESEMPENHO MATEMÁTICO EM ESCOLARES"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ALANNY_NUNES_DE_SANTANA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/MAISA_BELFORT_TEIXEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5821> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE NURSING PROFESSIONAL IS STRONGLY SUBJECT TO JOB BURNOUT DUE TO THE LARGE SIZE OF HIS WORK AND THE VARIOUS HAZARDS RELATED TO THE CONDITIONS IMPOSED BY HIS WORK. THE PRESENT STUDY AIMS TO EVALUATE OCCUPATIONAL STRESS AND BURNOUT SYNDROME IN EMERGENCY NURSING PROFESSIONALS OF A PUBLIC HOSPITAL IN CAMARAGIBE-PE. THIS IS A DESCRIPTIVE, QUANTITATIVE AND PREVALENT CROSS-SECTIONAL STUDY. THE SAMPLE CONSISTED OF 72 NURSING PROFESSIONALS, 58 TECHNICIANS AND 14 NURSES. PARTICIPANTS ANSWERED THREE SELF"@pt,
        "THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO INVESTIGATE THE DECISION MAKING OF STUDENTS IN THE 1ST, 2ND AND 3RD GRADES OF HIGH SCHOOL FACING FINANCIAL SITUATIONS, SEEKING TO ANSWER THE RESEARCH QUESTIONS: (I) ARE THE HEURISTICS OF ANCHORING, AFFECTION, MENTAL ACCOUNTING AND LOSS AVERSIONS PRESENT IN STUDENTS CHOICES FACING FINANCIAL SITUATIONS? (II) WHICH OF THESE HEURISTICS ARE MOST FREQUENTLY MOBILIZED BY STUDENTS IN DECISION MAKING FACING PROPOSED FINANCIAL SITUATIONS? (III) ARE THERE DIFFERENCES IN THESE HEU"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "27FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "28MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTRESSE LABORAL E SÍNDROME DE BURNOUT EM UMA EQUIPE DE ENFERMAGEM DE URGÊNCIA E EMERGÊNCIA"@pt,
        "HEURÍSTICAS NAS TOMADAS DE DECISÕES DE ESTUDANTES DO ENSINO MÉDIO FRENTE A SITUAÇÕES FINANCEIRAS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2019"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/JESSICA_BARBOSA_DA_SILVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/LUCIANA_BATISTA_DE_SOUZA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/PSICOLOGIA_COGNITIVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/SAÚDE_PÚBLICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/5822> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "NON-SUICIDAL SELF-INJURY IS A GROWING PUBLIC HEALTH PROBLEM, WHICH CAN MANIFEST ITSELF IN COMORBIDITY WITH OTHER DISORDERS, OR IN ISOLATION, REVEALING THE MULTIDIMENSIONALITY OF THIS BEHAVIOR AND THE NEED FOR RESEARCH WHICH CAN CONTRIBUTE ON UNDERSTANDING IT. DESPITE THE RELEVANCE OF THE MATTER, THE SCIENTIFIC LITERATURE HAS PRODUCED LITTLE PROGRESS IN THE LAST TEN YEARS. THE LACK OF RESEARCH FOCUSED AT INVESTIGATING THE COGNITIVE AND EMOTIONAL IMPAIRMENTS OF NON SUICIDAL SELF-INJURY HINDER THE "@pt,
        "THE EXPANDED NUCLEUS OF FAMILY HEALTH AND BASIC CARE WAS CREATED TO SUPPORT THE INSERTION OF THE FAMILY HEALTH STRATEGY IN THE HEALTH NETWORK AND TO EXPAND THE COMPREHENSIVENESS, RESOLUTION, TERRITORIALISATION AND REGIONALIZATION OF PHC ACTIONS. IT SHOULD BE COMPOSED OF A MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM GUIDED BY THE INTERDISCIPLINARITY AND INTEGRALITY OF THE ATTENTION AND BY THE THEORETICAL-METHODOLOGICAL REFERENCE OF THE MATRIX SUPPORT. THE PURPOSE OF THIS STUDY WAS TO ANALYZE THE DEVELOPMENT OF NASF M"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "05MAY2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "29MAR2019:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "INVESTIGAÇÃO NEUROCOGNITIVA DE FUNÇÕES EXECUTIVAS E RESPOSTA EMOCIONAL EM JOVENS COM AUTOLESÃO NÃO SUICIDA"@pt,
        "O APOIO MATRICIAL NO TRABALHO DO NÚCLEO DE APOIO À SAÚDE DA FAMÍLIA"@pt ;
