    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/EDUARDO_MATOS_OLIVEIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/CIÊNCIA_POLÍTICA> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6303> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "COMPETITION IS A RELEVANT DIMENSION IN ASSESSING THE QUALITY OF DEMOCRACY OF ANY DEMOCRACY. THE WORK DEFENDED THE IDEA THAT THE EXISTENCE OF AN EFFECTIVE OPPOSITION IS A COMPONENT OF THE POLITICAL COMPETITION, BEING POSSIBLE TO EVALUATE ITS QUALITY THROUGH THE FORM THAT AN OPPOSITION EXPRESSES ITSELF IN DIFFERENT DEGREES OF EFFECTIVENESS (INTENSITY), AND MANAGES BEYOND PRESENTING ITSELF, BECOME A VIABLE ELECTORAL ALTERNATIVE TO THE GOVERNMENT IN A GIVEN ELECTION. THE PROPOSED RESEARCH PROBLEM CO"@pt ;
