<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6321> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS DEALS WITH THE INTERNAL ORGANISATION OF PSDB AND PT POLITICAL PARTIES. THE GENERAL OBJECTIVE OF THE RESEARCH IS TO IDENTIFY THE VARIATION OF THE INTERNAL ORGANISATION OF THE POLITICAL PARTIES FROM THE EXPERIENCE OF RUNNING THE NATIONAL EXECUTIVE BRANCH. THE SPECIFIC OBJECTIVES ARE: (1) TO IDENTIFY THE ORGANISATIONAL CHANGES IN THE PSDB DURING THE FHC GOVERNMENT (1995-2002); (2) IDENTIFY THE ORGANIZATIONAL CHANGES IN THE PT DURING LULA'S ADMINISTRATION (2003-2010). EACH POLITICAL PART"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "21FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
