    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6457> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "ENVIRONMENTAL CONTAMINATION BY AGROCHEMICALS HAS BEEN INCREASINGLY ADDRESSED BY SEVERAL AUTHORS IN THE LITERATURE AND DISCUSSED BY CIVIL SOCIETY, BECAUSE OF THE WAY IN WHICH NEGATIVE EXTERNALITIES IN ALL ENVIRONMENTAL MATRICES ARE BEING FELT. THE PRESENT STUDY AIMED TO PROPOSE MEASURES OF ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT IN THE USE OF PESTICIDES WITH A FOCUS ON WATER RESOURCES FOR THE SUBBASIN OF THE LOWER NATUBA RIVER, IN VITÓRIA DE SANTO ANTÃO - PE. IN ORDER TO DO SO, WE USED INDEXES THAT ARE DESIGNED"@pt ;
