    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6461> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE USE OF MEDICINAL PLANTS TO TREAT DISEASES IS AN ANCIENT PRACTICE AND USED WORLDWIDE. AMONG THE MEDICINAL PLANTS, MYRACRODRUON URUNDEUVA ALLEMÃO (ANACARDIACEAE) AND SIDEROXYLON OBTUSIFOLIUM (ROEM. & SCHULT.) T. D. PENN. (SAPOTACEAE) STAND OUT, BOTH WIDELY USED TO TREAT INFLAMMATION AND INFECTIONS OF THE FEMALE GENITAL TRACT, STOMACH AND THROAT CONDITIONS, AND TO HEAL WOUNDS ON THE SKIN AND MUCOUS MEMBRANES. MANY PHARMACOLOGICAL PROPERTIES OF THE EXTRACTS AND COMPOUNDS ISOLATED FROM M. URUNDEU"@pt ;
