    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6465> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PESTICIDES ARE WIDELY USED IN AGRICULTURE, AS THEY DEMONSTRATE EFFECTIVENESS IN CONTROLLING THE MOST VARIED TYPES OF PESTS, AND BY ASSOCIATION, CONTRIBUTE TO GREATER FOOD PRODUCTIVITY. HOWEVER, ITS INDISCRIMINATE USE HAS BEEN CAUSING SERIOUS DAMAGE TO THE ENVIRONMENT AND THE LIVING ORGANISMS OF THESE IMPACTED ENVIRONMENTS, BECOMING A DELETERIOUS RELATIONSHIP FOR LIVING BEINGS. A TECHNIQUE THAT SHOWS PROMISE IN THE PROCESS OF IMPROVING AREAS IMPACTED BY THE INDISCRIMINATE USE OF PESTICIDES IS BIO"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "10NOV2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
