    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6479> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "IN THE INDUSTRIAL SCENARIO, IT IS COMMON TO USE OILS AND PETRODERIVATIVES THAT ARE TOXIC AND DIFFICULT TO REMOVE, SUCH AS OCB1 OIL. FOR THE CLEANING OF MACHINES, EQUIPMENTS AND OTHER SURFACES IMPREGNATED BY THESE OILS, INDUSTRIES ADOPT THE USE OF HIGH COST PRODUCTS WHICH ARE OFTEN ALSO TOXIC AND HARMFUL TO WORKERS' HEALTH AND THE ENVIRONMENT. IN VIEW OF THIS PROBLEM, THIS THESIS PRESENTS THE FORMULATION OF BIODEGRADABLE, NONTOXIC, LOW COST AND EFFICIENT DETERGENTS IN THE REMOVAL OF INDUSTRIAL OI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "19FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
