    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6480> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "NANOSTRUCTURED MATERIALS (SUCH AS PARTICLES, FIBERS AND COMPOSITES) HAVE BEEN ATTRACTED GROWING INTEREST IN SEVERAL TECHNOLOGICAL APPLICATIONS IN BIOLOGY AND HEALTH, WITH THE AIM OF REDUCING SIDE EFFECTS, INCREASING THEIR ACTIVITY IN VITRO OR IN VIVO, PROTECTING AND PREVENTING DEGRADATION OF SUBSTANCES AND APPLIED IN THE DETECTION OF SPECIFIC MOLECULES. THE GENERAL OBJECTIVE OF THIS WORK WAS TO DEVELOP AND APPLY STRUCTURED MATERIALS ON A MICRO AND NANOMETRIC SCALE FOR ENCAPSULATION AND DETECTION"@pt ;
