<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6481> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS STUDY PRESENTS THREE EXPERIMENTAL PHASES: A FIRST EVALUATION OF THE EFFECT OF LICURI OIL SUPPLEMENTATION ON FOLLICULAR ACTIVATION AND NEEDS, AND THE DEVELOPMENT OF SECONDARY SHEEP FOLLICLES AFTER IN VITRO CULTIVATION WITH LEPTIN. 32 SHEEP, DISTRIBUTED IN FOUR GROUPS, RECEIVED 0% FEED (CONTROL); 2%; 4% OR 5% LICURI OIL FOR 77 DAYS. AFTER COLLECTING THE OVARIES, MORPHOLOGY AND FOLLICULAR ACTIVATION WERE EVALUATED, AND SECONDARY FOLLICLES FROM EACH TREATMENT WERE CULTURED (12 DAYS) IN ¿-MEM + "@pt ;
