<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6502> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE SEARCH FOR NEW BIOACTIVE COMPOUNDS IS MOTIVATED BY THE NEED TO OBTAIN MORE EFFECTIVE THERAPEUTIC RESULTS THAT ACT SELECTIVELY IN THE TREATMENT OF DISEASES. IN THIS SCENARIO, THE DERIVATIVES OF THIAZOLES AND THIAZOLIDINEDIONES HAVE BEEN EXTENSIVELY EXPLORED DUE TO THEIR WIDE RANGE OF BIOLOGICAL ACTIVITIES DESCRIBED IN THE LITERATURE. THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS WORK WAS TO DETERMINE THE CYTOTOXIC AND ANTIBACTERIAL EFFECT OF NEW DERIVATIVES OF THIAZOLIDINEDIONES (SERIES ST AND NW) AND THIAZOLE (SERI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "28FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "EFEITO ANTICANCERÍGENO, ANTIBACTERIANO E TOXICOLÓGICO DE DERIVADOS DO TIAZOL E TIAZOLIDINEDIONA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/PEDRO_SILVINO_PEREIRA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6511> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "BASED ON THE THEME OF MEDICINAL PLANTS AND THE ETHNOMEDICINAL FUNCTIONS ATTRIBUTED TO SELAGINELLA CONVOLUTA (JERICHO, CLOSED-HAND OR PARROT-HAND), THE OBJECTIVE WAS TO EVALUATE IN VITRO THE INFLUENCE OF SUPPLEMENTATION WITH EXTRACT OF SELAGINELLA CONVOLUTA IN THE CULTURE MEDIUM OF OVARIAN FOLLICLES AND SHEEP THEREBY CREATING SCIENTIFIC EVIDENCE ABOUT THE REAL PROPERTIES OF THE PLANT SPECIES ON THE FEMALE REPRODUCTIVE SYSTEM.THE FIRST EXPERIMENT WAS BASED ON THE INVESTIGATION OF POSSIBLE RELATION"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "ESTUDO DA ATIVIDADE DO EXTRATO ETANÓLICO DE SELAGINELLA CONVOLUTA SOBRE O CRESCIMENTO IN VITRO DE FOLÍCULOS OVINOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/RENATA_GOMES_REVOREDO> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6539> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CISPLATIN IS ONE OF MOST EFFICIENT ANTICANCER DRUGS, BUT IT PROMOTES OVARIAN TOXICITY BY INCREASING THE OXIDATIVE STRESS. THUS, PRETREATMENT BEFORE CHEMOTHERAPY WITH NATURAL COMPOUNDS WITH ANTIOXIDANT EFFECTS COULD REDUCE THIS TOXICITY. RECENTLY, AMBURANA CEARENSIS (THE CHAPTER 1 OF THIS THESIS SHOWS A REVIEW ABOUT THE IN VITRO EFFECTS OF THIS PLANT IN FEMALE REPRODUCTION) AND ITS SECONDARY METABOLITES, GALLIC ACID AND PROTOCHATECUIC ACID, HAVE ATTRACTED ATTENTION BECAUSE OF THEIR ANTIOXIDANT AC"@pt,
        "CLASSROOM READING AND WRITING PRACTICES ARE SOMETIMES SEEN BY SOME STUDENTS IN PUBLIC SCHOOLS AS ARBITRARY AND TIRING ACTIVITIES, RATHER THAN AS AN IMPORTANT PRACTICE THAT WILL SERVE A LIFETIME. THIS PAPER INVESTIGATES THE USE OF CORDEL LITERATURE AS AN INTERVENTION PEDAGOGICAL TOOL TO MOTIVATE THE STUDENTS' READING AND WRITING DEVELOPMENT. THROUGH A SIMPLE AND DIRECT LANGUAGE, COUPLED WITH THE SONORITY OF RHYME, THE CORDEL ALLOWS A BROAD AND INTERDISCIPLINARY APPROACH. USING THE LINGUISTIC VARI"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "19FEB2020:00:00:00"^^xsd:date,
        "24MAR2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "A LITERATURA DE CORDEL COMO PRÁTICA MOTIVADORA DA LEITURA E DA ESCRITA EM SALA DE AULA"@pt,
        "PAPEL DO EXTRATO DE AMBURANA CEARENSIS, ÁCIDO GÁLICO E ÁCIDO PROTOCATECUICO, NA PREVENÇÃO DA TOXICIDADE OVARIANA INDUZIDA PELA CISPLATINA EM CAMUNDONGOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2017"^^xsd:gYear,
        "2020"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/ANA_VALERIA_UBALDO_DA_SILVA>,
        <http://example.com/capes#author/BRUNA_BORTOLONI_GOUVEIA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/BIOTECNOLOGIA_-_REDE_RENORBIO>,
        <http://example.com/capes#program/LETRAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6540> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE CONSTRUCTION OF KNOULEDGE IN SCHOOL THOUGH CULTURAL SPREAD IS REQUIRIMENT OF THE CONTEMPORARY TEACHING AND LEARNING PROCESS. THUS THIS WORK RUNS, WITH THE AID OF LITERATURA AND OTHERS ARTISTIC MANIFESTATIONS, THE PEDAGOGICAL ROUTE OF PROJECT DEVELOPED FOR THE LITERACY OF THE INDIVIDUAL INVOLVED. THE OBJECT OF THE RESEARCH ARE THE USE OF LESS SOCIALLY PRESTIGIOUS LITERATURE, AS THE CORDEL'S BOOKLET, IN ORDER IS PROMOTE THE LITERACY DURING BASIC EDUCACION. THE SURVEYED EVENTS LASTED TWO YEARS,"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "17MAR2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "A LITERATURA EM FESTIVAIS ESCOLARES: O FOLHETO DE CORDEL NA ESCOLA"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2017"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CARLOS_FREDERICO_DE_GOUVEA_CALDAS> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/LETRAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6541> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK INVESTIGATED HOW THE READING MEDIATION OF THE PORTUGUESE LANGUAGE TEACHER OCCURS IN THE PERFORMANCE OF READING ACTIVITIES IN THE CLASSROOM. THUS, IT WAS ALSO SOUGHT TO OBSERVE IF THERE IS POSSIBLY ANY RELATION BETWEEN THIS MEDIATION OF THE PORTUGUESE-LANGUAGE TEACHER AND THE LOW LEVELS OF READING PROFICIENCY VERIFIED IN THE RESULTS OF EXTERNAL EVALUATIONS SUCH AS THE NATIONAL SYSTEM FOR THE EVALUATION OF BASIC EDUCATION (SAEB) AND THE EDUCATIONAL EVALUATION SYSTEM OF PERNAMBUCO "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "10MAY2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "A MEDIAÇÃO LEITORA NO OITAVO ANO DO ENSINO FUNDAMENTAL: POR UM ENSINO SEM NEGLIGÊNCIAS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2017"^^xsd:gYear ;
    capes:isAuthoredBy <http://example.com/capes#author/CATARINA_PIRES_QUIRINO_DE_SA> ;
    capes:isFromProgram <http://example.com/capes#program/LETRAS> .

<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6542> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE DEVELOPMENT OF RESEARCHES USING BIOLOGICAL SYSTEMS IN ORDER TO EXTRACT NEW BIOMOLECULES, ESPECIALLY PROTEASES AND LECTINS, HAS BEEN GROWING SINCE THE DISCOVERY OF ITS DIVERSE APPLICATIONS IN BIOTECHNOLOGICAL PROCESSES. THEREFORE, THE OBJECTIVE OF THIS THESIS WAS TO EVALUATE THE BIOTECHNOLOGICAL POTENTIAL OF GLIRICIDIA SEPIUM SEED AND ITS USE AS A SUBSTRATE FOR FERMENTATION OF PLANTS GROWTH-PROMOTING BACTERIA AIMING TO INDUCE THE PRODUCTION OF FIBRINOLYTIC PROTEASES, AS WELL AS THE ISOLATION,"@pt ;
