<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6800> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PERNAMBUCO BASIN (BPE) IS A MARGINAL BASIN OF THE EASTERN PORTION OF SOUTH AMERICAN PLATFORM, FORMED DURING THE SOUTH ATLANTIC OCEAN OPENING. THE NARROW COASTAL ZONE OF PEB IS BOUNDED TO NORTH BY THE PERNAMBUCO SHEAR ZONE, NEAR RECIFE CITY, AND BY THE MARAGOGI-BARREIROS HIGH, TO SOUTH. ALTHOUGH, EVIDENCES ABOUT POST-RIFT TECTONIC REACTIVATION EVENTS HAS BEEN REPORTED IN PREVIOUS WORKS, NONE HAVE SYSTEMATICALY TREATED THE CHARACTERISTICS AND TECTONO-STRATIGRAPHIC RELATIONS OF THESE EVENTS IN "@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "09JAN2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
