<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6802> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK BRINGS NEW INFORMATION ABOUT THE LIMIT BETWEEN THE PERNAMBUCO AND PARAÍBA BASINS DURING THE MAASTRICHTIAN. UNTIL THE PRESENT WORK GRAMAME FORMATION, CARBONATIC UNIT THAT HAD ONLY BEEN DESCRIBED IN THE NORTHERN REGION OF RECIFE, NOW HAS ITS REGISTRATION IN THE SOUTH REGION. THE MAIN OBJECTIVE OF THE STUDY WAS TO IMPROVE THE EXISTING KNOWLEDGE ABOUT THE CITED UNIT AND AS A DATA BASE THE YATE STRATIGRAPHIC WELL (1 LABIO-PE3), IN THE RANGE OF 50 TO 54 METERS, WHERE BETWEEN DEPTHS 50"@pt ;
