<http://example.com/capes#thesis/6837> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE PLANTS USED IN FOLK MEDICINE HAVE BEEN SOUGHT BY THE PHARMACEUTICAL INDUSTRIES THAT ARE LOOKING FOR NEW PROTOTYPES USEFUL FOR THE MANUFACTURE OF DRUGS DIRECTED TO THE TREATMENT OF VARIOUS DISEASES. THIS HAS LED TO A RESURGENCE OF INTEREST IN SECONDARY METABOLITES PRODUCED BY SEVERAL PLANTS SUCH AS PHENOLIC COMPOUNDS, AMONG WHICH COUMARINS ARE PROMINENT. THESE PURIFIED SUBSTANCES EXHIBIT POTENT AND RELEVANT BIOLOGICAL ACTIVITIES AS WELL AS LOW TOXICITY IN MAMMALS. IN THIS WAY, THE SET OF BENE"@pt ;
