<http://example.com/capes#thesis/7151> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH IS AIMED TO ANALYZE THE ENVIRONMENTAL DEGREE OF VULNERABILITY AND CONTAMINATION IN THE PARNAÍBA RIVER, SPECIFICALLY IN THE URBAN STRETCH OF TERESINA, BASED ON ITS GEOLOGICAL, SEDIMENTOLOGICAL HISTORY AND BATHYMETRIC DESCRIPTION. BEARING IN MIND THAT THE MORPHOLOGY OF THIS RIVER IS IN CONSTANT TRANSFORMATION BECAUSE IT IS SUBJECTED TO INTERNAL AND EXTERNAL MODIFYING AGENTS, WITH EMPHASIS ON ANTHROPIC IMPACTS, THE FOLLOWING METHODOLOGY WAS USED: SURVEY AND ANALYSIS OF GEOCARTOGRAPHIC"@pt ;
