<http://example.com/capes#thesis/7259> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS DISSERTATION HAS THE OBJECTIVE OF ANALYSING THE FRAILTY OF THE CURRENT SOCIAL SECURITY SYSTEM ON THE PROTECTIONS IT GRANTS TO WORKERS THAT DWELL IN INFORMALITY. THE CHARACTERISTICS OF THE WORKING SOCIETY AFTER THE FALL OF THE WELFARE STATE AND THE RISE OF GLOBALIZATION AND OF THE FINANCIAL CAPITAL POINT TOWARDS A SCENARIO OF PRECARIZATION AND DRASTIC REDUCTIONS OF JOB VACANCIES. IN THIS REALITY THE DOMINATION OF INFORMAL WORK IS NOTICEABLE, REPRESENTING TODAY ABOUT HALF OF THE ECONOMICALLY "@pt ;
