<http://example.com/capes#thesis/7277> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS RESEARCH HAS INVESTIGATED THE THEME OF CONSTITUTIONAL INTERPRETATION AND ITS LIMITS FROM THE ASSUMPTIONS OF CRITICAL RATIONALISM, USING THE WORKS OF KARL POPPER AS STARTING POINTS. IN ORDER TO REVEAL THE PRECISE EXTENT OF THE INTERPRETATIVE PROBLEM IN THE BRAZILIAN SUPREME FEDERAL COURT (STF), AN EXPLORATORY RESEARCH WAS MADE ON 2016'S DECISIONS THAT USED EMPIRICAL DATA, WITH THE AIM OF ACHIEVING AN ANALYSIS OF THE ARGUMENTATION OF THE BRAZILIAN JUDGES. BASED ON A BRIEF DISCUSSION ABOUT FIV"@pt ;
