    capes:hasAbstract "THE PRESENT WORK'S SUBJECT CONSISTS AT THE FUNDAMENTALS OF THE PROPERTY ACCORDING TO THOMAS AQUINAS AND ITS REFLEXES IN THE BRAZILIAN JURIDICAL EXPERIENCE PRE-CODIFICATION. INDEED, THE CURRENT DEFINITION OF PROPERTY CORRESPONDS TO ONLY ONE OF THE MANY POSSIBLE SOLUTIONS FOR THE DISTRIBUTION OF GOODS IN SOCIETY AND THE REGULATION OF THEIR USE BY MEN. THE STUDY OF PROPRIETARY HISTORY ALLOWS US TO UNDERSTAND OTHER FOUNDATIONS FOR THE APPROPRIATION OF GOODS. IN THE MEDIEVAL PERIOD, FOR EXAMPLE, PROP"@pt ;
