<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8182> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE INTERNATIONAL CONCEPTION OF SMART CITIES POINTS TO THE USE OF SMART TECHNOLOGIES TO SOLVE SOCIO-ENVIRONMENTAL, ECONOMIC AND CULTURAL CHALLENGES. THIS STRATEGY AIMS TO RAISE THE CITY'S QUALITY OF LIFE IN THE FACE OF FUTURE CHALLENGES THAT REQUIRE SOCIAL INNOVATION, SUSTAINABLE POLICIES AND SMART PLANNING. IN A COMPLEX AND GLOBAL BUSINESS ENVIRONMENT, IMPROVING PERFORMANCE AND ENSURING COMPLIANCE WITH ALL ENVIRONMENTAL, HEALTH AND SAFETY OBLIGATIONS, COMMITMENTS AND CONSTRAINTS IS A CHALLENGE."@pt ;
