<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8545> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS SEEKS TO DEAL WITH THE THEME OF ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT IN THE NORTHEAST REGION OF BRAZIL. THE WORK IS DIVIDED INTO FOUR CHAPTERS. THE FIRST CHAPTER FOCUSES ON THE APPROACH TO THE SOCIOECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT OF THE NORTHEAST OVER THE FIRST TWO DECADES OF THE 21ST CENTURY. THE WORK CONTEXTUALIZES THE REGION, ITS HISTORY, SOME ACTIVE PUBLIC POLICIES AND EMPHASIZES THE SEMI-ARID TERRITORY, NOTABLY A SUB-REGION OF INTEREST DUE TO ITS STILL FRAGILE SOCIO-ECONOMIC FOUNDATIONS. THE ANALYSIS, WHI"@pt ;
