<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8547> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THE GLOBAL RACE FOR NET ZERO, REINFORCED AT COP26, HAS MADE THE RENEWABLE ENERGY MARKET ONE OF THE MOST PROMISING TO ATTRACT INVESTMENT BY 2050. FOR SOME DEVELOPING COUNTRIES WITH A VOCATION FOR RENEWABLE ENERGIES, THIS VOLUME OF RESOURCES CAN GENERATE A BOOST TO THE LOCAL SOCIO-ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT, BEING STRENGTHENED WITH THE CONSIDERATION OF SOCIAL ASPECTS IN ENERGY POLICIES. AMONG THE SOCIAL ISSUES IN THE HOLE OF ENERGY SECTOR, JOB DYNAMICS HAVE DRAWN GREAT ATTENTION FROM POLICYMAKERS AND AC"@pt ;
