<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8549> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS ADDRESSES THE RELEVANCE OF SPACE IN THE STUDY OF VARIOUS PHENOMENA OF SOCIAL, ECONOMIC ORDER, AMONG OTHERS, AS WITH THE OBSERVATION OF DIFFERENT PATTERNS OF BEHAVIOR THROUGH SPACE IT IS POSSIBLE TO INVESTIGATE THE DIFFERENT DIMENSIONS OF HUMAN INTERACTION AND HOW THIS CAN BE RELATED WITH THE PHENOMENA THAT ARE THE OBJECT OF STUDY. THUS, THREE APPLICATIONS WERE CARRIED OUT WHERE THE INFLUENCE OF CHARACTERISTICS OR INTERACTIONS THROUGH SPACE PROVED TO BE EXTREMELY RELEVANT TO OBTAIN CO"@pt ;
