<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8553> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "KINDERGARTEN IS THE FIRST SCHOOL ENVIROMENT FOR CHILDREN TO LIVE TOGETHER. THERE ARE A LOT OF EVIDENCES POINTING TO THE BENEFITS OF THE ENROLLMENT IN THIS ENVIROMENT ON THE FUTURE SCHOOL PERFORMANCE, SPECIALLY IN THE COGNITIVE SKILLS. HOWEVER, THE LITERATURE IS STILL VERY LIMITED ABOUT THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN THIS FIRST SCHOOL STAGE AND THE DEVELOPMENT OF SOFT SKILLS. THEREBY, THIS RESEARCH AIMS TO CONTRIBUTE BY MEASURING THE AVERAGE IMPACT OF KINDERGARTEN ON SOFT AND COG- NITIVE SKILLS, FOR CH"@pt ;
