<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8556> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "THIS THESIS INVESTIGATES THE TAXATION OF CIGARETTES IN THE PRESENCE OF SMUGGLING. IN THIS SENSE, IT PRESENTS A DEBATE ABOUT THE HARMFUL EFFECTS OF SMOKING, AND THE USE OF PUBLIC POLICIES TO REDUCE THE PREVALENCE, IN PARTICULAR, THE TAXATION OF CIGARETTES. IN ADDITION, IT ASSESSES THE ISSUE OF TAXATION OF CIGARETTES IN THE PRESENCE OF SMUGGLING, WHICH IS THE BRAZILIAN CASE. THEN, IT BUILDS FROM A COMPUTABLE GENERAL EQUILIBRIUM MODEL WITH MICRO-FOUNDATIONS AND CHARACTERISTICS OF THE BRAZILIAN ECON"@pt ;
