<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8557> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "WHY DOES BRAZIL STILL HAVE ONE OF THE LARGEST BANKING SPREADS IN THE WORLD? EFFICIENCY AND COST IN OBTAINING CREDIT ARE CRUCIAL IN A NATION'S ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT. THE PRESENT WORK SEEKS TO ANALYZE THE CASE, MAKING A COMPARISON WITH THE COUNTRIES OF THE WORLD, INVESTIGATING MAINLY, BUT NOT ONLY, THE RELATIONSHIP OF CREDIT RECOVERY AND MARKET CONCENTRATION WITH THE BANKING SPREAD. THROUGH THE AVAILABILITY OF AGGREGATED NATIONAL DATA FROM THE WORLD BANK, 46 COUNTRIES ARE COMPARED DURING THE YEARS "@pt ;
