<http://example.com/capes#thesis/8882> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "PEGMATITE MINERALS INCLUDING FELDSPARS ARE WIDELY USED IN CERAMICS, PAINT AND CONSTRUCTION INDUSTRIES. FELDSPARS ARE ALUMINUM SILICATES AND THE MAIN CONSTITUENTS OF PEGMATITES. IN GENERAL, FELDSPAR PEGMATITES ARE RELEASED BY FRAGMENTATION AND CONCENTRATED BY SIEVING OR SCREENING. THERMAL TREATMENT WITHOUT CRYSTALLINE STRUCTURE DESTRUCTION COULD BE AN AUXILIARY TOOL TO RELEASE ECONOMIC INTEREST MINERALS SINCE MATERIALS PRESENTS DIFFERENTIATED VOLUMETRIC DILATION WITH THE TEMPERATURE INCREASE. THE"@pt ;
