<http://example.com/capes#thesis/9201> a capes:Thesis ;
    capes:hasAbstract "CALOTROPIS PROCERA, IS A MEDICINAL PLANT KNOWN IN PERNAMBUCO AS \"SILK-COTTON\". IS LATICÍFER PLANT BELONGING TO THE FAMILY APOCYNACEAE BROADLY FOUND IN THE BRAZILIAN NORTHEAST. CURRENT LITERATURE DATA SHOW THAT PROTEINS OBTAINED FROM ITS LATEX HARBOUR ANTI-INFLAMMATORY ACTION. IN THE PRESENT STUDY, A PROTEIN FRACTION OBTAINED BY ION-EXCHANGE CHROMATOGRAPHY NAMED LPPII, WHICH IS RICH IN CYSTEINE PROTEASES, HAD ITS IMMUNMODULATORY ACTIVITY EVALUATED IN CULTURES OF PERITONEAL MACROPHAGES INFECTED BY"@pt ;
    capes:hasDefenseDate "24FEB2017:00:00:00"^^xsd:date ;
    capes:hasTitle "CARACTERIZAÇÃO IMUNOMODULATÓRIA DE PROTEASES CISTEÍNICAS OBTIDAS DO LÁTEX DE CALOTROPIS PROCERA EM CULTURAS DE MACRÓFAGOS"@pt ;
    capes:hasYear "2017"^^xsd:gYear ;
